var book = {
	"name": "Isaiah",
	"numChapters": 66,
	"chapters": {
		"1": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">1 </span>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17656A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17656A\"></sup>vision of Isaiah the son of Amoz, which he saw concerning Judah and Jerusalem <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17656B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17656B\"></sup>in the days of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17656C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17656C\"></sup>Uzziah, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17656D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17656D\"></sup>Jotham, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17656E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17656E\"></sup>Ahaz, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17656F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17656F\"></sup>Hezekiah, kings of Judah.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17657G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17657G\"></sup>Hear, O heavens, and give ear, O <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17657H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17657H\"></sup>earth;for the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has spoken:“Children <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17657I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17657I\"></sup>have I reared and brought up,but they have rebelled against me.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>The ox <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17658J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17658J\"></sup>knows its owner,and the donkey its master's crib,but Israel does <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17658K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17658K\"></sup>not know,my people do not understand.”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Ah, sinful nation,a people laden with iniquity,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17659L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17659L\"></sup>offspring of evildoers,children who deal corruptly!They have forsaken the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,they have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17659M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17659M\"></sup>despised <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17659N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17659N\"></sup>the Holy One of Israel,they are utterly <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17659O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17659O\"></sup>estranged.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Why will you still be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17660P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17660P\"></sup>struck down?Why will you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17660Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17660Q\"></sup>continue to rebel?The whole head is sick,and the whole heart faint.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17661R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17661R\"></sup>From the sole of the foot even to the head,there is no soundness in it,but bruises and soresand raw wounds;they are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17661S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17661S\"></sup>not pressed out or bound upor softened with oil.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17662T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17662T\"></sup>Your country lies desolate;your cities are burned with fire;in your very presenceforeigners devour your land;it is desolate, as overthrown by foreigners.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17663U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17663U\"></sup>the daughter of Zion is leftlike a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17663V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17663V\"></sup>booth in a vineyard,like a lodge in a cucumber field,like a besieged city.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17664W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17664W\"></sup>If the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hostshad not left us <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17664X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17664X\"></sup>a few survivors,we should have been like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17664Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17664Y\"></sup>Sodom,and become like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17664Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17664Z\"></sup>Gomorrah.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Hear the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,you rulers of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17665AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17665AA\"></sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17665AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17665AB\"></sup>Sodom!Give ear to the teaching of our God,you people of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17665AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17665AC\"></sup>Gomorrah!",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17666AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17666AD\"></sup>“What to me is the multitude of your sacrifices?says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>;I have had enough of burnt offerings of ramsand the fat of well-fed beasts;I do not delight in the blood of bulls,or of lambs, or of goats.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“When you come to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17667AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17667AE\"></sup>appear before me,who has required of youthis trampling of my courts?",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Bring no more vain offerings;incense is an abomination to me.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17668AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17668AF\"></sup>New moon and Sabbath and the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17668AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17668AG\"></sup>calling of convocations—I cannot endure <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17668AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17668AH\"></sup>iniquity and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17668AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17668AI\"></sup>solemn assembly.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17669AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17669AJ\"></sup>new moons and your appointed feastsmy soul hates;they have become a burden to me;I am weary of bearing them.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>When you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17670AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17670AK\"></sup>spread out your hands,I will hide my eyes from you;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17670AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17670AL\"></sup>even though you make many prayers,I will not listen;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17670AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17670AM\"></sup>your hands are full of blood.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17671AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17671AN\"></sup>Wash yourselves; make yourselves clean;remove the evil of your deeds from before my eyes;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17671AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17671AO\"></sup>cease to do evil,",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><span class=\"indent-1-breaks\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>learn to do good;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17672AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17672AP\"></sup>seek justice,correct oppression;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17672AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17672AQ\"></sup>bring justice to the fatherless,plead the widow's cause.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“Come now, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17673AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17673AR\"></sup>let us reason together, says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>:though your sins are like scarlet,they shall be as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17673AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17673AS\"></sup>white as snow;though they are red like crimson,they shall become like wool.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17674AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17674AT\"></sup>If you are willing and obedient,you shall eat the good of the land;",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>but if you refuse and rebel,you shall be eaten by the sword;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17675AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17675AU\"></sup>for the mouth of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has spoken.”",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>How the faithful city<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17676AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17676AV\"></sup>has become a whore,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17676AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17676AW\"></sup>she who was full of justice!Righteousness lodged in her,but now murderers.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17677AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17677AX\"></sup>Your silver has become dross,your best wine mixed with water.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Your princes are rebelsand companions of thieves.Everyone <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17678AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17678AY\"></sup>loves a bribeand runs after gifts.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17678AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17678AZ\"></sup>They do not bring justice to the fatherless,and the widow's cause does not come to them.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Therefore the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17679BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17679BA\"></sup>Lord declares,the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts,the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17679BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17679BB\"></sup>Mighty One of Israel:“Ah, I will get relief from my enemies<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17679BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17679BC\"></sup>and avenge myself on my foes.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17680BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17680BD\"></sup>I will turn my hand against youand will smelt away your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17680BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17680BE\"></sup>dross as with lyeand remove all your alloy.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>And I will restore your judges <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17681BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17681BF\"></sup>as at the first,and your counselors as at the beginning.Afterward <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17681BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17681BG\"></sup>you shall be called the city of righteousness,the faithful city.”",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17682BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17682BH\"></sup>Zion shall be redeemed by justice,and those in her who repent, by righteousness.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17683BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17683BI\"></sup>But rebels and sinners shall be broken together,and those who forsake the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> shall be consumed.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17684BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17684BJ\"></sup>For they shall be ashamed of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17684BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17684BK\"></sup>the oaksthat you desired;and you shall blush for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17684BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17684BL\"></sup>the gardensthat you have chosen.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>For you shall be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17685BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17685BM\"></sup>like an oakwhose leaf withers,and like a garden without water.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>And the strong shall become <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17686BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17686BN\"></sup>tinder,and his work a spark,and both of them shall burn together,with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17686BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17686BO\"></sup>none to quench them."
		},
		"2": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">2 </span>The word that Isaiah the son of Amoz saw concerning Judah and Jerusalem.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17688A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17688A\"></sup>It shall come to pass in the latter daysthat <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17688B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17688B\"></sup>the mountain of the house of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>shall be established as the highest of the mountains,and shall be lifted up above the hills;and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17688C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17688C\"></sup>all the nations shall flow to it,",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><span class=\"indent-1-breaks\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17689D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17689D\"></sup>many peoples shall come, and say:“Come, let us go up to the mountain of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,to the house of the God of Jacob,that he may teach us his waysand that we may walk in his paths.”For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17689E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17689E\"></sup>out of Zion shall go forth the law,and the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> from Jerusalem.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>He shall judge between the nations,and shall decide disputes for many peoples;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17690F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17690F\"></sup>and they shall beat their swords into plowshares,and their spears into pruning hooks;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17690G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17690G\"></sup>nation shall not lift up sword against nation,neither shall they learn war anymore.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>O house of Jacob,come, let us walkin <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17691H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17691H\"></sup>the light of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>For you have rejected your people,the house of Jacob,because they are full of things <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17692I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17692I\"></sup>from the eastand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17692J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17692J\"></sup>of fortune-tellers <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17692K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17692K\"></sup>like the Philistines,and they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17692L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17692L\"></sup>strike hands with the children of foreigners.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Their land is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17693M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17693M\"></sup>filled with silver and gold,and there is no end to their treasures;their land is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17693N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17693N\"></sup>filled with horses,and there is no end to their chariots.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Their land is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17694O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17694O\"></sup>filled with idols;they bow down to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17694P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17694P\"></sup>the work of their hands,to what their own fingers have made.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>So man <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17695Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17695Q\"></sup>is humbled,and each one <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17695R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17695R\"></sup>is brought low—do not forgive them!",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17696S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17696S\"></sup>Enter into the rockand hide in the dust<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17696T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17696T\"></sup>from before the terror of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,and from the splendor of his majesty.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17697U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17697U\"></sup>The haughty looks of man shall be brought low,and the lofty pride of men shall be humbled,and the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> alone will be exalted in that day.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17698V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17698V\"></sup>For the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts has a dayagainst all that is proud and lofty,against all that is lifted up—and it shall be brought low;",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>against all the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17699W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17699W\"></sup>cedars of Lebanon,lofty and lifted up;and against all the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17699X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17699X\"></sup>oaks of Bashan;",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>against all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17700Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17700Y\"></sup>the lofty mountains,and against all the uplifted hills;",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>against every high tower,and against every fortified wall;",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>against all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17702Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17702Z\"></sup>the ships of Tarshish,and against all the beautiful craft.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17703AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17703AA\"></sup>And the haughtiness of man shall be humbled,and the lofty pride of men shall be brought low,and the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> alone will be exalted in that day.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17704AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17704AB\"></sup>And the idols shall utterly pass away.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17705AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17705AC\"></sup>And people shall enter the caves of the rocksand the holes of the ground,from before the terror of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,and from the splendor of his majesty,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17705AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17705AD\"></sup>when he rises to terrify the earth.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>In that day <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17706AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17706AE\"></sup>mankind will cast awaytheir idols of silver and their idols of gold,which they made for themselves to worship,to the moles and to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17706AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17706AF\"></sup>bats,",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17707AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17707AG\"></sup>to enter the caverns of the rocksand the clefts of the cliffs,from before the terror of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,and from the splendor of his majesty,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17707AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17707AH\"></sup>when he rises to terrify the earth.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17708AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17708AI\"></sup>Stop regarding man<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17708AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17708AJ\"></sup>in whose nostrils is breath,for of what account is he?"
		},
		"3": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">3 </span>For behold, the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17709A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17709A\"></sup>Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span> of hostsis taking away from Jerusalem and from Judahsupport and supply,all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17709B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17709B\"></sup>support of bread,and all support of water;",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17710C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17710C\"></sup>the mighty man and the soldier,the judge and the prophet,the diviner and the elder,",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>the captain of fiftyand the man of rank,the counselor and the skillful magicianand the expert in charms.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17712D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17712D\"></sup>And I will make boys their princes,and infants shall rule over them.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17713E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17713E\"></sup>And the people will oppress one another,every one his fellowand every one his neighbor;the youth will be insolent to the elder,and the despised to the honorable.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17714F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17714F\"></sup>a man will take hold of his brotherin the house of his father, saying:“You have a cloak;you shall be our leader,and this heap of ruinsshall be under your rule”;",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>in that day he will speak out, saying:“I will not be a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17715G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17715G\"></sup>healer;in my house there is neither bread nor cloak;you shall not make meleader of the people.”",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>For Jerusalem has stumbled,and Judah has fallen,because their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17716H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17716H\"></sup>speech and their deeds are against the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17716I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17716I\"></sup>defying his glorious presence.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>For the look on their faces bears witness against them;they proclaim their sin <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17717J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17717J\"></sup>like Sodom;they do not hide it.Woe to them!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17717K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17717K\"></sup>For they have brought evil on themselves.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17718L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17718L\"></sup>Tell the righteous that it shall be well with them,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17718M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17718M\"></sup>for they shall eat the fruit of their deeds.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17719N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17719N\"></sup>Woe to the wicked! It shall be ill with him,for what his hands have dealt out shall be done to him.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>My people—<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17720O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17720O\"></sup>infants are their oppressors,and women rule over them.O my people, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17720P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17720P\"></sup>your guides mislead youand they have swallowed up the course of your paths.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17721Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17721Q\"></sup>has taken his place to contend;he stands to judge peoples.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will enter into judgmentwith the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17722R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17722R\"></sup>elders and princes of his people:“It is you who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17722S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17722S\"></sup>have devoured the vineyard,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17722T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17722T\"></sup>the spoil of the poor is in your houses.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>What do you mean by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17723U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17723U\"></sup>crushing my people,by grinding the face of the poor?”declares the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span> of hosts.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17724V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17724V\"></sup>Because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17724W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17724W\"></sup>the daughters of Zion are haughtyand walk with outstretched necks,glancing wantonly with their eyes,mincing along as they go,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17724X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17724X\"></sup>tinkling with their feet,",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>therefore the Lord <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17725Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17725Y\"></sup>will strike with a scabthe heads of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17725Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17725Z\"></sup>the daughters of Zion,and the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will lay bare their secret parts.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>In that day the Lord will take away <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17726AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17726AA\"></sup>the finery of the anklets, the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17726AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17726AB\"></sup>headbands, and the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17726AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17726AC\"></sup>crescents;",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>the pendants, the bracelets, and the scarves;",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17728AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17728AD\"></sup>headdresses, the armlets, the sashes, the perfume boxes, and the amulets;",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>the signet rings and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17729AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17729AE\"></sup>nose rings;",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17730AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17730AF\"></sup>festal robes, the mantles, the cloaks, and the handbags;",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>the mirrors, the linen garments, the turbans, and the veils.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Instead of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17732AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17732AG\"></sup>perfume there will be rottenness;and instead of a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17732AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17732AH\"></sup>belt, a rope;and instead of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17732AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17732AI\"></sup>well-set hair, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17732AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17732AJ\"></sup>baldness;and instead of a rich robe, a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17732AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17732AK\"></sup>skirt of sackcloth;and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17732AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17732AL\"></sup>branding instead of beauty.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Your men shall fall by the swordand your mighty men in battle.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17734AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17734AM\"></sup>her gates shall lament and mourn;empty, she shall <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17734AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17734AN\"></sup>sit on the ground."
		},
		"4": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">4 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17735A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17735A\"></sup>And seven women <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17735B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17735B\"></sup>shall take hold of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17735C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17735C\"></sup>one man in that day, saying, “We will eat our own bread and wear our own clothes, only let us be called by your name; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17735D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17735D\"></sup>take away our reproach.”",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>In that day <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17736E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17736E\"></sup>the branch of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> shall be beautiful and glorious, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17736F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17736F\"></sup>the fruit of the land shall be the pride and honor of the survivors of Israel.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17737G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17737G\"></sup>And he who is left in Zion and remains in Jerusalem will be called <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17737H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17737H\"></sup>holy, everyone who has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17737I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17737I\"></sup>been recorded for life in Jerusalem,",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>when <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17738J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17738J\"></sup>the Lord shall have washed away the filth of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17738K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17738K\"></sup>the daughters of Zion and cleansed the bloodstains of Jerusalem from its midst by a spirit of judgment and by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17738L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17738L\"></sup>a spirit of burning.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Then the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will create over the whole site of Mount Zion and over her assemblies <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17739M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17739M\"></sup>a cloud by day, and smoke and the shining of a flaming fire by night; for over all the glory there will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17739N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17739N\"></sup>a canopy.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17740O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17740O\"></sup>There will be a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17740P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17740P\"></sup>booth for shade by day from the heat, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17740Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17740Q\"></sup>for a refuge and a shelter from the storm and rain."
		},
		"5": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">5 </span>Let me sing for my belovedmy love song concerning his vineyard:My beloved had <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17741A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17741A\"></sup>a vineyardon a very fertile hill.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>He dug it and cleared it of stones,and planted it with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17742B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17742B\"></sup>choice vines;he built a watchtower in the midst of it,and hewed out a wine vat in it;and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17742C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17742C\"></sup>he looked for it to yield grapes,but it yielded wild grapes.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And now, O inhabitants of Jerusalemand men of Judah,judge between me and my vineyard.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17744D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17744D\"></sup>What more was there to do for my vineyard,that I have not done in it?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17744E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17744E\"></sup>When I looked for it to yield grapes,why did it yield wild grapes?",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>And now I will tell youwhat I will do to my vineyard.I will remove <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17745F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17745F\"></sup>its hedge,and it shall be devoured;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17745G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17745G\"></sup>I will break down its wall,and it shall be trampled down.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>I will make it a waste;it shall not be pruned or hoed,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17746H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17746H\"></sup>briers and thorns shall grow up;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17746I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17746I\"></sup>I will also command the cloudsthat they rain no rain upon it.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17747J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17747J\"></sup>For the vineyard of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hostsis the house of Israel,and the men of Judahare his pleasant planting;and he looked for justice,but behold, bloodshed;for righteousness,but behold, an outcry!",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Woe to those who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17748K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17748K\"></sup>join house to house,who add field to field,until there is no more room,and you are made to dwell alonein the midst of the land.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts has sworn in my hearing:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17749L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17749L\"></sup>“Surely many houses shall be desolate,large and beautiful houses, without inhabitant.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17750M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17750M\"></sup>For ten acres of vineyard shall yield but one bath,and a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17750N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17750N\"></sup>homer of seed shall yield but an ephah.”",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Woe to those who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17751O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17751O\"></sup>rise early in the morning,that they may run after strong drink,who tarry late into the eveningas wine inflames them!",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17752P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17752P\"></sup>They have lyre and harp,tambourine and flute and wine at their feasts,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17752Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17752Q\"></sup>but they do not regard the deeds of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,or see the work of his hands.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Therefore my people go into exile<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17753R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17753R\"></sup>for lack of knowledge;their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17753S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17753S\"></sup>honored men go hungry,and their multitude is parched with thirst.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Therefore Sheol has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17754T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17754T\"></sup>enlarged its appetiteand opened <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17754U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17754U\"></sup>its mouth beyond measure,and the nobility of Jerusalem and her multitude will go down,her revelers and he who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17754V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17754V\"></sup>exults in her.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17755W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17755W\"></sup>Man is humbled, and each one is brought low,and the eyes of the haughty are brought low.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17756X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17756X\"></sup>But the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts is exalted in justice,and the Holy God shows himself holy in righteousness.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Then shall the lambs graze <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17757Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17757Y\"></sup>as in their pasture,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17757Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17757Z\"></sup>nomads shall eat among the ruins of the rich.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Woe to those who draw iniquity with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17758AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17758AA\"></sup>cords of falsehood,who draw sin as with cart ropes,",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>who say: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17759AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17759AB\"></sup>“Let him be quick,let him speed his workthat we may see it;let the counsel of the Holy One of Israel draw near,and let it come, that we may know it!”",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Woe to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17760AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17760AC\"></sup>those who call evil goodand good evil,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17760AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17760AD\"></sup>who put darkness for lightand light for darkness,who put bitter for sweetand sweet for bitter!",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Woe to those who are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17761AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17761AE\"></sup>wise in their own eyes,and shrewd in their own sight!",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Woe to those who are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17762AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17762AF\"></sup>heroes at drinking wine,and valiant men in mixing strong drink,",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17763AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17763AG\"></sup>acquit the guilty for a bribe,and deprive the innocent of his right!",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Therefore, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17764AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17764AH\"></sup>as the tongue of fire devours the stubble,and as dry grass sinks down in the flame,so <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17764AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17764AI\"></sup>their root will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17764AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17764AJ\"></sup>as rottenness,and their blossom go up like dust;for they have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17764AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17764AK\"></sup>rejected the law of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts,and have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17764AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17764AL\"></sup>despised the word of the Holy One of Israel.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Therefore <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17765AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17765AM\"></sup>the anger of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> was kindled against his people,and he stretched out his hand against them and struck them,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17765AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17765AN\"></sup>the mountains quaked;and their corpses were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17765AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17765AO\"></sup>as refusein the midst of the streets.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17765AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17765AP\"></sup>For all this his anger has not turned away,and his hand is stretched out still.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>He will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17766AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17766AQ\"></sup>raise a signal for nations far away,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17766AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17766AR\"></sup>whistle for them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17766AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17766AS\"></sup>from the ends of the earth;and behold, quickly, speedily they come!",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17767AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17767AT\"></sup>None is weary, none stumbles,none slumbers or sleeps,not a waistband is loose,not a sandal strap broken;",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17768AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17768AU\"></sup>their arrows are sharp,all their bows bent,their horses' hoofs seem like flint,and their wheels <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17768AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17768AV\"></sup>like the whirlwind.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>Their roaring is like a lion,like young lions they roar;they growl and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17769AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17769AW\"></sup>seize their prey;they carry it off, and none can rescue.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>They will growl over it on that day,like the growling of the sea.And if one looks to the land,behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17770AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17770AX\"></sup>darkness and distress;and the light is darkened by its clouds."
		},
		"6": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">6 </span>In the year that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17771A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17771A\"></sup>King Uzziah died I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17771B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17771B\"></sup>saw the Lord sitting upon a throne, high and lifted up; and the train of his robe filled the temple.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Above him stood the seraphim. Each had <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17772C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17772C\"></sup>six wings: with two he covered his face, and with two he covered his feet, and with two he flew.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And one called to another and said:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17773D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17773D\"></sup>“Holy, holy, holy is the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17773E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17773E\"></sup>the whole earth is full of his glory!”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17774F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17774F\"></sup>the foundations of the thresholds shook at the voice of him who called, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17774G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17774G\"></sup>the house was filled with smoke.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>And I said: “Woe is me! <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17775H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17775H\"></sup>For I am lost; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17775I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17775I\"></sup>for I am a man of unclean lips, and I dwell in the midst of a people of unclean lips; for my eyes have seen the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17775J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17775J\"></sup>King, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts!”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Then one of the seraphim flew to me, having in his hand a burning coal that he had taken with tongs from the altar.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>And he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17777K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17777K\"></sup>touched my mouth and said: “Behold, this has touched your lips; your guilt is taken away, and your sin atoned for.”",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>And I heard the voice of the Lord saying, “Whom shall I send, and who will go for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17778L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17778L\"></sup>us?” Then I said, “Here I am! Send me.”",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>And he said, “Go, and say to this people:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17779M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17779M\"></sup>“‘Keep on hearing, but do not understand;keep on seeing, but do not perceive.’",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17780N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17780N\"></sup>Make the heart of this people <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17780O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17780O\"></sup>dull,and their ears heavy,and blind their eyes;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17780P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17780P\"></sup>lest they see with their eyes,and hear with their ears,and understand with their hearts,and turn and be healed.”",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Then I said, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17781Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17781Q\"></sup>“How long, O Lord?”And he said:“Until <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17781R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17781R\"></sup>cities lie wastewithout inhabitant,and houses without people,and the land is a desolate waste,",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>and the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> removes people far away,and the forsaken places are many in the midst of the land.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17783S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17783S\"></sup>And though a tenth remain in it,it will be burned again,like a terebinth or an oak,whose stump <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17783T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17783T\"></sup>remainswhen it is felled.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17783U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17783U\"></sup>The holy seed is its stump."
		},
		"7": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">7 </span>In the days of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17784A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17784A\"></sup>Ahaz the son of Jotham, son of Uzziah, king of Judah, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17784B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17784B\"></sup>Rezin the king of Syria and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17784C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17784C\"></sup>Pekah the son of Remaliah the king of Israel came up to Jerusalem to wage war against it, but could not yet mount an attack against it.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>When the house of David was told, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17785D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17785D\"></sup>“Syria is in league with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17785E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17785E\"></sup>Ephraim,” the heart of Ahaz and the heart of his people shook as the trees of the forest shake before the wind.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to Isaiah, “Go out to meet Ahaz, you and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17786F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17786F\"></sup>Shear-jashub your son, at the end of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17786G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17786G\"></sup>the conduit of the upper pool on the highway to the Washer's Field.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>And say to him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17787H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17787H\"></sup>‘Be careful, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17787I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17787I\"></sup>be quiet, do not fear, and do not let your heart be faint because of these two <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17787J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17787J\"></sup>smoldering stumps of firebrands, at the fierce anger of Rezin and Syria and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17787K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17787K\"></sup>the son of Remaliah.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Because Syria, with Ephraim and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17788L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17788L\"></sup>the son of Remaliah, has devised evil against you, saying,",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“Let us go up against Judah and terrify it, and let us conquer it for ourselves, and set up the son of Tabeel as king in the midst of it,”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17790M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17790M\"></sup>“‘It shall not stand,and it shall not come to pass.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>For the head of Syria is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17791N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17791N\"></sup>Damascus,and the head of Damascus is Rezin.And within sixty-five yearsEphraim will be shattered from being a people.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>And the head of Ephraim is Samaria,and the head of Samaria is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17792O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17792O\"></sup>the son of Remaliah.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17792P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17792P\"></sup>If you are not firm in faith,you will not be firm at all.’”",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Again the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> spoke to Ahaz:",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“Ask <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17794Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17794Q\"></sup>a sign of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God; let it be deep as Sheol or high as heaven.”",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>But Ahaz said, “I will not ask, and I will not put the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> to the test.”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>And he said, “Hear then, O house of David! Is it too little for you to weary men, that you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17796R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17796R\"></sup>weary my God also?",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Therefore the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17797S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17797S\"></sup>Lord himself will give you a sign. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17797T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17797T\"></sup>Behold, the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17797U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17797U\"></sup>virgin shall conceive and bear a son, and shall call his name <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17797V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17797V\"></sup>Immanuel.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>He shall eat <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17798W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17798W\"></sup>curds and honey when he knows how to refuse the evil and choose the good.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17799X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17799X\"></sup>For before the boy knows how to refuse the evil and choose the good, the land whose two kings you dread will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17799Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17799Y\"></sup>deserted.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17800Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17800Z\"></sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will bring upon you and upon your people and upon your father's house such days as have not come since the day that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17800AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17800AA\"></sup>Ephraim departed from Judah—the king of Assyria!”",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>In that day the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17801AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17801AB\"></sup>whistle for the fly that is at the end of the streams of Egypt, and for the bee that is in the land of Assyria.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>And they will all come and settle in the steep ravines, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17802AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17802AC\"></sup>in the clefts of the rocks, and on all the thornbushes, and on all the pastures.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>In that day <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17803AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17803AD\"></sup>the Lord will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17803AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17803AE\"></sup>shave with a razor that is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17803AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17803AF\"></sup>hired beyond <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17803AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17803AG\"></sup>the River—with the king of Assyria—the head and the hair of the feet, and it will sweep away the beard also.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17804AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17804AH\"></sup>In that day a man will keep alive a young cow and two sheep,",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>and because of the abundance of milk that they give, he will eat curds, for everyone who is left in the land will eat <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17805AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17805AI\"></sup>curds and honey.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>In that day every place where there used to be a thousand vines, worth a thousand shekels of silver, will become <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17806AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17806AJ\"></sup>briers and thorns.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17807AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17807AK\"></sup>With bow and arrows a man will come there, for all the land will be briers and thorns.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17808AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17808AL\"></sup>And as for all the hills that used to be hoed with a hoe, you will not come there for fear <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17808AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17808AM\"></sup>of briers and thorns, but they will become a place where cattle are let loose and where sheep tread."
		},
		"8": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">8 </span>Then the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to me, “Take a large tablet <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17809A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17809A\"></sup>and write on it in common characters, ‘Belonging to Maher-shalal-hash-baz.’",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17810B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17810B\"></sup>I will get reliable witnesses, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17810C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17810C\"></sup>Uriah the priest and Zechariah the son of Jeberechiah, to attest for me.”",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And I went to the prophetess, and she conceived and bore a son. Then the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to me, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17811D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17811D\"></sup>“Call his name Maher-shalal-hash-baz;",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17812E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17812E\"></sup>for before the boy knows how to cry ‘My father’ or ‘My mother,’ the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17812F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17812F\"></sup>wealth of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17812G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17812G\"></sup>Damascus and the spoil of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17812H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17812H\"></sup>Samaria will be carried away before the king of Assyria.”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> spoke to me again:",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“Because this people has refused the waters of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17814I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17814I\"></sup>Shiloah that flow gently, and rejoice over <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17814J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17814J\"></sup>Rezin and the son of Remaliah,",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>therefore, behold, the Lord is bringing up against them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17815K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17815K\"></sup>the waters of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17815L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17815L\"></sup>the River, mighty and many, the king of Assyria and all his glory. And it <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17815M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17815M\"></sup>will rise over all its channels and go over all its banks,",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>and it will sweep on into Judah, it will overflow and pass on, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17816N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17816N\"></sup>reaching even to the neck, and its <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17816O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17816O\"></sup>outspread wings will fill the breadth of your land, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17816P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17816P\"></sup>O Immanuel.”",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Be broken, you peoples, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17817Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17817Q\"></sup>be shattered;give ear, all you far countries;strap on your armor and be shattered;strap on your armor and be shattered.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Take counsel together, but it will come to nothing;speak a word, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17818R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17818R\"></sup>but it will not stand,for God <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17818S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17818S\"></sup>is with us.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>For the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> spoke thus to me with his strong hand upon me, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17819T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17819T\"></sup>warned me not to walk in the way of this people, saying:",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“Do not call <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17820U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17820U\"></sup>conspiracy all that this people calls conspiracy, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17820V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17820V\"></sup>do not fear what they fear, nor be in dread.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>But the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17821W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17821W\"></sup>him you shall honor as holy. Let him be your fear, and let him be your dread.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>And he will become a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17822X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17822X\"></sup>sanctuary and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17822Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17822Y\"></sup>a stone of offense and a rock of stumbling to both houses of Israel, a trap and a snare to the inhabitants of Jerusalem.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>And many <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17823Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17823Z\"></sup>shall stumble on it. They shall fall and be broken; they shall be snared and taken.”",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Bind up <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17824AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17824AA\"></sup>the testimony; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17824AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17824AB\"></sup>seal the teaching among my disciples.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17825AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17825AC\"></sup>wait for the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, who is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17825AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17825AD\"></sup>hiding his face from the house of Jacob, and I will hope in him.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17826AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17826AE\"></sup>Behold, I and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17826AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17826AF\"></sup>the children whom the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has given me are signs and portents in Israel from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, who dwells on Mount Zion.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>And when they say to you, “Inquire of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17827AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17827AG\"></sup>mediums and the necromancers who chirp and mutter,” should not a people inquire of their God? Should they inquire of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17827AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17827AH\"></sup>the dead on behalf of the living?",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17828AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17828AI\"></sup>To the teaching and to the testimony! If they will not speak according to this word, it is because they have no <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17828AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17828AJ\"></sup>dawn.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>They will pass through the land, greatly distressed and hungry. And when they are hungry, they will be enraged and will speak contemptuously against their king and their God, and turn their faces upward.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17830AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17830AK\"></sup>And they will look to the earth, but behold, distress and darkness, the gloom of anguish. And they will be thrust into <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17830AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17830AL\"></sup>thick darkness."
		},
		"9": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">9 </span> But there will be no <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17831A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17831A\"></sup>gloom for her who was in anguish. In the former time he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17831B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17831B\"></sup>brought into contempt the land of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17831C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17831C\"></sup>Zebulun and the land of Naphtali, but in the latter time he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17831D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17831D\"></sup>has made glorious the way of the sea, the land beyond the Jordan, Galilee of the nations.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17832E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17832E\"></sup>The people <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17832F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17832F\"></sup>who walked in darknesshave seen a great light;those who dwelt in a land of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17832G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17832G\"></sup>deep darkness,on them has light shone.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17833H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17833H\"></sup>You have multiplied the nation;you have increased its joy;they rejoice before youas with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17833I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17833I\"></sup>joy at the harvest,as they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17833J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17833J\"></sup>are glad <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17833K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17833K\"></sup>when they divide the spoil.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17834L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17834L\"></sup>For the yoke of his burden,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17834M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17834M\"></sup>and the staff for his shoulder,the rod of his oppressor,you have broken as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17834N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17834N\"></sup>on the day of Midian.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17835O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17835O\"></sup>For every boot of the tramping warrior in battle tumultand every garment rolled in bloodwill be burned as fuel for the fire.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17836P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17836P\"></sup>For to us a child is born,to us <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17836Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17836Q\"></sup>a son is given;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17836R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17836R\"></sup>and the government shall be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17836S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17836S\"></sup>upon his shoulder,and his name shall be calledWonderful <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17836T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17836T\"></sup>Counselor, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17836U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17836U\"></sup>Mighty God,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17836V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17836V\"></sup>Everlasting <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17836W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17836W\"></sup>Father, Prince of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17836X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17836X\"></sup>Peace.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Of the increase of his government and of peace<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17837Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17837Y\"></sup>there will be no end,on the throne of David and over his kingdom,to establish it and to uphold it<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17837Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17837Z\"></sup>with justice and with righteousnessfrom this time forth and forevermore.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17837AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17837AA\"></sup>The zeal of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts will do this.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>The Lord has sent a word against Jacob,and it will fall on Israel;",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>and all the people will know,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17839AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17839AB\"></sup>Ephraim and the inhabitants of Samaria,who say in pride and in arrogance of heart:",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“The bricks have fallen,but we will build with dressed stones;the sycamores have been cut down,but we will put cedars in their place.”",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>But the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> raises the adversaries of Rezin against him,and stirs up his enemies.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17842AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17842AC\"></sup>The Syrians on the east and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17842AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17842AD\"></sup>the Philistines on the westdevour Israel with open mouth.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17842AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17842AE\"></sup>For all this his anger has not turned away,and his hand is stretched out still.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>The people <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17843AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17843AF\"></sup>did not turn to him who struck them,nor inquire of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>So the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> cut off from Israel <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17844AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17844AG\"></sup>head and tail,palm branch and reed in one day—",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17845AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17845AH\"></sup>the elder and honored man is the head,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17845AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17845AI\"></sup>the prophet who teaches lies is the tail;",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>for those who guide this people have been leading them astray,and those who are guided by them are swallowed up.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Therefore the Lord does not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17847AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17847AJ\"></sup>rejoice over their young men,and has no compassion on their fatherless and widows;for everyone is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17847AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17847AK\"></sup>godless and an evildoer,and every mouth speaks <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17847AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17847AL\"></sup>folly.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17847AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17847AM\"></sup>For all this his anger has not turned away,and his hand is stretched out still.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>For wickedness burns like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17848AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17848AN\"></sup>a fire;it consumes briers and thorns;it kindles the thickets of the forest,and they roll upward in a column of smoke.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Through the wrath of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hoststhe land is scorched,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17849AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17849AO\"></sup>the people are like fuel for the fire;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17849AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17849AP\"></sup>no one spares another.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17850AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17850AQ\"></sup>They slice meat on the right, but are still hungry,and they devour on the left, but are not satisfied;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17850AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17850AR\"></sup>each devours the flesh of his own arm,",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Manasseh devours Ephraim, and Ephraim devours Manasseh;together they are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17851AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17851AS\"></sup>against Judah.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17851AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17851AT\"></sup>For all this his anger has not turned away,and his hand is stretched out still."
		},
		"10": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">10 </span>Woe to those who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17852A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17852A\"></sup>decree iniquitous decrees,and the writers who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17852B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17852B\"></sup>keep writing oppression,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>to turn aside the needy from justiceand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17853C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17853C\"></sup>to rob the poor of my people of their right,that widows may be their spoil,and that they may make the fatherless their prey!",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>What will you do on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17854D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17854D\"></sup>the day of punishment,in the ruin that will come <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17854E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17854E\"></sup>from afar?To whom will you flee for help,and where will you leave your wealth?",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Nothing remains but to crouch among the prisonersor fall among the slain.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17855F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17855F\"></sup>For all this his anger has not turned away,and his hand is stretched out still.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Woe to Assyria, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17856G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17856G\"></sup>the rod of my anger;the staff in their hands is my fury!",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Against a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17857H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17857H\"></sup>godless nation I send him,and against the people of my wrath I command him,to take <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17857I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17857I\"></sup>spoil and seize plunder,and to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17857J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17857J\"></sup>tread them down like the mire of the streets.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>But he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17858K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17858K\"></sup>does not so intend,and his heart does not so think;but it is in his heart to destroy,and to cut off nations not a few;",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>for he says:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17859L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17859L\"></sup>“Are not my commanders all kings?",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17860M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17860M\"></sup>Is not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17860N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17860N\"></sup>Calno like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17860O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17860O\"></sup>Carchemish?Is not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17860P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17860P\"></sup>Hamath like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17860Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17860Q\"></sup>Arpad?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17860R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17860R\"></sup>Is not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17860S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17860S\"></sup>Samaria like Damascus?",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>As my hand has reached to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17861T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17861T\"></sup>the kingdoms of the idols,whose carved images were greater than those of Jerusalem and Samaria,",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>shall I not do to Jerusalem and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17862U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17862U\"></sup>her idols<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17862V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17862V\"></sup>as I have done to Samaria and her images?”",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17863W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17863W\"></sup>When the Lord has finished all his work on Mount Zion and on Jerusalem, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17863X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17863X\"></sup>he will punish the speech of the arrogant heart of the king of Assyria and the boastful look in his eyes.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17864Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17864Y\"></sup>For he says:“By the strength of my hand I have done it,and by my wisdom, for I have understanding;I remove the boundaries of peoples,and plunder their treasures;like a bull I bring down those who sit on thrones.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>My hand has found like a nestthe wealth of the peoples;and as one gathers eggs that have been forsaken,so I have gathered all the earth;and there was none that moved a wingor opened the mouth or chirped.”",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Shall <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17866Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17866Z\"></sup>the axe boast over him who hews with it,or the saw magnify itself against him who wields it?As if a rod should wield him who lifts it,or as if a staff should lift him who is not wood!",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Therefore the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span> of hostswill send wasting sickness among his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17867AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17867AA\"></sup>stout warriors,and under his glory <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17867AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17867AB\"></sup>a burning will be kindled,like the burning of fire.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17868AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17868AC\"></sup>The light of Israel will become a fire,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17868AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17868AD\"></sup>his Holy One a flame,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17868AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17868AE\"></sup>it will burn and devourhis thorns and briers <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17868AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17868AF\"></sup>in one day.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>The glory of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17869AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17869AG\"></sup>his forest and of his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17869AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17869AH\"></sup>fruitful landthe <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will destroy, both soul and body,and it will be as when a sick man wastes away.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>The remnant of the trees of his forest will be so fewthat a child can write them down.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17871AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17871AI\"></sup>In that day <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17871AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17871AJ\"></sup>the remnant of Israel and the survivors of the house of Jacob will no more <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17871AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17871AK\"></sup>lean on him who struck them, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17871AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17871AL\"></sup>will lean on the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, the Holy One of Israel, in truth.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>A remnant will return, the remnant of Jacob, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17872AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17872AM\"></sup>to the mighty God.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17873AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17873AN\"></sup>For though your people Israel be as the sand of the sea, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17873AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17873AO\"></sup>only a remnant of them will return. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17873AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17873AP\"></sup>Destruction is decreed, overflowing with righteousness.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>For the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span> of hosts will make a full end, as decreed, in the midst of all the earth.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Therefore thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span> of hosts: “O my people, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17875AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17875AQ\"></sup>who dwell in Zion, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17875AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17875AR\"></sup>be not afraid of the Assyrians when they strike with the rod and lift up their staff against you as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17875AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17875AS\"></sup>the Egyptians did.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17876AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17876AT\"></sup>in a very little while my fury will come to an end, and my anger will be directed to their destruction.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17877AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17877AU\"></sup>the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts will wield against them a whip, as when he struck <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17877AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17877AV\"></sup>Midian <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17877AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17877AW\"></sup>at the rock of Oreb. And his staff will be over the sea, and he will lift it <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17877AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17877AX\"></sup>as he did in Egypt.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>And in that day <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17878AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17878AY\"></sup>his burden will depart from your shoulder, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17878AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17878AZ\"></sup>his yoke from your neck; and the yoke will be broken because of the fat.”",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>He has come to Aiath;he has passed through <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17879BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17879BA\"></sup>Migron;at Michmash he stores <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17879BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17879BB\"></sup>his baggage;",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>they have crossed over <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17880BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17880BC\"></sup>the pass;at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17880BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17880BD\"></sup>Geba they lodge for the night;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17880BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17880BE\"></sup>Ramah trembles;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17880BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17880BF\"></sup>Gibeah of Saul has fled.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>Cry aloud, O daughter of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17881BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17881BG\"></sup>Gallim!Give attention, O Laishah!O poor <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17881BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17881BH\"></sup>Anathoth!",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>Madmenah is in flight;the inhabitants of Gebim flee for safety.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>This very day he will halt at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17883BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17883BI\"></sup>Nob;he will shake his fistat the mount of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17883BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17883BJ\"></sup>the daughter of Zion,the hill of Jerusalem.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>Behold, the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span> of hosts<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17884BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17884BK\"></sup>will lop <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17884BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17884BL\"></sup>the boughs with terrifying power;the great in height will be hewn down,and the lofty will be brought low.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>He will cut down <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17885BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17885BM\"></sup>the thickets of the forest with an axe,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17885BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17885BN\"></sup>Lebanon will fall by the Majestic One."
		},
		"11": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">11 </span>There shall come forth a shoot from the stump of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17886A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17886A\"></sup>Jesse,and a branch from his roots shall bear fruit.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17887B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17887B\"></sup>the Spirit of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> shall rest upon him,the Spirit of wisdom and understanding,the Spirit of counsel and might,the Spirit of knowledge and the fear of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And his delight shall be in the fear of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17888C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17888C\"></sup>He shall not judge by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17888D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17888D\"></sup>what his eyes see,or decide disputes by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17888E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17888E\"></sup>what his ears hear,",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17889F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17889F\"></sup>with righteousness he shall judge the poor,and decide with equity for the meek of the earth;and he shall <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17889G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17889G\"></sup>strike the earth with the rod of his mouth,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17889H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17889H\"></sup>with the breath of his lips <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17889I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17889I\"></sup>he shall kill the wicked.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Righteousness shall be the belt of his waist,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17890J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17890J\"></sup>faithfulness the belt of his loins.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17891K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17891K\"></sup>The wolf shall dwell with the lamb,and the leopard shall lie down with the young goat,and the calf and the lion and the fattened calf together;and a little child shall lead them.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>The cow and the bear shall graze;their young shall lie down together;and the lion shall eat straw like the ox.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>The nursing child shall play over the hole of the cobra,and the weaned child shall put his hand on the adder's den.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17894L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17894L\"></sup>They shall not hurt or destroyin all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17894M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17894M\"></sup>my holy mountain;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17894N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17894N\"></sup>for the earth shall be full of the knowledge of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>as the waters cover the sea.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>In that day <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17895O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17895O\"></sup>the root of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17895P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17895P\"></sup>Jesse, who shall stand as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17895Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17895Q\"></sup>a signal for the peoples—of him shall the nations inquire, and his resting place shall be glorious.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17896R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17896R\"></sup>In that day the Lord will extend his hand yet a second time to recover the remnant that remains of his people, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17896S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17896S\"></sup>from Assyria, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17896T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17896T\"></sup>from Egypt, from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17896U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17896U\"></sup>Pathros, from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17896V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17896V\"></sup>Cush, from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17896W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17896W\"></sup>Elam, from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17896X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17896X\"></sup>Shinar, from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17896Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17896Y\"></sup>Hamath, and from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17896Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17896Z\"></sup>the coastlands of the sea.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>He will raise <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17897AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17897AA\"></sup>a signal for the nationsand will assemble <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17897AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17897AB\"></sup>the banished of Israel,and gather the dispersed of Judahfrom the four corners of the earth.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17898AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17898AC\"></sup>The jealousy of Ephraim shall depart,and those who harass Judah shall be cut off;Ephraim shall not be jealous of Judah,and Judah shall not harass Ephraim.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17899AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17899AD\"></sup>But they shall swoop down on the shoulder of the Philistines in the west,and together they shall plunder <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17899AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17899AE\"></sup>the people of the east.They shall put out their hand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17899AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17899AF\"></sup>against <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17899AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17899AG\"></sup>Edom and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17899AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17899AH\"></sup>Moab,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17899AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17899AI\"></sup>the Ammonites shall obey them.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>And the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will utterly destroy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17900AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17900AJ\"></sup>the tongue of the Sea of Egypt,and will wave his hand over <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17900AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17900AK\"></sup>the Riverwith his scorching breath,and strike it into seven channels,and he will lead people across in sandals.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>And there will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17901AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17901AL\"></sup>a highway from Assyriafor the remnant that remains of his people,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17901AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17901AM\"></sup>as there was for Israelwhen they came up from the land of Egypt."
		},
		"12": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">12 </span>You will say <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17902A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17902A\"></sup>in that day:“I will give thanks to you, O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,for though you were angry with me,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17902B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17902B\"></sup>your anger turned away,that you might comfort me.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Behold, God is my salvation;I will trust, and will not be afraid;for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17903C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17903C\"></sup>the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span> is my strength and my song,and he has become my salvation.”",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17904D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17904D\"></sup>With joy you will draw water from the wells of salvation.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17905E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17905E\"></sup>And you will say in that day:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17905F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17905F\"></sup>“Give thanks to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,call upon his name,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17905G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17905G\"></sup>make known his deeds among the peoples,proclaim <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17905H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17905H\"></sup>that his name is exalted.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17906I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17906I\"></sup>“Sing praises to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, for he has done gloriously;let this be made known in all the earth.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Shout, and sing for joy, O inhabitant of Zion,for great <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17907J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17907J\"></sup>in your midst is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17907K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17907K\"></sup>the Holy One of Israel.”"
		},
		"13": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">13 </span>The oracle concerning <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17908A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17908A\"></sup>Babylon which <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17908B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17908B\"></sup>Isaiah the son of Amoz saw.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>On a bare hill <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17909C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17909C\"></sup>raise a signal;cry aloud to them;wave the hand for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17909D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17909D\"></sup>them to enterthe gates of the nobles.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>I myself have commanded my consecrated ones,and have summoned my mighty men to execute my anger,my proudly exulting ones.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>The sound <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17911E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17911E\"></sup>of a tumult is on the mountainsas of a great multitude!The sound of an uproar of kingdoms,of nations gathering together!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17911F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17911F\"></sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts is musteringa host for battle.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17912G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17912G\"></sup>They come from a distant land,from the end of the heavens,the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> and the weapons of his indignation,to destroy the whole land.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17913H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17913H\"></sup>Wail, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17913I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17913I\"></sup>the day of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is near;as destruction from the Almighty it will come!",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Therefore all hands will be feeble,and every human heart <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17914J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17914J\"></sup>will melt.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>They will be dismayed:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17915K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17915K\"></sup>pangs and agony will seize them;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17915L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17915L\"></sup>they will be in anguish like a woman in labor.They will look aghast at one another;their faces will be aflame.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17916M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17916M\"></sup>the day of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> comes,cruel, with wrath and fierce anger,to make the land a desolationand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17916N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17916N\"></sup>to destroy its sinners from it.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17917O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17917O\"></sup>For the stars of the heavens and their constellationswill not give their light;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17917P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17917P\"></sup>the sun will be dark at its rising,and the moon will not shed its light.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>I will punish <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17918Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17918Q\"></sup>the world for its evil,and the wicked for their iniquity;I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17918R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17918R\"></sup>put an end to the pomp of the arrogant,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17918S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17918S\"></sup>and lay low the pompous pride of the ruthless.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>I will make <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17919T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17919T\"></sup>people more rare than fine gold,and mankind than the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17919U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17919U\"></sup>gold of Ophir.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Therefore <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17920V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17920V\"></sup>I will make the heavens tremble,and the earth will be shaken out of its place,at the wrath of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hostsin the day of his fierce anger.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>And like a hunted gazelle,or like sheep with none to gather them,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17921W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17921W\"></sup>each will turn to his own people,and each will flee to his own land.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Whoever is found will be thrust through,and whoever is caught will fall by the sword.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17923X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17923X\"></sup>Their infants will be dashed in piecesbefore their eyes;their houses will be plunderedand their wives ravished.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17924Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17924Y\"></sup>I am stirring up the Medes against them,who have no regard for silverand do not delight in gold.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17925Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17925Z\"></sup>Their bows will slaughter the young men;they will have no mercy on the fruit of the womb;their eyes will not pity children.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>And Babylon, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17926AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17926AA\"></sup>the glory of kingdoms,the splendor and pomp of the Chaldeans,will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17926AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17926AB\"></sup>like Sodom and Gomorrahwhen God overthrew them.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17927AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17927AC\"></sup>It will never be inhabitedor lived in for all generations;no <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17927AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17927AD\"></sup>Arab will pitch his tent there;no <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17927AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17927AE\"></sup>shepherds will make their flocks lie down there.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17928AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17928AF\"></sup>wild animals will lie down there,and their houses will be full of howling creatures;there <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17928AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17928AG\"></sup>ostriches will dwell,and there wild goats will dance.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Hyenas will cry in its towers,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17929AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17929AH\"></sup>jackals in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17929AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17929AI\"></sup>the pleasant palaces;its time is close at handand its days will not be prolonged."
		},
		"14": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">14 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17930A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17930A\"></sup>For the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will have compassion on Jacob and will again choose Israel, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17930B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17930B\"></sup>will set them in their own land, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17930C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17930C\"></sup>sojourners will join them and will attach themselves to the house of Jacob.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17931D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17931D\"></sup>the peoples will take them and bring them to their place, and the house of Israel will possess them in the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>'s land <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17931E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17931E\"></sup>as male and female slaves. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17931F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17931F\"></sup>They will take captive those who were their captors, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17931G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17931G\"></sup>and rule over those who oppressed them.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>When the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has given you rest from your pain and turmoil and the hard service with which you were made to serve,",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>you will take up this <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17933H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17933H\"></sup>taunt against the king of Babylon:“How the oppressor has ceased,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17933I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17933I\"></sup>the insolent fury ceased!",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has broken the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17934J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17934J\"></sup>staff of the wicked,the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17934K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17934K\"></sup>scepter of rulers,",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17935L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17935L\"></sup>that struck the peoples in wrathwith unceasing blows,that ruled the nations in angerwith unrelenting persecution.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>The whole earth is at rest and quiet;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17936M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17936M\"></sup>they break forth into singing.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17937N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17937N\"></sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17937O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17937O\"></sup>The cypresses rejoice at you,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17937P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17937P\"></sup>the cedars of Lebanon, saying,‘Since you were laid low,no woodcutter comes up against us.’",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Sheol beneath is stirred upto meet you when you come;it rouses the shades to greet you,all who were leaders of the earth;it raises from their thronesall who were kings of the nations.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17939Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17939Q\"></sup>All of them will answerand say to you:‘You too have become as weak as we!You have become like us!’",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Your pomp is brought down to Sheol,the sound of your harps;maggots are laid as a bed beneath you,and worms are your covers.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“How <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17941R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17941R\"></sup>you are fallen from heaven,O Day Star, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17941S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17941S\"></sup>son of Dawn!How you are cut down to the ground,you who laid the nations low!",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>You said in your heart,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17942T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17942T\"></sup>‘I will ascend to heaven;above the stars of God<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17942U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17942U\"></sup>I will set my throne on high;I will sit on the mount of assemblyin the far reaches of the north;",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>I will ascend above the heights of the clouds;I will make myself like the Most High.’",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17944V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17944V\"></sup>But you are brought down to Sheol,to the far reaches of the pit.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Those who see you will stare at youand ponder over you:‘Is this <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17945W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17945W\"></sup>the man who made the earth tremble,who shook kingdoms,",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>who made the world like a desertand overthrew its cities,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17946X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17946X\"></sup>who did not let his prisoners go home?’",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>All the kings of the nations lie in glory,each in his own tomb;",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>but you are cast out, away from your grave,like a loathed branch,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17948Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17948Y\"></sup>clothed with the slain, those pierced by the sword,who go down to the stones of the pit,like a dead body trampled underfoot.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>You will not be joined with them in burial,because you have destroyed your land,you have slain your people.“May <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17949Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17949Z\"></sup>the offspring of evildoersnevermore be named!",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Prepare slaughter for his sons<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17950AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17950AA\"></sup>because of the guilt of their fathers,lest they rise and possess the earth,and fill the face of the world with cities.”",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>“I will rise up against them,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, “and will cut off from Babylon name and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17951AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17951AB\"></sup>remnant, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17951AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17951AC\"></sup>descendants and posterity,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>“And I will make it a possession of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17952AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17952AD\"></sup>hedgehog, and pools of water, and I will sweep it with the broom of destruction,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts has sworn:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17953AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17953AE\"></sup>“As I have planned,so shall it be,and as I have purposed,so shall it stand,",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17954AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17954AF\"></sup>I will break the Assyrian in my land,and on my mountains trample him underfoot;and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17954AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17954AG\"></sup>his yoke shall depart from them,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17954AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17954AH\"></sup>his burden from their shoulder.”",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>This is the purpose that is purposedconcerning the whole earth,and this is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17955AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17955AI\"></sup>the hand that is stretched outover all the nations.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17956AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17956AJ\"></sup>For the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts has purposed,and who will annul it?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17956AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17956AK\"></sup>His hand is stretched out,and who will turn it back?",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>In the year that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17957AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17957AL\"></sup>King Ahaz died came this <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17957AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17957AM\"></sup>oracle:",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>Rejoice not, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17958AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17958AN\"></sup>O Philistia, all of you,that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17958AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17958AO\"></sup>the rod that struck you is broken,for from the serpent's root will come forth an adder,and its fruit will be a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17958AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17958AP\"></sup>flying fiery serpent.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>And the firstborn of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17959AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17959AQ\"></sup>the poor will graze,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17959AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17959AR\"></sup>the needy lie down in safety;but I will kill your root with famine,and your remnant it will slay.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17960AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17960AS\"></sup>Wail, O <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17960AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17960AT\"></sup>gate; cry out, O city;melt in fear, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17960AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17960AU\"></sup>O Philistia, all of you!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17960AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17960AV\"></sup>For smoke comes out of the north,and there is no straggler in his ranks.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>What will one answer the messengers of the nation?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17961AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17961AW\"></sup>“The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has founded Zion,and in her the afflicted of his people find refuge.”"
		},
		"15": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">15 </span>An <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17962A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17962A\"></sup>oracle concerning <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17962B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17962B\"></sup>Moab.Because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17962C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17962C\"></sup>Ar of Moab is laid waste in a night,Moab is undone;because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17962D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17962D\"></sup>Kir of Moab is laid waste in a night,Moab is undone.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>He has gone up to the temple, and to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17963E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17963E\"></sup>Dibon,to the high places to weep;over <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17963F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17963F\"></sup>Nebo and over <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17963G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17963G\"></sup>MedebaMoab <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17963H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17963H\"></sup>wails.On every head is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17963I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17963I\"></sup>baldness;every beard is shorn;",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>in the streets they wear sackcloth;on the housetops and in the squareseveryone wails and melts in tears.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17965J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17965J\"></sup>Heshbon and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17965K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17965K\"></sup>Elealeh cry out;their voice is heard as far as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17965L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17965L\"></sup>Jahaz;therefore the armed men of Moab cry aloud;his soul trembles.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>My heart cries out for Moab;her fugitives flee to Zoar,to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17966M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17966M\"></sup>Eglath-shelishiyah.For at the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17966N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17966N\"></sup>ascent of Luhiththey go up weeping;on the road to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17966O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17966O\"></sup>Horonaimthey raise a cry of destruction;",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>the waters of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17967P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17967P\"></sup>Nimrimare a desolation;the grass is withered, the vegetation fails,the greenery is no more.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17968Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17968Q\"></sup>Therefore the abundance they have gainedand what they have laid upthey carry awayover the Brook of the Willows.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>For a cry has gonearound the land of Moab;her wailing reaches to Eglaim;her wailing reaches to Beer-elim.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>For the waters of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17970R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17970R\"></sup>Dibon are full of blood;for I will bring upon Dibon even more,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17970S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17970S\"></sup>a lion for those of Moab who escape,for the remnant of the land."
		},
		"16": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">16 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17971A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17971A\"></sup>Send the lamb to the ruler of the land,from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17971B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17971B\"></sup>Sela, by way of the desert,to the mount of the daughter of Zion.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Like fleeing birds,like a scattered nest,so are the daughters of Moabat <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17972C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17972C\"></sup>the fords of the Arnon.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“Give counsel;grant justice;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17973D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17973D\"></sup>make your shade like nightat the height of noon;shelter the outcasts;do not reveal the fugitive;",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>let <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17974E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17974E\"></sup>the outcasts of Moabsojourn among you;be a shelter to themfrom the destroyer.When the oppressor is no more,and destruction has ceased,and he who tramples underfoot has vanished from the land,",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17975F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17975F\"></sup>then a throne will be established in steadfast love,and on it will sit in faithfulnessin the tent of Davidone who judges and seeks justiceand is swift to do righteousness.”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17976G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17976G\"></sup>We have heard of the pride of Moab—how proud he is!—<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17976H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17976H\"></sup>of his arrogance, his pride, and his insolence;in his idle boasting he is not right.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Therefore let Moab wail for Moab,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17977I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17977I\"></sup>let everyone wail.Mourn, utterly stricken,for the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17977J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17977J\"></sup>raisin cakes of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17977K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17977K\"></sup>Kir-hareseth.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>For the fields of Heshbon languish,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17978L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17978L\"></sup>the vine of Sibmah;the lords of the nationshave struck down its branches,which reached to Jazerand strayed to the desert;its shoots spread abroadand passed over the sea.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Therefore <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17979M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17979M\"></sup>I weep with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17979N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17979N\"></sup>the weeping of Jazerfor the vine of Sibmah;I drench you with my tears,O Heshbon and Elealeh;for over <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17979O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17979O\"></sup>your summer fruit and your harvestthe shout has ceased.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17980P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17980P\"></sup>And joy and gladness are taken away from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17980Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17980Q\"></sup>the fruitful field,and in the vineyards no <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17980R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17980R\"></sup>songs are sung,no cheers are raised;no <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17980S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17980S\"></sup>treader treads out wine <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17980T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17980T\"></sup>in the presses;I have put an end to the shouting.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Therefore <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17981U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17981U\"></sup>my inner parts moan like a lyre for Moab,and my inmost self for Kir-hareseth.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>And when Moab presents himself, when <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17982V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17982V\"></sup>he wearies himself on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17982W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17982W\"></sup>the high place, when he comes to his sanctuary to pray, he will not prevail.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>This is the word that the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> spoke concerning Moab <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17983X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17983X\"></sup>in the past.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>But now the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has spoken, saying, “In three years, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17984Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17984Y\"></sup>like the years of a hired worker, the glory of Moab will be brought into contempt, in spite of all his great multitude, and those who remain will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17984Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17984Z\"></sup>very few and feeble.”"
		},
		"17": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">17 </span>An <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17985A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17985A\"></sup>oracle concerning <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17985B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17985B\"></sup>Damascus.Behold, Damascus will cease to be a cityand will become a heap of ruins.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>The cities of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17986C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17986C\"></sup>Aroer are deserted;they will be for flocks,which will lie down, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17986D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17986D\"></sup>none will make them afraid.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>The fortress will disappear from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17987E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17987E\"></sup>Ephraim,and the kingdom from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17987F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17987F\"></sup>Damascus;and the remnant of Syria will belike <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17987G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17987G\"></sup>the glory of the children of Israel,declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>And in that day <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17988H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17988H\"></sup>the glory of Jacob will be brought low,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17988I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17988I\"></sup>the fat of his flesh will grow lean.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>And it shall be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17989J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17989J\"></sup>as when the reaper gathers standing grainand his arm harvests the ears,and as when one gleans the ears of grainin <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17989K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17989K\"></sup>the Valley of Rephaim.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17990L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17990L\"></sup>Gleanings will be left in it,as when an olive tree is beaten—two or three berriesin the top of the highest bough,four or fiveon the branches of a fruit tree,declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> God of Israel.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17991M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17991M\"></sup>In that day man will look to his Maker, and his eyes will look on the Holy One of Israel.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17992N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17992N\"></sup>He will not look to the altars, the work of his hands, and he will not look on what his own fingers have made, either the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17992O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17992O\"></sup>Asherim or the altars of incense.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17993P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17993P\"></sup>In that day their strong cities will be like the deserted places of the wooded heights and the hilltops, which they deserted because of the children of Israel, and there will be desolation.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17994Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17994Q\"></sup>you have forgotten the God of your salvationand have not remembered the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17994R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17994R\"></sup>Rock of your refuge;therefore, though you plant pleasant plantsand sow the vine-branch of a stranger,",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>though you make them grow on the day that you plant them,and make them blossom in the morning that you sow,yet the harvest will flee awayin a day of grief and incurable pain.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Ah, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17996S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17996S\"></sup>the thunder of many peoples;they thunder like the thundering of the sea!Ah, the roar of nations;they roar like the roaring of mighty waters!",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17997T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17997T\"></sup>The nations roar like the roaring of many waters,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17997U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17997U\"></sup>but he will rebuke them, and they will flee far away,chased <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17997V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17997V\"></sup>like chaff on the mountains before the windand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17997W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17997W\"></sup>whirling dust before the storm.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17998X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17998X\"></sup>At evening time, behold, terror!Before morning, they are no more!This is the portion of those who loot us,and the lot of those who plunder us."
		},
		"18": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">18 </span>Ah, land of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17999A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17999A\"></sup>whirring wingsthat is beyond the rivers of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17999B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17999B\"></sup>Cush,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>which <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18000C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18000C\"></sup>sends ambassadors by the sea,in vessels of papyrus on the waters!Go, you swift messengers,to a nation <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18000D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18000D\"></sup>tall and smooth,to a people feared near and far,a nation <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18000E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18000E\"></sup>mighty and conquering,whose land the rivers divide.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>All you inhabitants of the world,you who dwell on the earth,when <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18001F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18001F\"></sup>a signal is raised on the mountains, look!When a trumpet is blown, hear!",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>For thus the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to me:“I will quietly look <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18002G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18002G\"></sup>from my dwellinglike clear heat in sunshine,like a cloud of dew in the heat of harvest.”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18003H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18003H\"></sup>For before the harvest, when the blossom is over,and the flower becomes a ripening grape,he cuts off the shoots with pruning hooks,and the spreading branches he lops off and clears away.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18004I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18004I\"></sup>They shall all of them be leftto the birds of prey of the mountainsand to the beasts of the earth.And the birds of prey will summer on them,and all the beasts of the earth will winter on them.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18005J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18005J\"></sup>At that time tribute will be brought to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hostsfrom a people <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18005K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18005K\"></sup>tall and smooth,from a people feared near and far,a nation mighty and conquering,whose land the rivers divide,to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18005L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18005L\"></sup>Mount Zion, the place of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18005M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18005M\"></sup>name of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts."
		},
		"19": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">19 </span>An <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18006A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18006A\"></sup>oracle concerning <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18006B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18006B\"></sup>Egypt.Behold, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18006C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18006C\"></sup>is riding on a swift cloudand comes to Egypt;and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18006D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18006D\"></sup>the idols of Egypt will tremble at his presence,and the heart of the Egyptians will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18006E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18006E\"></sup>melt within them.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And I will stir up Egyptians against Egyptians,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18007F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18007F\"></sup>and they will fight, each against anotherand each against his neighbor,city against city, kingdom against kingdom;",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>and the spirit of the Egyptians within them will be emptied out,and I will confound their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18008G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18008G\"></sup>counsel;and they will inquire of the idols and the sorcerers,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18008H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18008H\"></sup>the mediums and the necromancers;",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>and I will give over the Egyptiansinto the hand of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18009I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18009I\"></sup>a hard master,and a fierce king will rule over them,declares the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span> of hosts.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>And the waters of the sea will be dried up,and the river will be dry and parched,",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>and its canals will become foul,and the branches of Egypt's Nile will diminish and dry up,reeds and rushes will rot away.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>There will be bare places by the Nile,on the brink of the Nile,and all that is sown by the Nile will be parched,will be driven away, and will be no more.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18013J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18013J\"></sup>fishermen will mourn and lament,all who cast a hook in the Nile;and they will languishwho spread nets on the water.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>The workers in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18014K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18014K\"></sup>combed flax will be in despair,and the weavers of white cotton.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Those who are the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18015L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18015L\"></sup>pillars of the land will be crushed,and all who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18015M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18015M\"></sup>work for pay will be grieved.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>The princes of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18016N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18016N\"></sup>Zoan are utterly foolish;the wisest counselors of Pharaoh give stupid counsel.How can you say to Pharaoh,“I am a son of the wise,a son of ancient kings”?",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Where then are your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18017O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18017O\"></sup>wise men?Let them tell youthat they might know what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts has purposed against Egypt.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>The princes of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18018P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18018P\"></sup>Zoan have become fools,and the princes of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18018Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18018Q\"></sup>Memphis are deluded;those who are the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18018R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18018R\"></sup>cornerstones of her tribeshave made Egypt stagger.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has mingled within her <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18019S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18019S\"></sup>a spirit of confusion,and they will make Egypt stagger in all its deeds,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18019T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18019T\"></sup>as a drunken man staggers in his vomit.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>And there will be nothing for Egyptthat <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18020U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18020U\"></sup>head or tail, palm branch or reed, may do.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>In that day the Egyptians will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18021V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18021V\"></sup>like women, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18021W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18021W\"></sup>tremble with fear before the hand that the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts shakes over them.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>And the land of Judah will become a terror to the Egyptians. Everyone to whom it is mentioned will fear because of the purpose that the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts has purposed against them.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18023X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18023X\"></sup>In that day there will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18023Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18023Y\"></sup>five cities in the land of Egypt that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18023Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18023Z\"></sup>speak the language of Canaan and swear allegiance to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts. One of these will be called the City of Destruction.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>In that day there will be an <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18024AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18024AA\"></sup>altar to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> in the midst of the land of Egypt, and a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18024AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18024AB\"></sup>pillar to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> at its border.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18025AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18025AC\"></sup>It will be a sign and a witness to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts in the land of Egypt. When they cry to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> because of oppressors, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18025AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18025AD\"></sup>he will send them a savior and defender, and deliver them.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18026AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18026AE\"></sup>And the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will make himself known to the Egyptians, and the Egyptians will know the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> in that day <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18026AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18026AF\"></sup>and worship with sacrifice and offering, and they will make vows to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> and perform them.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18027AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18027AG\"></sup>And the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will strike Egypt, striking and healing, and they will return to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, and he will listen to their pleas for mercy and heal them.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18028AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18028AH\"></sup>In that day there will be a highway from Egypt to Assyria, and Assyria will come into Egypt, and Egypt into Assyria, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18028AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18028AI\"></sup>and the Egyptians will worship with the Assyrians.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>In that day Israel will be the third with Egypt and Assyria, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18029AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18029AJ\"></sup>a blessing in the midst of the earth,",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>whom the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts has blessed, saying, “Blessed be Egypt <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18030AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18030AK\"></sup>my people, and Assyria <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18030AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18030AL\"></sup>the work of my hands, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18030AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18030AM\"></sup>Israel my inheritance.”"
		},
		"20": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">20 </span>In the year that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18031A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18031A\"></sup>the commander in chief, who was sent by Sargon the king of Assyria, came to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18031B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18031B\"></sup>Ashdod and fought against it and captured it—",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>at that time the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> spoke by Isaiah the son of Amoz, saying, “Go, and loose the sackcloth from your waist and take off your sandals from your feet,” and he did so, walking <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18032C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18032C\"></sup>naked and barefoot.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Then the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said, “As my servant Isaiah has walked naked and barefoot for three years <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18033D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18033D\"></sup>as a sign and a portent against Egypt and Cush,",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>so shall the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18034E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18034E\"></sup>king of Assyria lead away the Egyptian captives and the Cushite exiles, both the young and the old, naked and barefoot, with buttocks uncovered, the nakedness of Egypt.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18035F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18035F\"></sup>Then they shall be dismayed and ashamed because of Cush their hope and of Egypt their boast.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>And the inhabitants of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18036G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18036G\"></sup>this coastland will say in that day, ‘Behold, this is what has happened to those in whom we hoped and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18036H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18036H\"></sup>to whom we fled for help to be delivered from the king of Assyria! And we, how shall we escape?’”"
		},
		"21": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">21 </span>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18037A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18037A\"></sup>oracle concerning the wilderness of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18037B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18037B\"></sup>the sea.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18037C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18037C\"></sup>As whirlwinds in the Negeb sweep on,it comes from the wilderness,from a terrible land.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>A stern vision is told to me;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18038D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18038D\"></sup>the traitor betrays,and the destroyer destroys.Go up, O <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18038E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18038E\"></sup>Elam;lay siege, O <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18038F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18038F\"></sup>Media;all the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18038G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18038G\"></sup>sighing she has causedI bring to an end.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Therefore my loins are filled with anguish;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18039H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18039H\"></sup>pangs have seized me,like the pangs of a woman in labor;I am bowed down so that I cannot hear;I am dismayed so that I cannot see.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>My heart staggers; horror has appalled me;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18040I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18040I\"></sup>the twilight I longed forhas been turned for me into trembling.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18041J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18041J\"></sup>They prepare the table,they spread the rugs,they eat, they drink.Arise, O princes;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18041K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18041K\"></sup>oil the shield!",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>For thus the Lord said to me:“Go, set a watchman;let him announce what he sees.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>When he sees riders, horsemen in pairs,riders on donkeys, riders on camels,let him listen diligently,very diligently.”",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Then he who saw cried out:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18044L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18044L\"></sup>“Upon a watchtower I stand, O Lord,continually by day,and at my post I am stationedwhole nights.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>And behold, here come riders,horsemen in pairs!”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18045M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18045M\"></sup>And he answered,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18045N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18045N\"></sup>“Fallen, fallen is Babylon;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18045O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18045O\"></sup>and all the carved images of her godshe has shattered to the ground.”",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>O <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18046P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18046P\"></sup>my threshed and winnowed one,what I have heard from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts,the God of Israel, I announce to you.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18047Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18047Q\"></sup>oracle concerning <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18047R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18047R\"></sup>Dumah.One is calling to me from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18047S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18047S\"></sup>Seir,“Watchman, what time of the night?Watchman, what time of the night?”",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>The watchman says:“Morning comes, and also <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18048T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18048T\"></sup>the night.If you will inquire, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18048U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18048U\"></sup>inquire;come back again.”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18049V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18049V\"></sup>oracle concerning <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18049W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18049W\"></sup>Arabia.In the thickets in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18049X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18049X\"></sup>Arabia you will lodge,O <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18049Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18049Y\"></sup>caravans of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18049Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18049Z\"></sup>Dedanites.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>To the thirsty bring water;meet the fugitive with bread,O inhabitants of the land of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18050AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18050AA\"></sup>Tema.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>For they have fled from the swords,from the drawn sword,from the bent bow,and from the press of battle.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>For thus the Lord said to me, “Within a year, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18052AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18052AB\"></sup>according to the years of a hired worker, all the glory of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18052AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18052AC\"></sup>Kedar will come to an end.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>And the remainder of the archers of the mighty men of the sons of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18053AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18053AD\"></sup>Kedar will be few, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18053AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18053AE\"></sup>for the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, the God of Israel, has spoken.”"
		},
		"22": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">22 </span>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18054A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18054A\"></sup>oracle concerning <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18054B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18054B\"></sup>the valley of vision.What do you mean that you have gone up,all of you, to the housetops,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>you who are full of shoutings,tumultuous city, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18055C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18055C\"></sup>exultant town?Your slain are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18055D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18055D\"></sup>not slain with the swordor dead in battle.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18056E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18056E\"></sup>All your leaders have fled together;without the bow they were captured.All of you who were found were captured,though they had fled far away.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Therefore I said:“Look away from me;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18057F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18057F\"></sup>let me weep bitter tears;do not labor to comfort meconcerning the destruction of the daughter of my people.”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18058G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18058G\"></sup>For the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span> of hosts has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18058H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18058H\"></sup>a dayof tumult and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18058I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18058I\"></sup>trampling and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18058J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18058J\"></sup>confusionin <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18058K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18058K\"></sup>the valley of vision,a battering down of wallsand a shouting to the mountains.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18059L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18059L\"></sup>Elam bore the quiverwith chariots and horsemen,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18059M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18059M\"></sup>Kir uncovered the shield.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Your choicest valleys were full of chariots,and the horsemen took their stand at the gates.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>He has taken away <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18061N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18061N\"></sup>the covering of Judah.In that day you looked to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18061O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18061O\"></sup>the weapons of the House of the Forest,",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>and you saw that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18062P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18062P\"></sup>the breaches of the city of David were many. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18062Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18062Q\"></sup>You collected the waters of the lower pool,",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>and you counted the houses of Jerusalem, and you broke down the houses to fortify the wall.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18064R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18064R\"></sup>You made a reservoir between <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18064S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18064S\"></sup>the two walls for the water of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18064T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18064T\"></sup>the old pool. But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18064U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18064U\"></sup>you did not look to him who did it, or see him who planned it long ago.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>In that day <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18065V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18065V\"></sup>the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span> of hostscalled for weeping and mourning,for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18065W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18065W\"></sup>baldness and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18065X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18065X\"></sup>wearing sackcloth;",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>and behold, joy and gladness,killing oxen and slaughtering sheep,eating flesh and drinking wine.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18066Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18066Y\"></sup>“Let us eat and drink,for tomorrow we die.”",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18067Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18067Z\"></sup>has revealed himself in my ears:“Surely <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18067AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18067AA\"></sup>this iniquity will not be atoned for you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18067AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18067AB\"></sup>until you die,”says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span> of hosts.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span> of hosts, “Come, go to this steward, to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18068AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18068AC\"></sup>Shebna, who is over the household, and say to him:",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>What have you to do here, and whom have you here, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18069AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18069AD\"></sup>that you have cut out here a tomb for yourself, you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18069AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18069AE\"></sup>who cut out a tomb on the height and carve a dwelling for yourself in the rock?",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Behold, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will hurl you away violently, O you strong man. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18070AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18070AF\"></sup>He will seize firm hold on you",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>and whirl you around and around, and throw you like a ball into a wide land. There you shall die, and there shall be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18071AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18071AG\"></sup>your glorious chariots, you shame of your master's house.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18072AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18072AH\"></sup>I will thrust you from your office, and you will be pulled down from your station.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>In that day I will call my servant <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18073AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18073AI\"></sup>Eliakim the son of Hilkiah,",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18074AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18074AJ\"></sup>I will clothe him with your robe, and will bind your sash on him, and will commit your authority to his hand. And he shall be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18074AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18074AK\"></sup>a father to the inhabitants of Jerusalem and to the house of Judah.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>And I will place <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18075AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18075AL\"></sup>on his shoulder <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18075AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18075AM\"></sup>the key of the house of David. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18075AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18075AN\"></sup>He shall open, and none shall shut; and he shall shut, and none shall open.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>And I will fasten him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18076AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18076AO\"></sup>like a peg in a secure place, and he will become <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18076AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18076AP\"></sup>a throne of honor to his father's house.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>And they will hang on him the whole honor of his father's house, the offspring and issue, every small vessel, from the cups to all the flagons.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>In that day, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18078AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18078AQ\"></sup>the peg that was fastened in a secure place will give way, and it will be cut down and fall, and the load that was on it will be cut off, for the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has spoken.”"
		},
		"23": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">23 </span>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18079A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18079A\"></sup>oracle concerning <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18079B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18079B\"></sup>Tyre.Wail, O <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18079C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18079C\"></sup>ships of Tarshish,for Tyre is laid waste, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18079D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18079D\"></sup>without house or harbor!From <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18079E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18079E\"></sup>the land of Cyprusit is revealed to them.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Be still, O inhabitants of the coast;the merchants of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18080F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18080F\"></sup>Sidon, who cross the sea, have filled you.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And on many watersyour revenue was the grain of Shihor,the harvest of the Nile;you were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18081G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18081G\"></sup>the merchant of the nations.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Be ashamed, O <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18082H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18082H\"></sup>Sidon, for the sea has spoken,the stronghold of the sea, saying:“I have neither labored nor given birth,I have neither reared young mennor brought up young women.”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>When the report comes to Egypt,they will be in anguish over the report about Tyre.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18084I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18084I\"></sup>Cross over to Tarshish;wail, O inhabitants of the coast!",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Is this your exultant city<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18085J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18085J\"></sup>whose origin is from days of old,whose feet carried herto settle far away?",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Who has purposed thisagainst Tyre, the bestower of crowns,whose merchants were princes,whose traders were the honored of the earth?",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts has purposed it,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18087K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18087K\"></sup>to defile the pompous pride of all glory,to dishonor all the honored of the earth.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Cross over your land like the Nile,O daughter of Tarshish;there is no restraint anymore.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18089L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18089L\"></sup>He has stretched out his hand over the sea;he has shaken the kingdoms;the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has given command concerning Canaanto destroy its strongholds.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>And he said:“You will no more exult,O oppressed virgin daughter of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18090M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18090M\"></sup>Sidon;arise, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18090N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18090N\"></sup>cross over to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18090O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18090O\"></sup>Cyprus,even there you will have no rest.”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Behold the land of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18091P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18091P\"></sup>the Chaldeans! This is the people that was not; Assyria destined it for wild beasts. They erected <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18091Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18091Q\"></sup>their siege towers, they stripped her palaces bare, they made her a ruin.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18092R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18092R\"></sup>Wail, O ships of Tarshish,for your stronghold is laid waste.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>In that day Tyre will be forgotten for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18093S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18093S\"></sup>seventy years, like the days of one king. At the end of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18093T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18093T\"></sup>seventy years, it will happen to Tyre as in the song of the prostitute:",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“Take a harp;go about the city,O forgotten prostitute!Make sweet melody;sing many songs,that you may be remembered.”",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>At the end of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18095U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18095U\"></sup>seventy years, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will visit Tyre, and she will return to her wages and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18095V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18095V\"></sup>will prostitute herself with all the kingdoms of the world on the face of the earth.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Her merchandise and her wages will be holy to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>. It will not be stored or hoarded, but her merchandise will supply abundant food and fine clothing for those who dwell before the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>."
		},
		"24": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">24 </span>Behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18097A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18097A\"></sup>the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will empty the earth and make it desolate,and he will twist its surface and scatter its inhabitants.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18098B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18098B\"></sup>And it shall be, as with the people, so with the priest;as with the slave, so with his master;as with the maid, so with her mistress;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18098C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18098C\"></sup>as with the buyer, so with the seller;as with the lender, so with the borrower;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18098D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18098D\"></sup>as with the creditor, so with the debtor.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18099E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18099E\"></sup>The earth shall be utterly empty and utterly plundered;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18099F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18099F\"></sup>for the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has spoken this word.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18100G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18100G\"></sup>The earth mourns and withers;the world languishes and withers;the highest people of the earth languish.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>The earth lies <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18101H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18101H\"></sup>defiledunder its inhabitants;for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18101I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18101I\"></sup>they have transgressed the laws,violated the statutes,broken the everlasting covenant.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Therefore <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18102J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18102J\"></sup>a curse devours the earth,and its inhabitants <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18102K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18102K\"></sup>suffer for their guilt;therefore the inhabitants of the earth are scorched,and few men are left.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18103L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18103L\"></sup>The wine mourns,the vine languishes,all the merry-hearted sigh.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18104M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18104M\"></sup>The mirth of the tambourines is stilled,the noise of the jubilant has ceased,the mirth of the lyre is stilled.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>No more do they drink wine <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18105N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18105N\"></sup>with singing;strong drink is bitter to those who drink it.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18106O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18106O\"></sup>The wasted city is broken down;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18106P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18106P\"></sup>every house is shut up so that none can enter.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18107Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18107Q\"></sup>There is an outcry in the streets for lack of wine;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18107R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18107R\"></sup>all joy has grown dark;the gladness of the earth is banished.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Desolation is left in the city;the gates are battered into ruins.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>For thus it shall be in the midst of the earthamong the nations,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18109S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18109S\"></sup>as when an olive tree is beaten,as at the gleaning when the grape harvest is done.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>They lift up their voices, they sing for joy;over the majesty of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> they shout from the west.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18111T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18111T\"></sup>Therefore in the east give glory to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>;in the coastlands of the sea, give glory to the name of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, the God of Israel.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18112U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18112U\"></sup>From the ends of the earth we hear songs of praise,of glory to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18112V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18112V\"></sup>the Righteous One.But I say, “I waste away,I waste away. Woe is me!For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18112W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18112W\"></sup>the traitors have betrayed,with betrayal the traitors have betrayed.”",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18113X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18113X\"></sup>Terror and the pit and the snareare upon you, O inhabitant of the earth!",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18114Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18114Y\"></sup>He who flees at the sound of the terrorshall fall into the pit,and he who climbs out of the pitshall be caught in the snare.For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18114Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18114Z\"></sup>the windows of heaven are opened,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18114AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18114AA\"></sup>the foundations of the earth tremble.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>The earth is utterly broken,the earth is split apart,the earth is violently shaken.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>The earth <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18116AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18116AB\"></sup>staggers like a drunken man;it sways like a hut;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18116AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18116AC\"></sup>its transgression lies heavy upon it,and it falls, and will not rise again.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>On that day the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will punishthe host of heaven, in heaven,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18117AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18117AD\"></sup>the kings of the earth, on the earth.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18118AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18118AE\"></sup>They will be gathered togetheras prisoners in a pit;they will be shut up in a prison,and after many days <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18118AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18118AF\"></sup>they will be punished.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18119AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18119AG\"></sup>Then the moon will be confoundedand the sun ashamed,for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18119AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18119AH\"></sup>the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts reignson Mount Zion and in Jerusalem,and his glory will be before his elders."
		},
		"25": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">25 </span>O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18120A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18120A\"></sup>you are my God;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18120B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18120B\"></sup>I will exalt you; I will praise your name,for you have done wonderful things,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18120C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18120C\"></sup>plans formed of old, faithful and sure.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>For you have made the city <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18121D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18121D\"></sup>a heap,the fortified city a ruin;the foreigners' palace is a city no more;it will never be rebuilt.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18122E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18122E\"></sup>Therefore strong peoples will glorify you;cities of ruthless nations will fear you.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18123F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18123F\"></sup>For you have been a stronghold to the poor,a stronghold to the needy in his distress,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18123G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18123G\"></sup>a shelter from the storm and a shade from the heat;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18123H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18123H\"></sup>for the breath of the ruthless is like a storm against a wall,",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><span class=\"indent-1-breaks\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18124I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18124I\"></sup>like heat in a dry place.You subdue the noise of the foreigners;as heat by the shade of a cloud,so the song of the ruthless is put down.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18125J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18125J\"></sup>On this mountain the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts will make for all peoplesa feast of rich food, a feast of well-aged wine,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18125K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18125K\"></sup>of rich food full of marrow, of aged wine well refined.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>And he will swallow up <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18126L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18126L\"></sup>on this mountainthe covering that is cast over all peoples,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18126M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18126M\"></sup>the veil that is spread over all nations.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><span class=\"indent-1-breaks\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18127N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18127N\"></sup>He will swallow up death forever;and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18127O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18127O\"></sup>the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span> will wipe away tears from all faces,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18127P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18127P\"></sup>the reproach of his people he will take away from all the earth,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18127Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18127Q\"></sup>for the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has spoken.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>It will be said on that day,“Behold, this is our God; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18128R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18128R\"></sup>we have waited for him, that he might save us.This is the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>; we have waited for him;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18128S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18128S\"></sup>let us be glad and rejoice in his salvation.”",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>For the hand of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will rest <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18129T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18129T\"></sup>on this mountain,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18129U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18129U\"></sup>Moab shall be trampled down in his place,as straw is trampled down in a dunghill.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18130V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18130V\"></sup>And he will spread out his hands in the midst of itas a swimmer spreads his hands out to swim,but the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18130W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18130W\"></sup>will lay low his pompous pride together with the skill of his hands.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>And the high fortifications of his walls he will bring down,lay low, and cast to the ground, to the dust."
		},
		"26": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">26 </span>In that day <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18132A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18132A\"></sup>this song will be sung in the land of Judah:“We have a strong city;he sets up <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18132B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18132B\"></sup>salvationas walls and bulwarks.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18133C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18133C\"></sup>Open the gates,that the righteous nation that keeps faith may enter in.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18134D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18134D\"></sup>You keep him in perfect peacewhose mind is stayed on you,because he trusts in you.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Trust in the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> forever,for the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span> is an everlasting rock.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18136E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18136E\"></sup>For he has humbledthe inhabitants of the height,the lofty city.He lays it low, lays it low to the ground,casts it to the dust.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>The foot tramples it,the feet of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18137F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18137F\"></sup>the poor,the steps of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18137G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18137G\"></sup>the needy.”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>The path of the righteous is level;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18138H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18138H\"></sup>you make level the way of the righteous.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>In the path of your judgments,O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, we wait for you;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18139I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18139I\"></sup>your name and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18139J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18139J\"></sup>remembranceare the desire of our soul.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>My soul yearns for you in the night;my spirit within me earnestly seeks you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18140K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18140K\"></sup>For when your judgments are in the earth,the inhabitants of the world learn righteousness.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18141L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18141L\"></sup>If favor is shown to the wicked,he does not learn righteousness;in the land of uprightness he deals corruptlyand does not see the majesty of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18142M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18142M\"></sup>your hand is lifted up,but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18142N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18142N\"></sup>they do not see it.Let them see your zeal for your people, and be ashamed.Let <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18142O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18142O\"></sup>the fire for your adversaries consume them.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, you will ordain <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18143P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18143P\"></sup>peace for us,for you have indeed done for us all our works.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> our God,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18144Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18144Q\"></sup>other lords besides you have ruled over us,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18144R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18144R\"></sup>but your name alone we bring to remembrance.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>They are dead, they will not live;they are shades, they will not arise;to that end you have visited them with destructionand wiped out all remembrance of them.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18146S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18146S\"></sup>But you have increased the nation, O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,you have increased the nation; you are glorified;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18146T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18146T\"></sup>you have enlarged all the borders of the land.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18147U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18147U\"></sup>in distress they sought you;they poured out a whispered prayerwhen your discipline was upon them.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18148V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18148V\"></sup>Like a pregnant womanwho writhes and cries out in her pangswhen she is near to giving birth,so were we because of you, O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>;",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><span class=\"indent-1-breaks\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18149W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18149W\"></sup>we were pregnant, we writhed,but we have given birth to wind.We have accomplished no deliverance in the earth,and the inhabitants of the world have not fallen.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18150X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18150X\"></sup>Your dead shall live; their bodies shall rise.You who dwell in the dust, awake and sing for joy!For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18150Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18150Y\"></sup>your dew is a dew of light,and the earth will give birth to the dead.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Come, my people, enter your chambers,and shut your doors behind you;hide yourselves <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18151Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18151Z\"></sup>for a little whileuntil the fury has passed by.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18152AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18152AA\"></sup>For behold, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is coming out from his placeto punish the inhabitants of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18152AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18152AB\"></sup>the earth for their iniquity,and the earth will disclose the blood shed on it,and will no more cover its slain."
		},
		"27": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">27 </span>In that day the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> with his hard and great and strong <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18153A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18153A\"></sup>sword will punish <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18153B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18153B\"></sup>Leviathan the fleeing serpent, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18153C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18153C\"></sup>Leviathan the twisting serpent, and he will slay <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18153D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18153D\"></sup>the dragon that is in the sea.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>In that day,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18154E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18154E\"></sup>“A pleasant vineyard, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18154F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18154F\"></sup>sing of it!",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><span class=\"indent-1-breaks\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>I, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, am its keeper;every moment I water it.Lest anyone punish it,I keep it night and day;",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><span class=\"indent-1-breaks\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>I have no wrath.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18156G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18156G\"></sup>Would that I had thorns and briers to battle!I would march against them,I would burn them up together.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Or let them lay hold of my protection,let them make peace with me,let them make peace with me.”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18158H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18158H\"></sup>In days to come Jacob shall take root,Israel shall blossom and put forth shootsand fill the whole world with fruit.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18159I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18159I\"></sup>Has he struck them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18159J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18159J\"></sup>as he struck those who struck them?Or have they been slain <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18159K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18159K\"></sup>as their slayers were slain?",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18160L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18160L\"></sup>Measure by measure, by exile you contended with them;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18160M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18160M\"></sup>he removed them with his fierce breath in the day of the east wind.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Therefore by this <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18161N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18161N\"></sup>the guilt of Jacob will be atoned for,and this will be the full fruit of the removal of his sin:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18161O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18161O\"></sup>when he makes all the stones of the altarslike chalkstones crushed to pieces,no <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18161P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18161P\"></sup>Asherim or incense altars will remain standing.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18162Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18162Q\"></sup>For the fortified city is solitary,a habitation deserted and forsaken, like the wilderness;there the calf grazes;there it lies down and strips its branches.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>When its boughs are dry, they are broken;women come and make a fire of them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18163R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18163R\"></sup>For this is a people without discernment;therefore he who made them will not have compassion on them;he who formed them will show them no favor.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>In that day <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18164S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18164S\"></sup>from the river Euphrates to the Brook of Egypt the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will thresh out the grain, and you will be gleaned one by one, O people of Israel.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>And in that day <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18165T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18165T\"></sup>a great trumpet will be blown, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18165U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18165U\"></sup>and those who were lost in the land of Assyria and those who were driven out to the land of Egypt <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18165V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18165V\"></sup>will come and worship the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> on the holy mountain at Jerusalem."
		},
		"28": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">28 </span>Ah, the proud crown of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18166A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18166A\"></sup>the drunkards of Ephraim,and the fading flower of its glorious beauty,which is on the head of the rich valley of those overcome with wine!",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Behold, the Lord has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18167B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18167B\"></sup>one who is mighty and strong;like a storm of hail, a destroying tempest,like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18167C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18167C\"></sup>a storm of mighty, overflowing waters,he casts down to the earth with his hand.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18168D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18168D\"></sup>The proud crown of the drunkards of Ephraimwill be trodden underfoot;",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18169E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18169E\"></sup>and the fading flower of its glorious beauty,which is on the head of the rich valley,will be like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18169F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18169F\"></sup>a first-ripe fig before the summer:when someone sees it, he swallows itas soon as it is in his hand.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18170G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18170G\"></sup>In that day the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts will be a crown of glory,and a diadem of beauty, to the remnant of his people,",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18171H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18171H\"></sup>a spirit of justice to him who sits in judgment,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18171I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18171I\"></sup>strength to those who turn back the battle at the gate.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18172J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18172J\"></sup>These also reel with wineand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18172K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18172K\"></sup>stagger with strong drink;the priest and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18172L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18172L\"></sup>the prophet reel with strong drink,they are swallowed by wine,they stagger with strong drink,they reel in vision,they stumble in giving judgment.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>For all tables are full of filthy vomit,with no space left.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18174M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18174M\"></sup>“To whom will he teach knowledge,and to whom will he explain the message?Those who are weaned from the milk,those taken from the breast?",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>For it is precept upon precept, precept upon precept,line upon line, line upon line,here a little, there a little.”",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18176N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18176N\"></sup>For by people of strange lipsand with a foreign tonguethe <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will speak to this people,",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><span class=\"indent-1-breaks\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>to whom he has said,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18177O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18177O\"></sup>“This is rest;give rest to the weary;and this is repose”;yet they would not hear.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>And the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will be to themprecept upon precept, precept upon precept,line upon line, line upon line,here a little, there a little,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18178P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18178P\"></sup>that they may go, and fall backward,and be broken, and snared, and taken.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Therefore hear the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18179Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18179Q\"></sup>scoffers,who rule this people in Jerusalem!",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Because you have said, “We have made a covenant with death,and with Sheol we have an agreement,when the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18180R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18180R\"></sup>overwhelming whip passes throughit will not come to us,for we have made <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18180S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18180S\"></sup>lies our refuge,and in falsehood we have taken shelter”;",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>therefore thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18181T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18181T\"></sup>“Behold, I am the one who has laid as a foundation <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18181U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18181U\"></sup>in Zion,a stone, a tested stone,a precious cornerstone, of a sure foundation:‘Whoever believes will not be in haste.’",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>And I will make justice <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18182V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18182V\"></sup>the line,and righteousness <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18182W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18182W\"></sup>the plumb line;and hail will sweep away the refuge of lies,and waters will overwhelm the shelter.”",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18183X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18183X\"></sup>your covenant with death will be annulled,and your agreement with Sheol will not stand;when the overwhelming scourge passes through,you will be beaten down by it.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>As often as it passes through it will take you;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18184Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18184Y\"></sup>for morning by morning it will pass through,by day and by night;and it will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18184Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18184Z\"></sup>sheer terror to understand the message.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>For the bed is too short to stretch oneself on,and the covering too narrow to wrap oneself in.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>For the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will rise up <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18186AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18186AA\"></sup>as on Mount Perazim;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18186AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18186AB\"></sup>as in the Valley of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18186AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18186AC\"></sup>Gibeon he will be roused;to do his deed—strange is his deed!and to work his work—alien is his work!",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Now therefore do not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18187AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18187AD\"></sup>scoff,lest your bonds be made strong;for I have heard <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18187AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18187AE\"></sup>a decree of destructionfrom the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span> of hosts against the whole land.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Give ear, and hear my voice;give attention, and hear my speech.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Does he who plows for sowing plow continually?Does he continually open and harrow his ground?",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18190AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18190AF\"></sup>When he has leveled its surface,does he not scatter dill, sow cumin,and put in wheat in rowsand barley in its proper place,and emmer as the border?",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18191AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18191AG\"></sup>For he is rightly instructed;his God teaches him.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>Dill is not threshed with a threshing sledge,nor is a cart wheel rolled over cumin,but dill is beaten out with a stick,and cumin with a rod.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>Does one crush grain for bread?No, he does not thresh it forever;when he drives his cart wheel over itwith his horses, he does not crush it.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>This also comes from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts;he is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18194AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18194AH\"></sup>wonderful in counseland excellent in wisdom."
		},
		"29": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">29 </span>Ah, Ariel, Ariel,the city <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18195A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18195A\"></sup>where David encamped!Add year to year;let the feasts run their round.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Yet I will distress Ariel,and there shall be moaning and lamentation,and she shall be to me like an Ariel.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18197B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18197B\"></sup>And I will encamp against you all around,and will besiege you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18197C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18197C\"></sup>with towersand I will raise siegeworks against you.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18198D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18198D\"></sup>And you will be brought low; from the earth you shall speak,and from the dust your speech will be bowed down;your voice shall come from the ground like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18198E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18198E\"></sup>the voice of a ghost,and from the dust your speech shall whisper.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>But the multitude of your foreign foes shall be like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18199F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18199F\"></sup>small dust,and the multitude of the ruthless like passing chaff.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18199G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18199G\"></sup>And in an instant, suddenly,",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><span class=\"indent-1-breaks\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18200H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18200H\"></sup>you will be visited by the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hostswith thunder and with earthquake and great noise,with whirlwind and tempest, and the flame of a devouring fire.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18201I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18201I\"></sup>the multitude of all the nations that fight against Ariel,all that fight against her and her stronghold and distress her,shall be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18201J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18201J\"></sup>like a dream, a vision of the night.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18202K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18202K\"></sup>As when a hungry man dreams, and behold, he is eating,and awakes with his hunger not satisfied,or as when a thirsty man dreams, and behold, he is drinking,and awakes faint, with his thirst not quenched,so shall the multitude of all the nations bethat fight against Mount Zion.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Astonish yourselves and be astonished;blind yourselves and be blind!Be drunk, but not with wine;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18203L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18203L\"></sup>stagger, but not with strong drink!",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18204M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18204M\"></sup>For the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has poured out upon youa spirit of deep sleep,and has closed your eyes (the prophets),and covered your heads (the seers).",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>And the vision of all this has become to you like the words of a book that is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18205N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18205N\"></sup>sealed. When men give it to one who can read, saying, “Read this,” he says, “I cannot, for it is sealed.”",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>And when they give the book to one who cannot read, saying, “Read this,” he says, “I cannot read.”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>And the Lord said:“Because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18207O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18207O\"></sup>this people <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18207P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18207P\"></sup>draw near with their mouthand honor me with their lips,while their hearts are far from me,and their fear of me is a commandment taught by men,",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>therefore, behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18208Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18208Q\"></sup>I will againdo wonderful things with this people,with wonder upon wonder;and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18208R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18208R\"></sup>the wisdom of their wise men shall perish,and the discernment of their discerning men shall be hidden.”",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Ah, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18209S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18209S\"></sup>you who hide deep from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your counsel,whose deeds are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18209T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18209T\"></sup>in the dark,and who say, “Who sees us? Who knows us?”",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18210U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18210U\"></sup>You turn things upside down!Shall the potter be regarded as the clay,that the thing made should say of its maker,“He did not make me”;or the thing formed say of him who formed it,“He has no understanding”?",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Is it not yet a very little while<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18211V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18211V\"></sup>until Lebanon shall be turned into a fruitful field,and the fruitful field shall be regarded as a forest?",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>In that day <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18212W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18212W\"></sup>the deaf shall hear<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18212X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18212X\"></sup>the words of a book,and out of their gloom and darkness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18212Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18212Y\"></sup>the eyes of the blind shall see.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18213Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18213Z\"></sup>The meek shall obtain fresh joy in the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,and the poor among mankind shall exult in the Holy One of Israel.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>For the ruthless shall come to nothingand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18214AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18214AA\"></sup>the scoffer cease,and all who watch to do evil shall be cut off,",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>who by a word make a man out to be an offender,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18215AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18215AB\"></sup>lay a snare for him who reproves in the gate,and with an empty plea <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18215AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18215AC\"></sup>turn aside him who is in the right.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Therefore thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18216AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18216AD\"></sup>who redeemed Abraham, concerning the house of Jacob:“Jacob shall no more be ashamed,no more shall his face grow pale.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>For when he sees his children,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18217AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18217AE\"></sup>the work of my hands, in his midst,they will sanctify my name;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18217AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18217AF\"></sup>they will sanctify the Holy One of Jacoband will stand in awe of the God of Israel.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>And those <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18218AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18218AG\"></sup>who go astray in spirit will come to understanding,and those who murmur will accept instruction.”"
		},
		"30": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">30 </span>“Ah, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18219A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18219A\"></sup>stubborn children,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18219B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18219B\"></sup>“who carry out a plan, but not mine,and who make <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18219C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18219C\"></sup>an alliance, but not of my Spirit,that they may add sin to sin;",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18220D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18220D\"></sup>who set out to go down to Egypt,without asking for my direction,to take refuge in the protection of Pharaohand to seek shelter in the shadow of Egypt!",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18221E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18221E\"></sup>Therefore shall the protection of Pharaoh turn to your shame,and the shelter in the shadow of Egypt to your humiliation.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>For though his officials are at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18222F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18222F\"></sup>Zoanand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18222G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18222G\"></sup>his envoys reach <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18222H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18222H\"></sup>Hanes,",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>everyone comes to shamethrough <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18223I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18223I\"></sup>a people that cannot profit them,that brings neither help nor profit,but shame and disgrace.”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>An <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18224J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18224J\"></sup>oracle on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18224K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18224K\"></sup>the beasts of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18224L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18224L\"></sup>the Negeb.Through a land of trouble and anguish,from where come the lioness and the lion,the adder and the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18224M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18224M\"></sup>flying fiery serpent,they carry their riches on the backs of donkeys,and their treasures on the humps of camels,to a people that cannot profit them.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Egypt's <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18225N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18225N\"></sup>help is worthless and empty;therefore I have called her<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18225O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18225O\"></sup>“Rahab who sits still.”",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>And now, go, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18226P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18226P\"></sup>write it before them on a tabletand inscribe it in a book,that it may be for the time to comeas a witness forever.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18227Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18227Q\"></sup>For they are a rebellious people,lying children,children unwilling to hearthe instruction of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>;",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18228R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18228R\"></sup>who say to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18228S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18228S\"></sup>the seers, “Do not see,”and to the prophets, “Do not prophesy to us what is right;speak to us <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18228T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18228T\"></sup>smooth things,prophesy illusions,",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>leave the way, turn aside from the path,let us hear no more about the Holy One of Israel.”",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Therefore thus says the Holy One of Israel,“Because you despise this wordand trust in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18230U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18230U\"></sup>oppression and perversenessand rely on them,",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>therefore this iniquity shall be to you<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18231V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18231V\"></sup>like a breach in a high wall, bulging out and about to collapse,whose breaking comes suddenly, in an instant;",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>and its breaking is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18232W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18232W\"></sup>like that of a potter's vesselthat is smashed so ruthlesslythat among its fragments not a shard is foundwith which to take fire from the hearth,or to dip up water out of the cistern.”",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>For thus said the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, the Holy One of Israel,“In <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18233X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18233X\"></sup>returning and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18233Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18233Y\"></sup>rest you shall be saved;in quietness and in trust shall be your strength.”But you were unwilling,",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum mid-line\">16 </sup>and you said,“No! We will flee upon <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18234Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18234Z\"></sup>horses”;therefore you shall flee away;and, “We will ride upon swift steeds”;therefore your pursuers shall be swift.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18235AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18235AA\"></sup>A thousand shall flee at the threat of one;at the threat of five you shall flee,till you are leftlike a flagstaff on the top of a mountain,like a signal on a hill.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Therefore the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18236AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18236AB\"></sup>waits to be gracious to you,and therefore he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18236AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18236AC\"></sup>exalts himself to show mercy to you.For the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is a God of justice;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18236AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18236AD\"></sup>blessed are all those who wait for him.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>For a people shall dwell <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18237AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18237AE\"></sup>in Zion, in Jerusalem; you shall weep no more. He will surely be gracious to you at the sound of your cry. As soon as he hears it, he answers you.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>And though the Lord give you the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18238AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18238AF\"></sup>bread of adversity and the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18238AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18238AG\"></sup>water of affliction, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18238AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18238AH\"></sup>yet your Teacher will not hide himself anymore, but your eyes shall see your Teacher.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18239AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18239AI\"></sup>And your ears shall hear a word behind you, saying, “This is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18239AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18239AJ\"></sup>the way, walk in it,” when you turn to the right or when you turn to the left.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Then you will defile your carved idols overlaid with silver and your gold-plated metal images. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18240AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18240AK\"></sup>You will scatter them as unclean things. You will say to them, “Be gone!”",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18241AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18241AL\"></sup>And he will give <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18241AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18241AM\"></sup>rain for the seed with which you sow the ground, and bread, the produce of the ground, which will be rich and plenteous. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18241AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18241AN\"></sup>In that day your livestock will graze in large pastures,",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18242AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18242AO\"></sup>the oxen and the donkeys that work the ground will eat seasoned fodder, which has been winnowed with shovel and fork.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18243AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18243AP\"></sup>on every lofty mountain and every high hill there will be brooks running with water, in the day of the great slaughter, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18243AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18243AQ\"></sup>when the towers fall.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18244AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18244AR\"></sup>Moreover, the light of the moon will be as the light of the sun, and the light of the sun will be sevenfold, as the light of seven days, in the day when <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18244AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18244AS\"></sup>the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> binds up <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18244AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18244AT\"></sup>the brokenness of his people, and heals the wounds inflicted by his blow.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>Behold, the name of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> comes from afar,burning with his anger, and in thick rising smoke;his lips are full of fury,and his tongue is like a devouring fire;",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18246AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18246AU\"></sup>his breath is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18246AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18246AV\"></sup>like an overflowing streamthat reaches up to the neck;to sift the nations with the sieve of destruction,and to place on the jaws of the peoples <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18246AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18246AW\"></sup>a bridle that leads astray.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>You shall have a song as in the night when a holy feast is kept, and gladness of heart, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18247AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18247AX\"></sup>as when one sets out to the sound of the flute to go to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18247AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18247AY\"></sup>the mountain of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18247AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18247AZ\"></sup>the Rock of Israel.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>And the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18248BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18248BA\"></sup>will cause his majestic voice to be heard and the descending blow of his arm to be seen, in furious anger <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18248BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18248BB\"></sup>and a flame of devouring fire, with a cloudburst <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18248BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18248BC\"></sup>and storm and hailstones.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>The Assyrians will be terror-stricken at the voice of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18249BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18249BD\"></sup>when he strikes with his rod.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>And every stroke of the appointed staff that the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> lays on them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18250BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18250BE\"></sup>will be to the sound of tambourines and lyres. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18250BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18250BF\"></sup>Battling with brandished arm, he will fight with them.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18251BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18251BG\"></sup>a burning place has long been prepared; indeed, for the king it is made ready, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18251BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18251BH\"></sup>its pyre made deep and wide, with fire and wood in abundance; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18251BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18251BI\"></sup>the breath of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, like a stream of sulfur, kindles it."
		},
		"31": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">31 </span>Woe to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18252A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18252A\"></sup>those who go down to Egypt for helpand rely on horses,who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18252B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18252B\"></sup>trust in chariots because they are manyand in horsemen because they are very strong,but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18252C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18252C\"></sup>do not look to the Holy One of Israelor consult the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>!",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18253D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18253D\"></sup>yet he is wise and brings disaster;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18253E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18253E\"></sup>he does not call back his words,but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18253F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18253F\"></sup>will arise against the house of the evildoersand against the helpers of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18253G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18253G\"></sup>those who work iniquity.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>The Egyptians are man, and not God,and their horses <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18254H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18254H\"></sup>are flesh, and not spirit.When the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> stretches out his hand,the helper will stumble, and he who is helped will fall,and they will all perish together.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>For thus the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to me,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18255I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18255I\"></sup>“As a lion or a young lion growls over his prey,and when a band of shepherds is called out against himhe is not terrified by their shoutingor daunted at their noise,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18255J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18255J\"></sup>so the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts will come downto fight on Mount Zion and on its hill.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18256K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18256K\"></sup>Like birds hovering, so the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hostswill protect Jerusalem;he will protect and deliver it;he will spare and rescue it.”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18257L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18257L\"></sup>Turn to him from whom people have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18257M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18257M\"></sup>deeply revolted, O children of Israel.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>For in that day <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18258N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18258N\"></sup>everyone shall cast away his idols of silver and his idols of gold, which your hands have sinfully made for you.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18259O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18259O\"></sup>“And the Assyrian shall fall by a sword, not of man;and a sword, not of man, shall devour him;and he shall flee from the sword,and his young men shall be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18259P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18259P\"></sup>put to forced labor.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18260Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18260Q\"></sup>His rock shall pass away in terror,and his officers desert the standard in panic,”declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, whose <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18260R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18260R\"></sup>fire is in Zion,and whose <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18260S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18260S\"></sup>furnace is in Jerusalem."
		},
		"32": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">32 </span>Behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18261A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18261A\"></sup>a king will reign in righteousness,and princes will rule in justice.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18262B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18262B\"></sup>Each will be like a hiding place from the wind,a shelter from the storm,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18262C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18262C\"></sup>like streams of water in a dry place,like the shade of a great rock in a weary land.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18263D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18263D\"></sup>Then the eyes of those who see will not be closed,and the ears of those who hear will give attention.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>The heart of the hasty will understand and know,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18264E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18264E\"></sup>and the tongue of the stammerers will hasten to speak distinctly.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18265F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18265F\"></sup>The fool will no more be called noble,nor the scoundrel said to be honorable.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18266G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18266G\"></sup>the fool speaks folly,and his heart is busy with iniquity,to practice ungodliness,to utter error concerning the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18266H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18266H\"></sup>to leave the craving of the hungry unsatisfied,and to deprive the thirsty of drink.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>As for the scoundrel—<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18267I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18267I\"></sup>his devices are evil;he plans wicked schemesto ruin the poor with lying words,even when the plea of the needy is right.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>But he who is noble plans noble things,and on noble things he stands.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18269J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18269J\"></sup>Rise up, you women <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18269K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18269K\"></sup>who are at ease, hear my voice;you complacent daughters, give ear to my speech.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>In little more than a yearyou will shudder, you complacent women;for the grape harvest fails,the fruit harvest will not come.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Tremble, you women <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18271L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18271L\"></sup>who are at ease,shudder, you complacent ones;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18271M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18271M\"></sup>strip, and make yourselves bare,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18271N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18271N\"></sup>and tie sackcloth around your waist.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18272O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18272O\"></sup>Beat your breasts for the pleasant fields,for the fruitful vine,",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18273P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18273P\"></sup>for the soil of my peoplegrowing up in thorns and briers,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18273Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18273Q\"></sup>yes, for all the joyous housesin the exultant city.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>For the palace is forsaken,the populous city deserted;the hill and the watchtowerwill become dens forever,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18274R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18274R\"></sup>a joy of wild donkeys,a pasture of flocks;",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>until <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18275S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18275S\"></sup>the Spirit is poured upon us from on high,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18275T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18275T\"></sup>the wilderness becomes a fruitful field,and the fruitful field is deemed a forest.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Then justice will dwell in the wilderness,and righteousness abide in the fruitful field.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18277U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18277U\"></sup>And the effect of righteousness will be peace,and the result of righteousness, quietness and trust forever.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>My people will abide in a peaceful habitation,in secure dwellings, and in quiet resting places.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18279V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18279V\"></sup>And it will hail when the forest falls down,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18279W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18279W\"></sup>and the city will be utterly laid low.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18280X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18280X\"></sup>Happy are you who sow beside all waters,who let the feet of the ox and the donkey range free."
		},
		"33": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">33 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18281A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18281A\"></sup>Ah, you destroyer,who yourself have not been destroyed,you traitor,whom none has betrayed!When you have ceased to destroy,you will be destroyed;and when you have finished betraying,they will betray you.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, be gracious to us; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18282B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18282B\"></sup>we wait for you.Be our arm every morning,our salvation in the time of trouble.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18283C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18283C\"></sup>At the tumultuous noise peoples flee;when you lift yourself up, nations are scattered,",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>and your spoil is gathered as the caterpillar gathers;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18284D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18284D\"></sup>as locusts leap, it is leapt upon.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18285E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18285E\"></sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is exalted, for he dwells on high;he will fill Zion with justice and righteousness,",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18286F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18286F\"></sup>and he will be the stability of your times,abundance of salvation, wisdom, and knowledge;the fear of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is Zion's treasure.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Behold, their heroes cry in the streets;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18287G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18287G\"></sup>the envoys of peace weep bitterly.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18288H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18288H\"></sup>The highways lie waste;the traveler ceases.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18288I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18288I\"></sup>Covenants are broken;cities are despised;there is no regard for man.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18289J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18289J\"></sup>The land mourns and languishes;Lebanon is confounded and withers away;Sharon is like a desert,and Bashan and Carmel shake off their leaves.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18290K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18290K\"></sup>“Now I will arise,” says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,“now I will lift myself up;now I will be exalted.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18291L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18291L\"></sup>You conceive chaff; you give birth to stubble;your breath is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18291M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18291M\"></sup>a fire that will consume you.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>And the peoples will be as if burned to lime,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18292N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18292N\"></sup>like thorns cut down, that are burned in the fire.”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Hear, you who are far off, what I have done;and you who are near, acknowledge my might.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>The sinners in Zion are afraid;trembling has seized the godless:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18294O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18294O\"></sup>“Who among us can dwell <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18294P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18294P\"></sup>with the consuming fire?Who among us can dwell with everlasting burnings?”",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18295Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18295Q\"></sup>He who walks righteously and speaks uprightly,who despises the gain of oppressions,who shakes his hands, lest they hold a bribe,who stops his ears from hearing of bloodshed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18295R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18295R\"></sup>and shuts his eyes from looking on evil,",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>he will dwell on the heights;his place of defense will be the fortresses of rocks;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18296S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18296S\"></sup>his bread will be given him; his water will be sure.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18297T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18297T\"></sup>Your eyes will behold the king in his beauty;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18297U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18297U\"></sup>they will see a land that stretches afar.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18298V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18298V\"></sup>Your heart will muse on the terror:“Where is he who counted, where is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18298W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18298W\"></sup>he who weighed the tribute?Where is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18298X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18298X\"></sup>he who counted the towers?”",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18299Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18299Y\"></sup>You will see no more the insolent people,the people <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18299Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18299Z\"></sup>of an obscure speech that you cannot comprehend,stammering in a tongue that you cannot understand.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Behold Zion, the city of our appointed feasts!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18300AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18300AA\"></sup>Your eyes will see Jerusalem,an untroubled habitation, an <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18300AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18300AB\"></sup>immovable tent,whose stakes will never be plucked up,nor will any of its cords be broken.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>But there the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> in majesty will be for usa place of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18301AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18301AC\"></sup>broad rivers and streams,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18301AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18301AD\"></sup>where no galley with oars can go,nor majestic ship can pass.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>For the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is our <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18302AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18302AE\"></sup>judge; the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is our <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18302AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18302AF\"></sup>lawgiver;the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is our <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18302AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18302AG\"></sup>king; he will save us.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Your cords hang loose;they cannot hold the mast firm in its placeor keep the sail spread out.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18303AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18303AH\"></sup>Then prey and spoil in abundance will be divided;even <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18303AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18303AI\"></sup>the lame will take the prey.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>And no inhabitant will say, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18304AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18304AJ\"></sup>“I am sick”;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18304AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18304AK\"></sup>the people who dwell there will be forgiven their iniquity."
		},
		"34": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">34 </span>Draw near, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18305A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18305A\"></sup>O nations, to hear,and give attention, O peoples!Let the earth hear, and all that fills it;the world, and all that comes from it.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>For the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is enraged against all the nations,and furious against all their host;he has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18306B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18306B\"></sup>devoted them to destruction, has given them over for slaughter.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Their slain shall be cast out,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18307C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18307C\"></sup>the stench of their corpses shall rise;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18307D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18307D\"></sup>the mountains shall flow with their blood.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18308E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18308E\"></sup>All the host of heaven shall rot away,and the skies roll up like a scroll.All their host shall fall,as leaves fall from the vine,like leaves falling from the fig tree.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>For my sword has drunk its fill in the heavens;behold, it descends for judgment upon <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18309F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18309F\"></sup>Edom,upon the people <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18309G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18309G\"></sup>I have devoted to destruction.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has a sword; it is sated with blood;it is gorged with fat,with the blood of lambs and goats,with the fat of the kidneys of rams.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18310H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18310H\"></sup>For the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has a sacrifice in Bozrah,a great slaughter in the land of Edom.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18311I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18311I\"></sup>Wild oxen shall <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18311J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18311J\"></sup>fall with them,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18311K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18311K\"></sup>young steers with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18311L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18311L\"></sup>the mighty bulls.Their land shall drink its fill of blood,and their soil shall be gorged with fat.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18312M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18312M\"></sup>For the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has a day of vengeance,a year of recompense for the cause of Zion.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18313N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18313N\"></sup>And the streams of Edom shall be turned into pitch,and her soil into sulfur;her land shall become burning pitch.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Night and day <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18314O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18314O\"></sup>it shall not be quenched;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18314P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18314P\"></sup>its smoke shall go up forever.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18314Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18314Q\"></sup>From generation to generation it shall lie waste;none shall pass through it forever and ever.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18315R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18315R\"></sup>But the hawk and the porcupine shall possess it,the owl and the raven shall dwell in it.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18315S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18315S\"></sup>He shall stretch the line of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18315T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18315T\"></sup>confusion over it,and the plumb line of emptiness.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Its nobles—there is no one there to call it a kingdom,and all its princes shall be nothing.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18317U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18317U\"></sup>Thorns shall grow over its strongholds,nettles and thistles in its fortresses.It shall be the haunt of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18317V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18317V\"></sup>jackals,an abode for ostriches.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18318W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18318W\"></sup>And wild animals shall meet with hyenas;the wild goat shall cry to his fellow;indeed, there the night bird settlesand finds for herself a resting place.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>There the owl nests and laysand hatches and gathers her young in her shadow;indeed, there <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18319X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18319X\"></sup>the hawks are gathered,each one with her mate.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Seek and read from the book of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>:Not one of these shall be missing;none shall be without her mate.For the mouth of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has commanded,and his Spirit has gathered them.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18321Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18321Y\"></sup>He has cast the lot for them;his hand has portioned it out to them with the line;they shall possess it forever;from generation to generation they shall dwell in it."
		},
		"35": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">35 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18322A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18322A\"></sup>The wilderness and the dry land shall be glad;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18322B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18322B\"></sup>the desert shall rejoice and blossom like the crocus;",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>it shall blossom abundantlyand rejoice with joy and singing.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18323C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18323C\"></sup>The glory of Lebanon shall be given to it,the majesty of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18323D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18323D\"></sup>Carmel and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18323E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18323E\"></sup>Sharon.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18323F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18323F\"></sup>They shall see the glory of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,the majesty of our God.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18324G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18324G\"></sup>Strengthen the weak hands,and make firm the feeble knees.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Say to those who have an anxious heart,“Be strong; fear not!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18325H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18325H\"></sup>Behold, your Godwill come with vengeance,with the recompense of God.He will come and save you.”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18326I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18326I\"></sup>Then the eyes of the blind shall be opened,and the ears of the deaf unstopped;",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18327J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18327J\"></sup>then shall the lame man leap like a deer,and the tongue of the mute sing for joy.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18327K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18327K\"></sup>For waters break forth in the wilderness,and streams in the desert;",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18328L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18328L\"></sup>the burning sand shall become a pool,and the thirsty ground springs of water;in the haunt of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18328M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18328M\"></sup>jackals, where they lie down,the grass shall become reeds and rushes.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18329N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18329N\"></sup>And a highway shall be there,and it shall be called the Way of Holiness;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18329O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18329O\"></sup>the unclean shall not pass over it.It shall belong to those who walk on the way;even if they are fools, they shall not go astray.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>No lion shall be there,nor shall any ravenous beast come up on it;they shall not be found there,but the redeemed shall walk there.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18331P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18331P\"></sup>And the ransomed of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> shall returnand come to Zion with singing;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18331Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18331Q\"></sup>everlasting joy shall be upon their heads;they shall obtain gladness and joy,and sorrow and sighing shall flee away."
		},
		"36": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">36 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18332A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18332A\"></sup>In the fourteenth year of King Hezekiah, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18332B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18332B\"></sup>Sennacherib king of Assyria came up against all the fortified cities of Judah and took them.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18333C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18333C\"></sup>And the king of Assyria sent the Rabshakeh from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18333D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18333D\"></sup>Lachish to King Hezekiah at Jerusalem, with a great army. And he stood <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18333E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18333E\"></sup>by the conduit of the upper pool on the highway to the Washer's Field.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And there came out to him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18334F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18334F\"></sup>Eliakim the son of Hilkiah, who was over the household, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18334G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18334G\"></sup>Shebna the secretary, and Joah the son of Asaph, the recorder.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>And the Rabshakeh said to them, “Say to Hezekiah, ‘Thus says the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18335H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18335H\"></sup>great king, the king of Assyria: On what do you rest this trust of yours?",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Do you think that mere words are strategy and power for war? In whom do you now trust, that you have rebelled against me?",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18337I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18337I\"></sup>Behold, you are trusting in Egypt, that broken reed of a staff, which will pierce the hand of any man who leans on it. Such is Pharaoh king of Egypt to all who trust in him.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>But if you say to me, “We trust in the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> our God,” is it not he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18338J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18338J\"></sup>whose high places and altars Hezekiah has removed, saying to Judah and to Jerusalem, “You shall worship before this altar”?",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Come now, make a wager with my master the king of Assyria: I will give you two thousand horses, if you are able on your part to set riders on them.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>How then can you repulse <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18340K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18340K\"></sup>a single captain among the least of my master's servants, when <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18340L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18340L\"></sup>you trust in Egypt for chariots and for horsemen?",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Moreover, is it without the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> that I have come up against this land to destroy it? <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18341M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18341M\"></sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to me, “Go up against this land and destroy it.”’”",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Then Eliakim, Shebna, and Joah said to the Rabshakeh, “Please speak to your servants <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18342N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18342N\"></sup>in Aramaic, for we understand it. Do not speak to us in the language of Judah within the hearing of the people who are on the wall.”",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>But the Rabshakeh said, “Has my master sent me to speak these words to your master and to you, and not to the men sitting on the wall, who are doomed with you to eat their own dung and drink their own urine?”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Then the Rabshakeh stood and called out in a loud voice in the language of Judah: “Hear the words of the great king, the king of Assyria!",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Thus says the king: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18345O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18345O\"></sup>‘Do not let Hezekiah deceive you, for he will not be able to deliver you.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Do not let Hezekiah make you trust in the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> by saying, “The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will surely deliver us. This city will not be given into the hand of the king of Assyria.”",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Do not listen to Hezekiah. For thus says the king of Assyria: Make your peace with me and come out to me. Then each one of you will eat of his own vine, and each one of his own fig tree, and each one of you will drink the water of his own cistern,",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>until <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18348P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18348P\"></sup>I come and take you away to a land like your own land, a land of grain and wine, a land of bread and vineyards.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Beware lest Hezekiah mislead you by saying, “The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will deliver us.” Has any of the gods of the nations delivered his land out of the hand of the king of Assyria?",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18350Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18350Q\"></sup>Where are the gods of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18350R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18350R\"></sup>Hamath and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18350S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18350S\"></sup>Arpad? Where are the gods of Sepharvaim? <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18350T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18350T\"></sup>Have they delivered Samaria out of my hand?",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18351U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18351U\"></sup>Who among all the gods of these lands have delivered their lands out of my hand, that the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> should deliver Jerusalem out of my hand?’”",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>But they were silent and answered him not a word, for the king's command was, “Do not answer him.”",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18353V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18353V\"></sup>Then Eliakim the son of Hilkiah, who was over the household, and Shebna the secretary, and Joah the son of Asaph, the recorder, came to Hezekiah with their clothes torn, and told him the words of the Rabshakeh."
		},
		"37": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">37 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18354A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18354A\"></sup>As soon as King Hezekiah heard it, he tore his clothes and covered himself with sackcloth and went into the house of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And he sent Eliakim, who was over the household, and Shebna the secretary, and the senior priests, covered with sackcloth, to the prophet <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18355B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18355B\"></sup>Isaiah the son of Amoz.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>They said to him, “Thus says Hezekiah, ‘This day is a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18356C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18356C\"></sup>day of distress, of rebuke, and of disgrace; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18356D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18356D\"></sup>children have come to the point of birth, and there is no strength to bring them forth.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18357E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18357E\"></sup>It may be that the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God will hear the words of the Rabshakeh, whom his master the king of Assyria has sent to mock the living God, and will rebuke the words that the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God has heard; therefore lift up your prayer for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18357F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18357F\"></sup>the remnant that is left.’”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>When the servants of King Hezekiah came to Isaiah,",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Isaiah said to them, “Say to your master, ‘Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>: Do not be afraid because of the words that you have heard, with which the young men of the king of Assyria have reviled me.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18360G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18360G\"></sup>I will put a spirit in him, so that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18360H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18360H\"></sup>he shall hear a rumor and return to his own land, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18360I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18360I\"></sup>I will make him fall by the sword in his own land.’”",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>The Rabshakeh returned, and found the king of Assyria fighting against <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18361J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18361J\"></sup>Libnah, for he had heard that the king had left <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18361K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18361K\"></sup>Lachish.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Now the king heard concerning Tirhakah king of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18362L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18362L\"></sup>Cush, “He has set out to fight against you.” And when he heard it, he sent messengers to Hezekiah, saying,",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“Thus shall you speak to Hezekiah king of Judah: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18363M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18363M\"></sup>‘Do not let your God in whom you trust deceive you by promising that Jerusalem will not be given into the hand of the king of Assyria.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Behold, you have heard what the kings of Assyria have done to all lands, devoting them to destruction. And shall you be delivered?",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18365N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18365N\"></sup>Have the gods of the nations delivered them, the nations that my fathers destroyed, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18365O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18365O\"></sup>Gozan, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18365P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18365P\"></sup>Haran, Rezeph, and the people of Eden who were in Telassar?",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18366Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18366Q\"></sup>Where is the king of Hamath, the king of Arpad, the king of the city of Sepharvaim, the king of Hena, or the king of Ivvah?’”",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Hezekiah received the letter from the hand of the messengers, and read it; and Hezekiah went up to the house of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, and spread it before the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>And Hezekiah prayed to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>:",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, God of Israel, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18369R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18369R\"></sup>enthroned above the cherubim, you are the God, you alone, of all the kingdoms of the earth; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18369S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18369S\"></sup>you have made heaven and earth.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18370T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18370T\"></sup>Incline your ear, O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, and hear; open your eyes, O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, and see; and hear <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18370U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18370U\"></sup>all the words of Sennacherib, which he has sent to mock the living God.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Truly, O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18371V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18371V\"></sup>the kings of Assyria have laid waste all the nations and their lands,",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>and have cast their gods into the fire. For they were no gods, but the work of men's hands, wood and stone. Therefore they were destroyed.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>So now, O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> our God, save us from his hand, that all the kingdoms of the earth may know that you alone are the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.”",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Then Isaiah the son of Amoz sent to Hezekiah, saying, “Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, the God of Israel: Because you have prayed to me concerning Sennacherib king of Assyria,",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>this is the word that the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has spoken concerning him:“‘She despises you, she scorns you—<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18375W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18375W\"></sup>the virgin daughter of Zion;she wags her head behind you—the daughter of Jerusalem.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>“‘Whom have you mocked and reviled?Against whom have you raised your voiceand lifted your eyes to the heights?Against <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18376X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18376X\"></sup>the Holy One of Israel!",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>By your servants you have mocked the Lord,and you have said, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18377Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18377Y\"></sup>With my many chariotsI have gone up the heights of the mountains,to the far recesses of Lebanon,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18377Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18377Z\"></sup>to cut down its tallest cedars,its choicest cypresses,to come to its remotest height,its most fruitful forest.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>I dug wellsand drank waters,to dry up with the sole of my footall <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18378AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18378AA\"></sup>the streams <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18378AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18378AB\"></sup>of Egypt.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18379AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18379AC\"></sup>“‘Have you not heardthat I determined it long ago?I planned from days of oldwhat now I bring to pass,that you should make fortified citiescrash into heaps of ruins,",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>while their inhabitants, shorn of strength,are dismayed and confounded,and have become like plants of the fieldand like tender grass,like grass on the housetops,blighted before it is grown.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>“‘I know your sitting downand your going out and coming in,and your raging against me.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18382AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18382AD\"></sup>Because you have raged against meand your complacency has come to my ears,I will put my hook in your noseand my bit in your mouth,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18382AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18382AE\"></sup>I will turn you back on the wayby which you came.’",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>“And this shall be the sign for you: this year you shall eat what grows of itself, and in the second year what springs from that. Then in the third year sow and reap, and plant vineyards, and eat their fruit.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>And the surviving remnant of the house of Judah <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18384AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18384AF\"></sup>shall again take root downward and bear fruit upward.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18385AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18385AG\"></sup>For out of Jerusalem shall go a remnant, and out of Mount Zion a band of survivors. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18385AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18385AH\"></sup>The zeal of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts will do this.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>“Therefore thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> concerning the king of Assyria: He shall not come into this city or shoot an arrow there or come before it with a shield or <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18386AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18386AI\"></sup>cast up a siege mound against it.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>By the way that he came, by the same he shall return, and he shall not come into this city, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18388AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18388AJ\"></sup>For I will defend this city to save it, for my own sake and for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18388AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18388AK\"></sup>the sake of my servant David.”",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18389AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18389AL\"></sup>And the angel of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> went out and struck down 185,000 in the camp of the Assyrians. And when people arose early in the morning, behold, these were all dead bodies.",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>Then Sennacherib king of Assyria departed and returned home and lived at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18390AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18390AM\"></sup>Nineveh.",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>And as he was worshiping in the house of Nisroch his god, Adrammelech and Sharezer, his sons, struck him down with the sword. And after they escaped into the land of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18391AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18391AN\"></sup>Ararat, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18391AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18391AO\"></sup>Esarhaddon his son reigned in his place."
		},
		"38": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">38 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18392A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18392A\"></sup>In those days Hezekiah became <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18392B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18392B\"></sup>sick and was at the point of death. And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18392C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18392C\"></sup>Isaiah the prophet the son of Amoz came to him, and said to him, “Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>: Set your house in order, for you shall die, you shall not recover.”",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Then Hezekiah turned his face to the wall and prayed to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>and said, “Please, O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, remember how <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18394D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18394D\"></sup>I have walked before you in faithfulness and with a whole heart, and have done what is good in your sight.” And Hezekiah wept bitterly.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Then the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to Isaiah:",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“Go and say to Hezekiah, Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, the God of David your father: I have heard your prayer; I have seen your tears. Behold, I will add <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18396E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18396E\"></sup>fifteen years to your life.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18397F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18397F\"></sup>I will deliver you and this city out of the hand of the king of Assyria, and will defend this city.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“This shall be the sign to you from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, that the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will do this thing that he has promised:",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18399G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18399G\"></sup>Behold, I will make the shadow cast by the declining sun on the dial of Ahaz turn back ten steps.” So the sun turned back on the dial the ten steps by which it had declined.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>A writing of Hezekiah king of Judah, after he had been sick and had recovered from his sickness:",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>I said, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18401H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18401H\"></sup>In the middle of my daysI must depart;I am consigned to the gates of Sheolfor the rest of my years.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>I said, I shall not see the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18402I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18402I\"></sup>in the land of the living;I shall look on man no moreamong the inhabitants of the world.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>My dwelling is plucked up and removed from me<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18403J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18403J\"></sup>like a shepherd's tent;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18403K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18403K\"></sup>like a weaver <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18403L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18403L\"></sup>I have rolled up my life;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18403M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18403M\"></sup>he cuts me off from the loom;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18403N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18403N\"></sup>from day to night you bring me to an end;",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><span class=\"indent-1-breaks\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18404O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18404O\"></sup>I calmed myself until morning;like a lion <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18404P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18404P\"></sup>he breaks all my bones;from day to night you bring me to an end.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18405Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18405Q\"></sup>a swallow or a crane I chirp;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18405R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18405R\"></sup>I moan like a dove.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18405S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18405S\"></sup>My eyes are weary with looking upward.O Lord, I am oppressed; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18405T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18405T\"></sup>be my pledge of safety!",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>What shall I say? For he has spoken to me,and he himself has done it.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18406U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18406U\"></sup>I walk slowly all my yearsbecause of the bitterness of my soul.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18407V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18407V\"></sup>O Lord, by these things men live,and in all these is the life of my spirit.Oh restore me to health and make me live!",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18408W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18408W\"></sup>Behold, it was for my welfarethat I had great bitterness;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18408X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18408X\"></sup>but in love you have delivered my lifefrom the pit of destruction,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18408Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18408Y\"></sup>for you have cast all my sinsbehind your back.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18409Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18409Z\"></sup>For Sheol does not thank you;death does not praise you;those who go down to the pit do not hopefor your faithfulness.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>The living, the living, he thanks you,as I do this day;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18410AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18410AA\"></sup>the father makes known to the childrenyour faithfulness.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will save me,and we will play my music on stringed instrumentsall the days of our lives,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18411AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18411AB\"></sup>at the house of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18412AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18412AC\"></sup>Now Isaiah had said, “Let them take a cake of figs and apply it to the boil, that he may recover.”",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Hezekiah also had said, “What is the sign that I shall go up to the house of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>?”"
		},
		"39": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">39 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18414A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18414A\"></sup>At that time Merodach-baladan the son of Baladan, king of Babylon, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18414B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18414B\"></sup>sent envoys with letters and a present to Hezekiah, for he heard that he had been sick and had recovered.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And Hezekiah welcomed them gladly. And he showed them his treasure house, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18415C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18415C\"></sup>the silver, the gold, the spices, the precious oil, his whole armory, all that was found in his storehouses. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18415D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18415D\"></sup>There was nothing in his house or in all his realm that Hezekiah did not show them.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Then Isaiah the prophet came to King Hezekiah, and said to him, “What did these men say? And from where did they come to you?” Hezekiah said, “They have come to me from a far country, from Babylon.”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>He said, “What have they seen in your house?” Hezekiah answered, “They have seen all that is in my house. There is nothing in my storehouses that I did not show them.”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Then Isaiah said to Hezekiah, “Hear the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts:",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18419E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18419E\"></sup>Behold, the days are coming, when all that is in your house, and that which your fathers have stored up till this day, shall be carried to Babylon. Nothing shall be left, says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18420F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18420F\"></sup>And some of your own sons, who will come from you, whom you will father, shall be taken away, and they shall be eunuchs in the palace of the king of Babylon.”",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Then Hezekiah said to Isaiah, “The word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> that you have spoken is good.” For he thought, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18421G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18421G\"></sup>“There will be peace and security in my days.”"
		},
		"40": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">40 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18422A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18422A\"></sup>Comfort, comfort my people, says your God.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18423B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18423B\"></sup>Speak tenderly to Jerusalem,and cry to herthat <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18423C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18423C\"></sup>her warfare is ended,that her iniquity is pardoned,that she has received from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>'s handdouble for all her sins.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18424D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18424D\"></sup>A voice cries:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18424E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18424E\"></sup>“In the wilderness prepare the way of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18424F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18424F\"></sup>make straight in the desert a highway for our God.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18425G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18425G\"></sup>Every valley shall be lifted up,and every mountain and hill be made low;the uneven ground shall become level,and the rough places a plain.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18426H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18426H\"></sup>And the glory of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> shall be revealed,and all flesh shall see it together,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18426I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18426I\"></sup>for the mouth of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has spoken.”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>A voice says, “Cry!”And I said, “What shall I cry?”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18427J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18427J\"></sup>All flesh is grass,and all its beauty is like the flower of the field.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>The grass withers, the flower fadeswhen the breath of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> blows on it;surely the people are grass.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18429K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18429K\"></sup>The grass withers, the flower fades,but the word of our God will stand forever.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Go on up to a high mountain,O Zion, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18430L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18430L\"></sup>herald of good news;lift up your voice with strength,O Jerusalem, herald of good news;lift it up, fear not;say to the cities of Judah,“Behold your God!”",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18431M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18431M\"></sup>Behold, the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span> comes with might,and his arm rules for him;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18431N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18431N\"></sup>behold, his reward is with him,and his recompense before him.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18432O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18432O\"></sup>He will tend his flock like a shepherd;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18432P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18432P\"></sup>he will gather the lambs in his arms;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18432Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18432Q\"></sup>he will carry them in his bosom,and gently lead those that are with young.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18433R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18433R\"></sup>Who has measured the waters in the hollow of his handand marked off the heavens with a span,enclosed the dust of the earth in a measureand weighed the mountains in scalesand the hills in a balance?",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18434S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18434S\"></sup>Who has measured the Spirit of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,or what man shows him his counsel?",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Whom did he consult,and who made him understand?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18435T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18435T\"></sup>Who taught him the path of justice,and taught him knowledge,and showed him the way of understanding?",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Behold, the nations are like a drop from a bucket,and are accounted <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18436U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18436U\"></sup>as the dust on the scales;behold, he takes up <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18436V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18436V\"></sup>the coastlands like fine dust.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Lebanon would not suffice for fuel,nor are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18437W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18437W\"></sup>its beasts enough for a burnt offering.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18438X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18438X\"></sup>All the nations are as nothing before him,they are accounted by him as less than nothing and emptiness.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18439Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18439Y\"></sup>To whom then will you liken God,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18439Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18439Z\"></sup>or what likeness compare with him?",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18440AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18440AA\"></sup>An idol! A craftsman casts it,and a goldsmith overlays it with goldand casts for it silver chains.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18441AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18441AB\"></sup>He who is too impoverished for an offeringchooses wood that will not rot;he seeks out a skillful craftsmanto set up an idol that will not move.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18442AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18442AC\"></sup>Do you not know? Do you not hear?Has it not been told you from the beginning?Have you not understood from the foundations of the earth?",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>It is he who sits above the circle of the earth,and its inhabitants are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18443AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18443AD\"></sup>like grasshoppers;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18443AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18443AE\"></sup>who stretches out the heavens like a curtain,and spreads them like a tent to dwell in;",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18444AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18444AF\"></sup>who brings princes to nothing,and makes the rulers of the earth as emptiness.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Scarcely are they planted, scarcely sown,scarcely has their stem taken root in the earth,when he blows on them, and they wither,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18445AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18445AG\"></sup>and the tempest carries them off like stubble.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18446AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18446AH\"></sup>To whom then will you compare me,that I should be like him? says the Holy One.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>Lift up your eyes on high and see:who created these?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18447AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18447AI\"></sup>He who brings out their host by number,calling them all by name;by the greatness of his mightand because he is strong in power,not one is missing.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>Why do you say, O Jacob,and speak, O Israel,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18448AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18448AJ\"></sup>“My way is hidden from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18448AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18448AK\"></sup>and my right is disregarded by my God”?",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>Have you not known? Have you not heard?The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18449AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18449AL\"></sup>the everlasting God,the Creator of the ends of the earth.He does not faint or grow weary;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18449AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18449AM\"></sup>his understanding is unsearchable.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>He gives power to the faint,and to him who has no might he increases strength.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>Even youths shall faint and be weary,and young men shall fall exhausted;",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18452AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18452AN\"></sup>they who wait for the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> shall renew their strength;they shall mount up with wings <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18452AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18452AO\"></sup>like eagles;they shall run and not be weary;they shall walk and not faint."
		},
		"41": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">41 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18453A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18453A\"></sup>Listen to me in silence, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18453B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18453B\"></sup>O coastlands;let the peoples renew their strength;let them approach, then let them speak;let us together draw near for judgment.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18454C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18454C\"></sup>Who stirred up one from the eastwhom victory meets at every <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18454D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18454D\"></sup>step?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18454E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18454E\"></sup>He gives up nations before him,so that he tramples kings underfoot;he makes them like dust with his sword,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18454F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18454F\"></sup>like driven stubble with his bow.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>He pursues them and passes on safely,by paths his feet have not trod.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18456G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18456G\"></sup>Who has performed and done this,calling the generations from the beginning?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18456H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18456H\"></sup>I, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, the first,and with the last; I am he.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18457I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18457I\"></sup>The coastlands have seen and are afraid;the ends of the earth tremble;they have drawn near and come.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Everyone helps his neighborand says to his brother, “Be strong!”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18459J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18459J\"></sup>The craftsman strengthens the goldsmith,and he who smooths with the hammer him who strikes the anvil,saying of the soldering, “It is good”;and they strengthen it with nails <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18459K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18459K\"></sup>so that it cannot be moved.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>But you, Israel, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18460L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18460L\"></sup>my servant,Jacob, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18460M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18460M\"></sup>whom I have chosen,the offspring of Abraham, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18460N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18460N\"></sup>my friend;",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>you whom I took from the ends of the earth,and called <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18461O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18461O\"></sup>from its farthest corners,saying to you, “You are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18461P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18461P\"></sup>my servant,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18461Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18461Q\"></sup>I have chosen you and not cast you off”;",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>fear not, for I am with you;be not dismayed, for I am your God;I will strengthen you, I will help you,I will uphold you with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18462R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18462R\"></sup>my righteous right hand.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18463S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18463S\"></sup>Behold, all who are incensed against youshall be put to shame and confounded;those who strive against youshall be as nothing and shall perish.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18464T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18464T\"></sup>You shall seek those who contend with you,but you shall not find them;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18464U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18464U\"></sup>those who war against youshall be as nothing at all.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>For I, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God,hold your right hand;it is I who say to you, “Fear not,I am the one who helps you.”",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Fear not, you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18466V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18466V\"></sup>worm Jacob,you men of Israel!I am the one who helps you, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>;your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18466W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18466W\"></sup>Redeemer is the Holy One of Israel.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18467X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18467X\"></sup>Behold, I make of you a threshing sledge,new, sharp, and having teeth;you shall thresh <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18467Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18467Y\"></sup>the mountains and crush them,and you shall make the hills like chaff;",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18468Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18468Z\"></sup>you shall winnow them, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18468AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18468AA\"></sup>the wind shall carry them away,and the tempest shall scatter them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18468AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18468AB\"></sup>And you shall rejoice in the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>;in the Holy One of Israel you shall glory.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18469AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18469AC\"></sup>When the poor and needy seek water,and there is none,and their tongue is parched with thirst,I the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will answer them;I the God of Israel will not forsake them.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18470AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18470AD\"></sup>I will open rivers on the bare heights,and fountains in the midst of the valleys.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18470AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18470AE\"></sup>I will make the wilderness a pool of water,and the dry land springs of water.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18471AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18471AF\"></sup>I will put in the wilderness the cedar,the acacia, the myrtle, and the olive.I will set in the desert <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18471AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18471AG\"></sup>the cypress,the plane and the pine together,",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>that they may see and know,may consider and understand together,that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18472AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18472AH\"></sup>the hand of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has done this,the Holy One of Israel has created it.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Set forth your case, says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>;bring your proofs, says the King of Jacob.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Let them bring them, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18474AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18474AI\"></sup>tell uswhat is to happen.Tell us the former things, what they are,that we may consider them,that we may know their outcome;or declare to us the things to come.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18475AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18475AJ\"></sup>Tell us what is to come hereafter,that we may know that you are gods;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18475AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18475AK\"></sup>do good, or do harm,that we may be dismayed and terrified.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18476AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18476AL\"></sup>you are nothing,and your work is less than nothing;an abomination is he who chooses you.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18477AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18477AM\"></sup>I stirred up one from the north, and he has come,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18477AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18477AN\"></sup>from the rising of the sun, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18477AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18477AO\"></sup>and he shall call upon my name;he shall trample on rulers as on mortar,as the potter treads clay.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18478AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18478AP\"></sup>Who declared it from the beginning, that we might know,and beforehand, that we might say, “He is right”?There was none who declared it, none who proclaimed,none who heard your words.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18479AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18479AQ\"></sup>I was the first to say to Zion, “Behold, here they are!”and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18479AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18479AR\"></sup>I give to Jerusalem a herald of good news.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18480AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18480AS\"></sup>But when I look, there is no one;among these there is no counselorwho, when I ask, gives an answer.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18481AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18481AT\"></sup>Behold, they are all a delusion;their works are nothing;their metal images are empty wind."
		},
		"42": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">42 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18482A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18482A\"></sup>Behold <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18482B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18482B\"></sup>my servant, whom I uphold,my chosen, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18482C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18482C\"></sup>in whom my soul delights;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18482D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18482D\"></sup>I have put my Spirit upon him;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18482E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18482E\"></sup>he will bring forth justice to the nations.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>He will not cry aloud or lift up his voice,or make it heard in the street;",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18484F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18484F\"></sup>a bruised reed he will not break,and a faintly burning wick he will not quench;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18484G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18484G\"></sup>he will faithfully bring forth justice.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>He will not grow faint or be discouragedtill he has established justice in the earth;and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18485H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18485H\"></sup>the coastlands wait for his law.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Thus says God, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,who created the heavens <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18486I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18486I\"></sup>and stretched them out,who spread out the earth and what comes from it,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18486J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18486J\"></sup>who gives breath to the people on itand spirit to those who walk in it:",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18487K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18487K\"></sup>I have called you in righteousness;I will take you by the hand and keep you;I will give you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18487L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18487L\"></sup>as a covenant for the people,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18487M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18487M\"></sup>a light for the nations,",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><span class=\"indent-1-breaks\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18488N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18488N\"></sup>to open the eyes that are blind,to bring out the prisoners from the dungeon,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18488O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18488O\"></sup>from the prison those who sit in darkness.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>; that is my name;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18489P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18489P\"></sup>my glory I give to no other,nor my praise to carved idols.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Behold, the former things have come to pass,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18490Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18490Q\"></sup>and new things I now declare;before they spring forthI tell you of them.”",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18491R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18491R\"></sup>Sing to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> a new song,his praise from the end of the earth,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18491S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18491S\"></sup>you who go down to the sea, and all that fills it,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18491T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18491T\"></sup>the coastlands and their inhabitants.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Let the desert and its cities lift up their voice,the villages that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18492U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18492U\"></sup>Kedar inhabits;let the habitants of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18492V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18492V\"></sup>Sela sing for joy,let them shout from the top of the mountains.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Let them give glory to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,and declare his praise in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18493W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18493W\"></sup>the coastlands.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18494X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18494X\"></sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> goes out like a mighty man,like a man of war <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18494Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18494Y\"></sup>he stirs up his zeal;he cries out, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18494Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18494Z\"></sup>he shouts aloud,he shows himself mighty against his foes.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>For a long time I have held my peace;I have kept still and restrained myself;now I will cry out <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18495AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18495AA\"></sup>like a woman in labor;I will gasp and pant.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18496AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18496AB\"></sup>I will lay waste mountains and hills,and dry up all their vegetation;I will turn the rivers into islands,and dry up the pools.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18497AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18497AC\"></sup>And I will lead the blindin a way that they do not know,in paths that they have not knownI will guide them.I will turn the darkness before them into light,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18497AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18497AD\"></sup>the rough places into level ground.These are the things I do,and I do not forsake them.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18498AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18498AE\"></sup>They are turned back and utterly put to shame,who trust in carved idols,who say to metal images,“You are our gods.”",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Hear, you deaf,and look, you blind, that you may see!",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Who is blind but my servant,or deaf as my messenger whom I send?Who is blind as my dedicated one,or blind as the servant of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>?",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18501AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18501AF\"></sup>He sees many things, but does not observe them;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18501AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18501AG\"></sup>his ears are open, but he does not hear.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> was pleased, for his righteousness' sake,to magnify his law and make it glorious.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>But this is a people plundered and looted;they are all of them trapped in holes<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18503AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18503AH\"></sup>and hidden in prisons;they have become plunder with none to rescue,spoil with none to say, “Restore!”",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Who among you will give ear to this,will attend and listen for the time to come?",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Who gave up Jacob to the looter,and Israel to the plunderers?Was it not the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, against whom we have sinned,in whose ways they would not walk,and whose law they would not obey?",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>So he poured on him the heat of his angerand the might of battle;it set him on fire all around, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18506AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18506AI\"></sup>but he did not understand;it burned him up, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18506AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18506AJ\"></sup>but he did not take it to heart."
		},
		"43": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">43 </span>But now thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18507A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18507A\"></sup>he who created you, O Jacob,he who formed you, O Israel:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18507B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18507B\"></sup>“Fear not, for I have redeemed you;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18507C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18507C\"></sup>I have called you by name, you are mine.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18508D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18508D\"></sup>When you pass through the waters, I will be with you;and through the rivers, they shall not overwhelm you;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18508E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18508E\"></sup>when you walk through fire <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18508F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18508F\"></sup>you shall not be burned,and the flame shall not consume you.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18509G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18509G\"></sup>I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God,the Holy One of Israel, your Savior.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18509H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18509H\"></sup>I give Egypt as your ransom,Cush and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18509I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18509I\"></sup>Seba in exchange for you.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Because you are precious in my eyes,and honored, and I love you,I give men in return for you,peoples in exchange for your life.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18511J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18511J\"></sup>Fear not, for I am with you;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18511K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18511K\"></sup>I will bring your offspring from the east,and from the west I will gather you.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>I will say to the north, Give up,and to the south, Do not withhold;bring <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18512L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18512L\"></sup>my sons from afarand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18512M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18512M\"></sup>my daughters from the end of the earth,",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>everyone who is called by my name,whom I created for my glory,whom I formed and made.”",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Bring out <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18514N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18514N\"></sup>the people who are blind, yet have eyes,who are deaf, yet have ears!",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18515O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18515O\"></sup>All the nations gather together,and the peoples assemble.Who among them can declare this,and show us the former things?Let them bring their witnesses to prove them right,and let them hear and say, It is true.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18516P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18516P\"></sup>“You are my witnesses,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,“and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18516Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18516Q\"></sup>my servant whom I have chosen,that you may know and believe meand understand that I am he.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18516R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18516R\"></sup>Before me no god was formed,nor shall there be any after me.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18517S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18517S\"></sup>I, I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,and besides me there is no savior.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>I declared and saved and proclaimed,when there was no strange god among you;and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18518T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18518T\"></sup>you are my witnesses,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, “and I am God.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Also <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18519U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18519U\"></sup>henceforth I am he;there is none who can deliver from my hand;I work, and who can turn it back?”",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,your Redeemer, the Holy One of Israel:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18520V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18520V\"></sup>“For your sake I send to Babylonand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18520W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18520W\"></sup>bring them all down as fugitives,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18520X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18520X\"></sup>even the Chaldeans, in the ships in which they rejoice.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, your Holy One,the Creator of Israel, your King.”",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18522Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18522Y\"></sup>who makes a way in the sea,a path in the mighty waters,",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18523Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18523Z\"></sup>brings forth chariot and horse,army and warrior;they lie down, they cannot rise,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18523AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18523AA\"></sup>they are extinguished, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18523AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18523AB\"></sup>quenched like a wick:",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18524AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18524AC\"></sup>“Remember not the former things,nor consider the things of old.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18525AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18525AD\"></sup>Behold, I am doing a new thing;now it springs forth, do you not perceive it?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18525AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18525AE\"></sup>I will make a way in the wilderness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18525AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18525AF\"></sup>and rivers in the desert.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>The wild beasts will honor me,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18526AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18526AG\"></sup>the jackals and the ostriches,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18526AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18526AH\"></sup>for I give water in the wilderness,rivers in the desert,to give drink to my chosen people,",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><span class=\"indent-1-breaks\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>the people whom I formed for myself<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18527AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18527AI\"></sup>that they might declare my praise.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>“Yet you did not call upon me, O Jacob;but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18528AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18528AJ\"></sup>you have been weary of me, O Israel!",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18529AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18529AK\"></sup>You have not brought me your sheep for burnt offerings,or honored me with your sacrifices.I have not burdened you with offerings,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18529AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18529AL\"></sup>or wearied you with frankincense.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>You have not bought me sweet cane with money,or satisfied me with the fat of your sacrifices.But you have burdened me with your sins;you have wearied me with your iniquities.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>“I, I am he<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18531AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18531AM\"></sup>who blots out <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18531AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18531AN\"></sup>your transgressions for my own sake,and I will not remember your sins.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>Put me in remembrance; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18532AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18532AO\"></sup>let us argue together;set forth your case, that you may be proved right.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18533AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18533AP\"></sup>Your first father sinned,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18533AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18533AQ\"></sup>your mediators transgressed against me.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>Therefore <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18534AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18534AR\"></sup>I will profane the princes of the sanctuary,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18534AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18534AS\"></sup>deliver Jacob to utter destructionand Israel to reviling."
		},
		"44": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">44 </span>“But now hear, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18535A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18535A\"></sup>O Jacob my servant,Israel whom I have chosen!",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> who made you,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18536B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18536B\"></sup>who formed you from the womb and will help you:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18536C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18536C\"></sup>Fear not, O Jacob my servant,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18536D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18536D\"></sup>Jeshurun whom I have chosen.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18537E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18537E\"></sup>For I will pour water on the thirsty land,and streams on the dry ground;I will pour my Spirit upon your offspring,and my blessing on your descendants.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>They shall spring up among the grass<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18538F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18538F\"></sup>like willows by flowing streams.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18539G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18539G\"></sup>This one will say, ‘I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>'s,’another will call on the name of Jacob,and another will write on his hand, ‘The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>'s,’and name himself by the name of Israel.”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, the King of Israeland <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18540H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18540H\"></sup>his Redeemer, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18540I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18540I\"></sup>“I am the first and I am the last;besides me there is no god.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18541J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18541J\"></sup>Who is like me? Let him proclaim it.Let him declare and set it before me,since I appointed an ancient people.Let them declare what is to come, and what will happen.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Fear not, nor be afraid;have I not told you from of old and declared it?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18542K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18542K\"></sup>And you are my witnesses!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18542L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18542L\"></sup>Is there a God besides me?There is no <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18542M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18542M\"></sup>Rock; I know not any.”",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18543N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18543N\"></sup>All who fashion idols are nothing, and the things they delight in do not profit. Their witnesses neither see nor know, that they may be put to shame.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18544O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18544O\"></sup>Who fashions a god or casts an idol that is profitable for nothing?",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18545P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18545P\"></sup>Behold, all his companions shall be put to shame, and the craftsmen are only human. Let them all assemble, let them stand forth. They shall be terrified; they shall be put to shame together.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18546Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18546Q\"></sup>The ironsmith takes a cutting tool and works it over the coals. He fashions it with hammers and works it with his strong arm. He becomes hungry, and his strength fails; he drinks no water and is faint.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>The carpenter stretches a line; he marks it out with a pencil. He shapes it with planes and marks it with a compass. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18547R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18547R\"></sup>He shapes it into the figure of a man, with the beauty of a man, to dwell in a house.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18548S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18548S\"></sup>He cuts down cedars, or he chooses a cypress tree or an oak and lets it grow strong among the trees of the forest. He plants a cedar and the rain nourishes it.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Then it becomes fuel for a man. He takes a part of it and warms himself; he kindles a fire and bakes bread. Also he makes a god and worships it; he makes it an idol and falls down before it.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Half of it he burns in the fire. Over the half he eats meat; he roasts it and is satisfied. Also he warms himself and says, “Aha, I am warm, I have seen the fire!”",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>And the rest of it he makes into a god, his idol, and falls down to it and worships it. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18551T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18551T\"></sup>He prays to it and says, “Deliver me, for you are my god!”",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>They know not, nor do they discern, for he has shut their eyes, so that they cannot see, and their hearts, so that they cannot understand.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>No one considers, nor is there knowledge or discernment to say, “Half of it I burned in the fire; I also baked bread on its coals; I roasted meat and have eaten. And shall I make the rest of it an <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18553U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18553U\"></sup>abomination? Shall I fall down before a block of wood?”",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18554V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18554V\"></sup>He feeds on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18554W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18554W\"></sup>ashes; a deluded heart has led him astray, and he cannot deliver himself or say, “Is there not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18554X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18554X\"></sup>a lie in my right hand?”",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Remember these things, O Jacob,and Israel, for you are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18555Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18555Y\"></sup>my servant;I formed you; you are my servant;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18555Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18555Z\"></sup>O Israel, you will not be forgotten by me.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18556AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18556AA\"></sup>I have blotted out your transgressions like a cloudand your sins like mist;return to me, for I have redeemed you.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18557AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18557AB\"></sup>Sing, O heavens, for the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has done it;shout, O <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18557AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18557AC\"></sup>depths of the earth;break forth into singing, O mountains,O forest, and every tree in it!For the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has redeemed Jacob,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18557AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18557AD\"></sup>and will be glorified in Israel.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18558AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18558AE\"></sup>your Redeemer,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18558AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18558AF\"></sup>who formed you from the womb:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18558AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18558AG\"></sup>“I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, who made all things,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18558AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18558AH\"></sup>who alone stretched out the heavens,who spread out the earth by myself,",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>who frustrates the signs of liarsand makes fools of diviners,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18559AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18559AI\"></sup>who turns wise men backand makes their knowledge foolish,",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18560AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18560AJ\"></sup>who confirms the word of his servantand fulfills the counsel of his messengers,who says of Jerusalem, ‘She shall be inhabited,’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18560AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18560AK\"></sup>and of the cities of Judah, ‘They shall be built,and I will raise up their ruins’;",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18561AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18561AL\"></sup>who says to the deep, ‘Be dry;I will dry up your rivers’;",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>who says of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18562AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18562AM\"></sup>Cyrus, ‘He is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18562AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18562AN\"></sup>my shepherd,and he shall fulfill all my purpose’;saying of Jerusalem, ‘She shall be built,’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18562AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18562AO\"></sup>and of the temple, ‘Your foundation shall be laid.’”"
		},
		"45": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">45 </span>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18563A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18563A\"></sup>his anointed, to Cyrus,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18563B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18563B\"></sup>whose right hand I have grasped,to subdue nations before himand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18563C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18563C\"></sup>to loose the belts of kings,to open doors before himthat gates may not be closed:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“I will go before youand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18564D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18564D\"></sup>level the exalted places,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18564E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18564E\"></sup>I will break in pieces the doors of bronzeand cut through the bars of iron,",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18565F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18565F\"></sup>I will give you the treasures of darknessand the hoards in secret places,that you may know that it is I, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,the God of Israel, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18565G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18565G\"></sup>who call you by your name.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>For the sake of my servant Jacob,and Israel my chosen,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18566H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18566H\"></sup>I call you by your name,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18566I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18566I\"></sup>I name you, though you do not know me.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18567J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18567J\"></sup>I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, and there is no other,besides me there is no God;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18567K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18567K\"></sup>I equip you, though you do not know me,",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18568L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18568L\"></sup>that people may know, from the rising of the sunand from the west, that there is none besides me;I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, and there is no other.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>I form light and create darkness;I make well-being and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18569M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18569M\"></sup>create calamity;I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, who does all these things.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18570N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18570N\"></sup>“Shower, O heavens, from above,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18570O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18570O\"></sup>let the clouds rain down righteousness;let the earth open, that salvation and righteousness may bear fruit;let the earth cause them both to sprout;I the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> have created it.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18571P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18571P\"></sup>“Woe to him who strives with him who formed him,a pot among earthen pots!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18571Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18571Q\"></sup>Does the clay say to him who forms it, ‘What are you making?’or ‘Your work has no handles’?",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Woe to him who says to a father, ‘What are you begetting?’or to a woman, ‘With what are you in labor?’”",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Thus says <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18573R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18573R\"></sup>the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,the Holy One of Israel, and the one who formed him:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18573S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18573S\"></sup>“Ask me of things to come;will you command me <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18573T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18573T\"></sup>concerning my children and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18573U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18573U\"></sup>the work of my hands?",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18574V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18574V\"></sup>I made the earthand created man on it;it was my hands <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18574W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18574W\"></sup>that stretched out the heavens,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18574X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18574X\"></sup>I commanded all their host.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18575Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18575Y\"></sup>I have stirred him up in righteousness,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18575Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18575Z\"></sup>and I will make all his ways level;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18575AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18575AA\"></sup>he shall build my city<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18575AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18575AB\"></sup>and set my exiles free,not for price or reward,”says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18576AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18576AC\"></sup>“The wealth of Egypt and the merchandise of Cush,and the Sabeans, men of stature,shall come over to you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18576AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18576AD\"></sup>and be yours;they shall follow you;they shall come over in chains and bow down to you.They will plead with you, saying:‘Surely God is in you, and there is no other,no god besides him.’”",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18577AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18577AE\"></sup>Truly, you are a God who hides himself,O God of Israel, the Savior.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18578AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18578AF\"></sup>All of them are put to shame and confounded;the makers of idols go in confusion together.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>But Israel is saved by the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>with everlasting salvation;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18579AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18579AG\"></sup>you shall not be put to shame or confoundedto all eternity.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18580AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18580AH\"></sup>For thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,who created the heavens(he is God!),who formed the earth and made it(he established it;he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18580AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18580AI\"></sup>did not create it empty,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18580AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18580AJ\"></sup>he formed it to be inhabited!):“I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, and there is no other.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18581AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18581AK\"></sup>I did not speak in secret,in a land of darkness;I did not say to the offspring of Jacob,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18581AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18581AL\"></sup>‘Seek me in vain.’I the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> speak <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18581AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18581AM\"></sup>the truth;I declare what is right.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18582AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18582AN\"></sup>“Assemble yourselves and come;draw near together,you survivors of the nations!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18582AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18582AO\"></sup>They have no knowledgewho <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18582AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18582AP\"></sup>carry about their wooden idols,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18582AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18582AQ\"></sup>and keep on praying to a godthat cannot save.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18583AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18583AR\"></sup>Declare and present your case;let them take counsel together!Who told this long ago?Who declared it of old?Was it not I, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>?And there is no other god besides me,a righteous God <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18583AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18583AS\"></sup>and a Savior;there is none besides me.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>“Turn to me and be saved,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18584AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18584AT\"></sup>all the ends of the earth!For I am God, and there is no other.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18585AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18585AU\"></sup>By myself I have sworn;from my mouth has gone out in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18585AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18585AV\"></sup>righteousnessa word that shall not return:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18585AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18585AW\"></sup>‘To me every knee shall bow,every tongue shall swear allegiance.’",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18586AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18586AX\"></sup>“Only in the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, it shall be said of me,are righteousness and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18586AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18586AY\"></sup>strength;to him shall come and be ashamed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18586AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18586AZ\"></sup>all who were incensed against him.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>In the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> all the offspring of Israelshall be justified and shall glory.”"
		},
		"46": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">46 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18588A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18588A\"></sup>Bel bows down; Nebo stoops;their idols are on beasts and livestock;these things you carry are borneas burdens on weary beasts.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>They stoop; they bow down together;they cannot save the burden,but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18589B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18589B\"></sup>themselves go into captivity.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“Listen to me, O house of Jacob,all the remnant of the house of Israel,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18590C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18590C\"></sup>who have been borne by me from before your birth,carried from the womb;",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18591D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18591D\"></sup>even to your old age I am he,and to gray hairs I will carry you.I have made, and I will bear;I will carry and will save.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18592E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18592E\"></sup>“To whom will you liken me and make me equal,and compare me, that we may be alike?",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18593F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18593F\"></sup>Those who lavish gold from the purse,and weigh out silver in the scales,hire a goldsmith, and he makes it into a god;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18593G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18593G\"></sup>then they fall down and worship!",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18594H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18594H\"></sup>They lift it to their shoulders, they carry it,they set it in its place, and it stands there;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18594I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18594I\"></sup>it cannot move from its place.If one cries to it, it does not answeror save him from his trouble.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“Remember this and stand firm,recall it to mind, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18595J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18595J\"></sup>you transgressors,",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><span class=\"indent-1-breaks\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>remember the former things of old;for I am God, and there is no other;I am God, and there is none like me,",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18597K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18597K\"></sup>declaring the end from the beginningand from ancient times things not yet done,saying, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18597L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18597L\"></sup>‘My counsel shall stand,and I will accomplish all my purpose,’",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18598M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18598M\"></sup>calling a bird of prey from the east,the man of my counsel from a far country.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18598N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18598N\"></sup>I have spoken, and I will bring it to pass;I have purposed, and I will do it.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“Listen to me, you stubborn of heart,you who are far from righteousness:",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18600O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18600O\"></sup>I bring near my righteousness; it is not far off,and my salvation will not delay;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18600P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18600P\"></sup>I will put salvation in Zion,for Israel my glory.”"
		},
		"47": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">47 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18601A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18601A\"></sup>Come down and sit in the dust,O virgin <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18601B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18601B\"></sup>daughter of Babylon;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18601C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18601C\"></sup>sit on the ground without a throne,O daughter of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18601D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18601D\"></sup>the Chaldeans!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18601E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18601E\"></sup>For you shall no more be calledtender and delicate.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Take the millstones and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18602F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18602F\"></sup>grind flour,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18602G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18602G\"></sup>put off your veil,strip off your robe, uncover your legs,pass through the rivers.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Your nakedness shall be uncovered,and your disgrace shall be seen.I will take vengeance,and I will spare no one.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18604H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18604H\"></sup>Our Redeemer—the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts is his name—is the Holy One of Israel.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18605I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18605I\"></sup>Sit in silence, and go into darkness,O daughter of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18605J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18605J\"></sup>the Chaldeans;for you shall no more be called<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18605K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18605K\"></sup>the mistress of kingdoms.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18606L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18606L\"></sup>I was angry with my people;I profaned my heritage;I gave them into your hand;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18606M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18606M\"></sup>you showed them no mercy;on the aged you made your yoke exceedingly heavy.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>You said, “I shall be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18607N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18607N\"></sup>mistress forever,”so that you did not lay these things to heartor remember their end.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Now therefore hear this, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18608O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18608O\"></sup>you lover of pleasures,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18608P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18608P\"></sup>who sit securely,who say in your heart,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18608Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18608Q\"></sup>“I am, and there is no one besides me;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18608R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18608R\"></sup>I shall not sit as a widowor know the loss of children”:",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18609S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18609S\"></sup>These two things shall come to youin a moment, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18609T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18609T\"></sup>in one day;the loss of children and widowhoodshall come upon you in full measure,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18609U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18609U\"></sup>in spite of your many sorceriesand the great power of your enchantments.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>You felt secure in your wickedness;you said, “No one sees me”;your wisdom and your knowledge led you astray,and you said in your heart,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18610V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18610V\"></sup>“I am, and there is no one besides me.”",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>But evil shall come upon you,which you will not know how to charm away;disaster shall fall upon you,for which you will not be able to atone;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18611W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18611W\"></sup>and ruin shall come upon you suddenly,of which you know nothing.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18612X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18612X\"></sup>Stand fast in your enchantmentsand your many sorceries,with which you have labored from your youth;perhaps you may be able to succeed;perhaps you may inspire terror.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>You are wearied with your many counsels;let them stand forth and save you,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18613Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18613Y\"></sup>those who divide the heavens,who gaze at the stars,who at the new moons make knownwhat shall come upon you.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18614Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18614Z\"></sup>they are like stubble;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18614AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18614AA\"></sup>the fire consumes them;they cannot deliver themselvesfrom the power of the flame.No coal for warming oneself is this,no fire to sit before!",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Such to you are those with whom you have labored,who have done business with you from your youth;they wander about, each in his own direction;there is no one to save you."
		},
		"48": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">48 </span>Hear this, O house of Jacob,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18616A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18616A\"></sup>who are called by the name of Israel,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18616B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18616B\"></sup>who came from the waters of Judah,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18616C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18616C\"></sup>who swear by the name of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>and confess the God of Israel,but not in truth or right.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>For they call themselves after the holy city,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18617D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18617D\"></sup>and stay themselves on the God of Israel;the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts is his name.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“The former things <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18618E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18618E\"></sup>I declared of old;they went out from my mouth, and I announced them;then suddenly I did them, and they came to pass.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Because I know that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18619F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18619F\"></sup>you are obstinate,and your neck is an iron sinewand your forehead brass,",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18620G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18620G\"></sup>I declared them to you from of old,before they came to pass I announced them to you,lest you should say, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18620H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18620H\"></sup>‘My idol did them,my carved image and my metal image commanded them.’",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“You have heard; now see all this;and will you not declare it?From this time forth <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18621I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18621I\"></sup>I announce to you new things,hidden things that you have not known.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>They are created now, not long ago;before today you have never heard of them,lest you should say, ‘Behold, I knew them.’",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>You have never heard, you have never known,from of old your ear has not been opened.For I knew that you would surely deal treacherously,and that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18623J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18623J\"></sup>from before birth you were called a rebel.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18624K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18624K\"></sup>“For my name's sake I defer my anger;for the sake of my praise I restrain it for you,that I may not cut you off.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Behold, I have refined you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18625L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18625L\"></sup>but not as silver;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18625M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18625M\"></sup>I have tried you in the furnace of affliction.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18626N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18626N\"></sup>For my own sake, for my own sake, I do it,for how should my name be profaned?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18626O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18626O\"></sup>My glory I will not give to another.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“Listen to me, O Jacob,and Israel, whom I called!I am he; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18627P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18627P\"></sup>I am the first,and I am the last.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>My hand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18628Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18628Q\"></sup>laid the foundation of the earth,and my right hand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18628R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18628R\"></sup>spread out the heavens;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18628S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18628S\"></sup>when I call to them,they stand forth together.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“Assemble, all of you, and listen!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18629T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18629T\"></sup>Who among them has declared these things?The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> loves him;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18629U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18629U\"></sup>he shall perform his purpose on Babylon,and his arm shall be against <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18629V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18629V\"></sup>the Chaldeans.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18630W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18630W\"></sup>I, even I, have spoken and called him;I have brought him, and he will prosper in his way.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18631X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18631X\"></sup>Draw near to me, hear this:from the beginning I have not spoken in secret,from the time it came to be I have been there.”And now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18631Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18631Y\"></sup>the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span> has sent me, and his Spirit.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,your Redeemer, the Holy One of Israel:“I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God,who teaches you to profit,who leads you in the way you should go.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18633Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18633Z\"></sup>Oh that you had paid attention to my commandments!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18633AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18633AA\"></sup>Then your peace would have been like a river,and your righteousness like the waves of the sea;",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18634AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18634AB\"></sup>your offspring would have been like the sand,and your descendants like its grains;their name would never be cut offor destroyed from before me.”",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18635AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18635AC\"></sup>Go out from Babylon, flee from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18635AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18635AD\"></sup>Chaldea,declare this <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18635AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18635AE\"></sup>with a shout of joy, proclaim it,send it out to the end of the earth;say, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18635AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18635AF\"></sup>“The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has redeemed his servant Jacob!”",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18636AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18636AG\"></sup>They did not thirst when he led them through the deserts;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18636AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18636AH\"></sup>he made water flow for them from the rock;he split the rock and the water gushed out.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18637AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18637AI\"></sup>“There is no peace,” says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, “for the wicked.”"
		},
		"49": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">49 </span>Listen to me, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18638A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18638A\"></sup>O coastlands,and give attention, you peoples <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18638B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18638B\"></sup>from afar.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18638C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18638C\"></sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> called me from the womb,from the body of my mother he named my name.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18639D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18639D\"></sup>He made my mouth like a sharp sword;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18639E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18639E\"></sup>in the shadow of his hand he hid me;he made me a polished arrow;in his quiver he hid me away.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And he said to me, “You are my servant,Israel, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18640F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18640F\"></sup>in whom I will be glorified.”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18641G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18641G\"></sup>But I said, “I have labored in vain;I have spent my strength for nothing and vanity;yet surely my right is with the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,and my recompense with my God.”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18642H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18642H\"></sup>And now the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says,he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18642I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18642I\"></sup>who formed me from the womb to be his servant,to bring Jacob back to him;and that Israel might be gathered to him—for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18642J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18642J\"></sup>I am honored in the eyes of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,and my God has become my strength—",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>he says:“It is too light a thing that you should be my servantto raise up the tribes of Jacoband to bring back the preserved of Israel;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18643K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18643K\"></sup>I will make you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18643L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18643L\"></sup>as a light for the nations,that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18643M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18643M\"></sup>my salvation may reach to the end of the earth.”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18644N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18644N\"></sup>the Redeemer of Israel and his Holy One,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18644O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18644O\"></sup>to one deeply despised, abhorred by the nation,the servant of rulers:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18644P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18644P\"></sup>“Kings shall see and arise;princes, and they shall prostrate themselves;because of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, who is faithful,the Holy One of Israel, who has chosen you.”",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18645Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18645Q\"></sup>“In a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18645R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18645R\"></sup>time of favor I have answered you;in a day of salvation I have helped you;I will keep you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18645S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18645S\"></sup>and give youas a covenant to the people,to establish the land,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18645T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18645T\"></sup>to apportion the desolate heritages,",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18646U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18646U\"></sup>saying to the prisoners, ‘Come out,’to those who are in darkness, ‘Appear.’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18646V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18646V\"></sup>They shall feed along the ways;on all bare heights shall be their pasture;",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18647W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18647W\"></sup>they shall not hunger or thirst,neither scorching wind nor sun shall strike them,for he who has pity on them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18647X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18647X\"></sup>will lead them,and by springs of water will guide them.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18648Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18648Y\"></sup>And I will make all my mountains a road,and my highways shall be raised up.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18649Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18649Z\"></sup>Behold, these shall come from afar,and behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18649AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18649AA\"></sup>these from the north and from the west,and these from the land of Syene.”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18650AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18650AB\"></sup>Sing for joy, O heavens, and exult, O earth;break forth, O mountains, into singing!For the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18650AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18650AC\"></sup>has comforted his peopleand will have compassion on his afflicted.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>But Zion said, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18651AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18651AD\"></sup>“The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has forsaken me;my Lord has forgotten me.”",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18652AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18652AE\"></sup>“Can a woman forget her nursing child,that she should have no compassion on the son of her womb?Even these may forget,yet I will not forget you.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18653AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18653AF\"></sup>I have engraved you on the palms of my hands;your walls are continually before me.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Your builders make haste;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18654AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18654AG\"></sup>your destroyers and those who laid you waste go out from you.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18655AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18655AH\"></sup>Lift up your eyes around and see;they all gather, they come to you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18655AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18655AI\"></sup>As I live, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18655AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18655AJ\"></sup>you shall put them all on as an ornament;you shall bind them on as a bride does.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>“Surely your waste and your desolate placesand your devastated land—<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18656AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18656AK\"></sup>surely now you will be too narrow for your inhabitants,and those who swallowed you up will be far away.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18657AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18657AL\"></sup>The children of your bereavementwill yet say in your ears:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18657AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18657AM\"></sup>‘The place is too narrow for me;make room for me to dwell in.’",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Then you will say in your heart:‘Who has borne me these?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18658AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18658AN\"></sup>I was bereaved and barren,exiled and put away,but who has brought up these?Behold, I was left alone;from where have these come?’”",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>:“Behold, I will lift up my hand to the nations,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18659AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18659AO\"></sup>and raise my signal to the peoples;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18659AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18659AP\"></sup>and they shall bring your sons in their arms,and your daughters shall be carried on their shoulders.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18660AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18660AQ\"></sup>Kings shall be your foster fathers,and their queens your nursing mothers.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18660AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18660AR\"></sup>With their faces to the ground they shall bow down to you,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18660AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18660AS\"></sup>lick the dust of your feet.Then you will know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18660AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18660AT\"></sup>those who wait for me <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18660AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18660AU\"></sup>shall not be put to shame.”",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Can the prey be taken from the mighty,or the captives of a tyrant be rescued?",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>For thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18662AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18662AV\"></sup>“Even the captives of the mighty shall be taken,and the prey of the tyrant be rescued,for I will contend with those who contend with you,and I will save your children.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18663AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18663AW\"></sup>I will make your oppressors eat their own flesh,and they shall be drunk <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18663AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18663AX\"></sup>with their own blood as with wine.Then all flesh shall knowthat <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18663AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18663AY\"></sup>I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your Savior,and your Redeemer, the Mighty One of Jacob.”"
		},
		"50": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">50 </span>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>:“Where is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18664A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18664A\"></sup>your mother's certificate of divorce,with which <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18664B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18664B\"></sup>I sent her away?Or <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18664C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18664C\"></sup>which of my creditors is itto whom I have sold you?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18664D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18664D\"></sup>Behold, for your iniquities you were sold,and for your transgressions your mother was sent away.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18665E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18665E\"></sup>Why, when I came, was there no man;why, when I called, was there no one to answer?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18665F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18665F\"></sup>Is my hand shortened, that it cannot redeem?Or have I no power to deliver?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18665G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18665G\"></sup>Behold, by my rebuke <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18665H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18665H\"></sup>I dry up the sea,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18665I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18665I\"></sup>I make the rivers a desert;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18665J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18665J\"></sup>their fish stink for lack of waterand die of thirst.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18666K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18666K\"></sup>I clothe the heavens with blacknessand make sackcloth their covering.”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>The Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span> has given <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18667L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18667L\"></sup>methe tongue of those who are taught,that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18667M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18667M\"></sup>I may know how to sustain with a word<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18667N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18667N\"></sup>him who is weary.Morning by morning he awakens;he awakens my earto hear as those who are taught.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18668O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18668O\"></sup>The Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span> has opened my ear,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18668P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18668P\"></sup>and I was not rebellious;I turned not backward.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18669Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18669Q\"></sup>I gave my back to those who strike,and my cheeks to those who pull out the beard;I hid not my facefrom disgrace and spitting.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>But the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span> helps me;therefore I have not been disgraced;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18670R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18670R\"></sup>therefore I have set my face like a flint,and I know that I shall not be put to shame.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><span class=\"indent-1-breaks\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18671S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18671S\"></sup>He who vindicates me is near.Who will contend with me?Let us stand up together.Who is my adversary?Let him come near to me.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18672T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18672T\"></sup>Behold, the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span> helps me;who will declare me guilty?Behold, all of them will wear out like a garment;the moth will eat them up.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Who among you fears the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>and obeys <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18673U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18673U\"></sup>the voice of his servant?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18673V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18673V\"></sup>Let him who walks in darknessand has no lighttrust in the name of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>and rely on his God.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Behold, all you who kindle a fire,who equip yourselves with burning torches!Walk by the light of your fire,and by the torches that you have kindled!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18674W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18674W\"></sup>This you have from my hand:you shall lie down in torment."
		},
		"51": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">51 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18675A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18675A\"></sup>“Listen to me, you who pursue righteousness,you who seek the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>:look to the rock from which you were hewn,and to the quarry from which you were dug.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Look to Abraham your fatherand to Sarah who bore you;for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18676B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18676B\"></sup>he was but one when I called him,that I might bless him and multiply him.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>For the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18677C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18677C\"></sup>comforts Zion;he comforts all her waste placesand makes her wilderness like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18677D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18677D\"></sup>Eden,her desert like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18677E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18677E\"></sup>the garden of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18677F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18677F\"></sup>joy and gladness will be found in her,thanksgiving and the voice of song.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18678G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18678G\"></sup>“Give attention to me, my people,and give ear to me, my nation;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18678H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18678H\"></sup>for a law will go out from me,and I will set my justice for a light to the peoples.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18679I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18679I\"></sup>My righteousness draws near,my salvation has gone out,and my arms will judge the peoples;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18679J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18679J\"></sup>the coastlands hope for me,and for my arm they wait.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18680K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18680K\"></sup>Lift up your eyes to the heavens,and look at the earth beneath;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18680L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18680L\"></sup>for the heavens vanish like smoke,the earth will wear out like a garment,and they who dwell in it will die in like manner;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18680M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18680M\"></sup>but my salvation will be forever,and my righteousness will never be dismayed.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18681N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18681N\"></sup>“Listen to me, you who know righteousness,the people <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18681O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18681O\"></sup>in whose heart is my law;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18681P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18681P\"></sup>fear not the reproach of man,nor be dismayed at their revilings.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18682Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18682Q\"></sup>For the moth will eat them up like a garment,and the worm will eat them like wool,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18682R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18682R\"></sup>but my righteousness will be forever,and my salvation to all generations.”",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18683S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18683S\"></sup>Awake, awake, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18683T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18683T\"></sup>put on strength,O <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18683U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18683U\"></sup>arm of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>;awake, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18683V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18683V\"></sup>as in days of old,the generations of long ago.Was it not you who cut <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18683W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18683W\"></sup>Rahab in pieces,who pierced <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18683X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18683X\"></sup>the dragon?",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18684Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18684Y\"></sup>Was it not you who dried up the sea,the waters of the great deep,who made the depths of the sea a wayfor the redeemed to pass over?",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18685Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18685Z\"></sup>And the ransomed of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> shall returnand come to Zion with singing;everlasting joy shall be upon their heads;they shall obtain gladness and joy,and sorrow and sighing shall flee away.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“I, I am he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18686AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18686AA\"></sup>who comforts you;who are you that you are afraid of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18686AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18686AB\"></sup>man who dies,of the son of man who is made <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18686AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18686AC\"></sup>like grass,",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>and have forgotten the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, your Maker,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18687AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18687AD\"></sup>who stretched out the heavensand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18687AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18687AE\"></sup>laid the foundations of the earth,and you fear continually all the daybecause of the wrath of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18687AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18687AF\"></sup>the oppressor,when he sets himself to destroy?And where is the wrath of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18687AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18687AG\"></sup>the oppressor?",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18688AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18688AH\"></sup>He who is bowed down shall speedily be released;he shall not die and go down <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18688AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18688AI\"></sup>to the pit,neither shall his bread be lacking.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18689AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18689AJ\"></sup>who stirs up the sea so that its waves roar—the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts is his name.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18690AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18690AK\"></sup>And I have put my words in your mouth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18690AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18690AL\"></sup>and covered you in the shadow of my hand,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18690AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18690AM\"></sup>establishing the heavensand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18690AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18690AN\"></sup>laying the foundations of the earth,and saying to Zion, ‘You are my people.’”",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18691AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18691AO\"></sup>Wake yourself, wake yourself,stand up, O Jerusalem,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18691AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18691AP\"></sup>you who have drunk from the hand of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>the cup of his wrath,who have drunk to the dregsthe bowl, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18691AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18691AQ\"></sup>the cup of staggering.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18692AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18692AR\"></sup>There is none to guide heramong all the sons she has borne;there is none to take her by the handamong all the sons she has brought up.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18693AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18693AS\"></sup>These two things have happened to you—who will console you?—devastation and destruction, famine and sword;who will comfort you?",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18694AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18694AT\"></sup>Your sons have fainted;they lie at the head of every streetlike an <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18694AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18694AU\"></sup>antelope <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18694AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18694AV\"></sup>in a net;they are full of the wrath of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,the rebuke of your God.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18695AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18695AW\"></sup>Therefore hear this, you who are afflicted,who are drunk, but not with wine:",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Thus says your Lord, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,your God <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18696AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18696AX\"></sup>who pleads the cause of his people:“Behold, I have taken from your hand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18696AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18696AY\"></sup>the cup of staggering;the bowl of my wrath you shall drink no more;",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18697AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18697AZ\"></sup>and I will put it into the hand of your tormentors,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18697BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18697BA\"></sup>who have said to you,‘Bow down, that we may pass over’;and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18697BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18697BB\"></sup>you have made your back like the groundand like the street for them to pass over.”"
		},
		"52": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">52 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18698A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18698A\"></sup>Awake, awake,put on your strength, O Zion;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18698B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18698B\"></sup>put on your beautiful garments,O Jerusalem, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18698C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18698C\"></sup>the holy city;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18698D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18698D\"></sup>for there shall no more come into youthe uncircumcised and the unclean.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18699E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18699E\"></sup>Shake yourself from the dust and arise;be seated, O Jerusalem;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18699F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18699F\"></sup>loose the bonds from your neck,O captive daughter of Zion.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>For thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18700G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18700G\"></sup>“You were sold for nothing, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18700H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18700H\"></sup>you shall be redeemed without money.”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>For thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18701I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18701I\"></sup>“My people went down at the first into Egypt to sojourn there, and the Assyrian oppressed them for nothing.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Now therefore what have I here,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, “seeing that my people are taken away for nothing? Their rulers wail,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, “and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18702J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18702J\"></sup>continually all the day my name is despised.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Therefore my people shall know my name. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18703K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18703K\"></sup>Therefore in that day they shall know that it is I who speak; here I am.”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18704L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18704L\"></sup>How beautiful upon the mountainsare the feet of him who brings good news,who publishes peace, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18704M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18704M\"></sup>who brings good news of happiness,who publishes salvation,who says to Zion, “Your God reigns.”",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>The voice of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18705N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18705N\"></sup>your watchmen—they lift up their voice;together they sing for joy;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18705O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18705O\"></sup>for eye to eye they seethe return of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> to Zion.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18706P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18706P\"></sup>Break forth together into singing,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18706Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18706Q\"></sup>you waste places of Jerusalem,for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18706R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18706R\"></sup>the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has comforted his people;he has redeemed Jerusalem.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18707S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18707S\"></sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has bared his holy armbefore the eyes of all the nations,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18707T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18707T\"></sup>and all the ends of the earth shall seethe salvation of our God.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18708U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18708U\"></sup>Depart, depart, go out from there;touch no unclean thing;go out from the midst of her; purify yourselves,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18708V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18708V\"></sup>you who bear the vessels of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>For you shall not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18709W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18709W\"></sup>go out in haste,and you shall not go in flight,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18709X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18709X\"></sup>for the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will go before you,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18709Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18709Y\"></sup>and the God of Israel will be your rear guard.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18710Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18710Z\"></sup>my servant shall act wisely;he shall be high and lifted up,and shall be exalted.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>As many were astonished at you—<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18711AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18711AA\"></sup>his appearance was so marred, beyond human semblance,and his form beyond that of the children of mankind—",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>so <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18712AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18712AB\"></sup>shall he sprinkle many nations.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18712AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18712AC\"></sup>Kings shall shut their mouths because of him,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18712AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18712AD\"></sup>for that which has not been told them they see,and that which they have not heard they understand."
		},
		"53": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">53 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18713A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18713A\"></sup>Who has believed what he has heard from us?And to whom has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18713B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18713B\"></sup>the arm of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> been revealed?",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>For he grew up before him like a young plant,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18714C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18714C\"></sup>and like a root out of dry ground;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18714D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18714D\"></sup>he had no form or majesty that we should look at him,and no beauty that we should desire him.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18715E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18715E\"></sup>He was despised and rejected by men,a man of sorrows and acquainted with grief;and as one from whom men hide their faceshe was despised, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18715F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18715F\"></sup>we esteemed him not.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18716G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18716G\"></sup>Surely he has borne our griefsand carried our sorrows;yet we esteemed him stricken,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18716H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18716H\"></sup>smitten by God, and afflicted.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18717I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18717I\"></sup>But he was pierced for our transgressions;he was crushed for our iniquities;upon him was the chastisement that brought us peace,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18717J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18717J\"></sup>and with his wounds we are healed.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18718K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18718K\"></sup>All we like sheep have gone astray;we have turned—every one—to his own way;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18718L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18718L\"></sup>and the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has laid on himthe iniquity of us all.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>He was oppressed, and he was afflicted,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18719M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18719M\"></sup>yet he opened not his mouth;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18719N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18719N\"></sup>like a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18719O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18719O\"></sup>lamb that is led to the slaughter,and like a sheep that before its shearers is silent,so he opened not his mouth.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>By oppression and judgment he was taken away;and as for his generation, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18720P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18720P\"></sup>who consideredthat he was cut off out of the land of the living,stricken for the transgression of my people?",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>And they made his grave with the wicked<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18721Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18721Q\"></sup>and with a rich man in his death,although <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18721R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18721R\"></sup>he had done no violence,and there was no deceit in his mouth.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Yet <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18722S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18722S\"></sup>it was the will of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> to crush him;he has put him to grief;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18722T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18722T\"></sup>when his soul makes an offering for guilt,he shall see his offspring; he shall prolong his days;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18722U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18722U\"></sup>the will of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> shall prosper in his hand.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Out of the anguish of his soul he shall see and be satisfied;by his knowledge shall <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18723V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18723V\"></sup>the righteous one, my servant,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18723W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18723W\"></sup>make many to be accounted righteous,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18723X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18723X\"></sup>and he shall bear their iniquities.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18724Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18724Y\"></sup>Therefore I will divide him a portion with the many,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18724Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18724Z\"></sup>and he shall divide the spoil with the strong,because he poured out his soul to deathand was numbered with the transgressors;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18724AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18724AA\"></sup>yet he bore the sin of many,and makes intercession for the transgressors."
		},
		"54": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">54 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18725A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18725A\"></sup>“Sing, O barren one, who did not bear;break forth into singing and cry aloud,you who have not been in labor!For the children of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18725B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18725B\"></sup>the desolate one <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18725C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18725C\"></sup>will be morethan the children of her who is married,” says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18726D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18726D\"></sup>“Enlarge the place of your tent,and let the curtains of your habitations be stretched out;do not hold back; lengthen your cordsand strengthen your stakes.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18727E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18727E\"></sup>For you will spread abroad to the right and to the left,and your offspring will possess the nationsand will people the desolate cities.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“Fear not, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18728F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18728F\"></sup>for you will not be ashamed;be not confounded, for you will not be disgraced;for you will forget the shame of your youth,and the reproach of your widowhood you will remember no more.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18729G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18729G\"></sup>For your Maker is your husband,the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts is his name;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18729H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18729H\"></sup>and the Holy One of Israel is your Redeemer,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18729I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18729I\"></sup>the God of the whole earth he is called.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18730J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18730J\"></sup>For the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has called youlike a wife deserted and grieved in spirit,like a wife of youth when she is cast off,says your God.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18731K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18731K\"></sup>For a brief moment I deserted you,but with great compassion I will gather you.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18732L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18732L\"></sup>In overflowing anger for a momentI hid my face from you,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18732M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18732M\"></sup>but with everlasting love I will have compassion on you,”says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, your Redeemer.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“This is like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18733N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18733N\"></sup>the days of Noah to me:as I swore that the waters of Noahshould no more go over the earth,so I have sworn that I will not be angry with you,and will not rebuke you.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>For the mountains may departand the hills be removed,but my steadfast love shall not depart from you,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18734O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18734O\"></sup>my covenant of peace shall not be removed,”says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, who has compassion on you.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18735P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18735P\"></sup>“O afflicted one, storm-tossed and not comforted,behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18735Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18735Q\"></sup>I will set your stones in antimony,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18735R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18735R\"></sup>and lay your foundations with sapphires.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>I will make your pinnacles of agate,your gates of carbuncles,and all your wall of precious stones.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18737S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18737S\"></sup>All your children <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18737T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18737T\"></sup>shall be taught by the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18737U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18737U\"></sup>and great shall be the peace of your children.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>In righteousness you shall be established;you shall be far from oppression, for you shall not fear;and from terror, for it shall not come near you.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18739V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18739V\"></sup>If anyone stirs up strife,it is not from me;whoever stirs up strife with youshall fall because of you.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Behold, I have created the smithwho blows the fire of coalsand produces a weapon for its purpose.I have also created the ravager to destroy;",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><span class=\"indent-1-breaks\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>no weapon that is fashioned against you shall succeed,and you shall refute every tongue that rises against you in judgment.This is the heritage of the servants of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18741W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18741W\"></sup>and their vindication from me, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.”"
		},
		"55": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">55 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18742A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18742A\"></sup>“Come, everyone who thirsts,come to the waters;and he who has no money,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18742B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18742B\"></sup>come, buy and eat!Come, buy wine and milkwithout money and without price.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18743C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18743C\"></sup>Why do you spend your money for that which is not bread,and your labor for that which does not satisfy?Listen diligently to me, and eat what is good,and delight yourselves in rich food.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Incline your ear, and come to me;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18744D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18744D\"></sup>hear, that your soul may live;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18744E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18744E\"></sup>and I will make with you an everlasting covenant,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18744F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18744F\"></sup>my steadfast, sure love for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18744G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18744G\"></sup>David.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18745H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18745H\"></sup>Behold, I made him a witness to the peoples,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18745I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18745I\"></sup>a leader and commander for the peoples.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18746J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18746J\"></sup>Behold, you shall call a nation that you do not know,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18746K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18746K\"></sup>a nation that did not know you shall run to you,because of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God, and of the Holy One of Israel,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18746L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18746L\"></sup>for he has glorified you.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18747M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18747M\"></sup>“Seek the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> while he may be found;call upon him while he is near;",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>let the wicked forsake his way,and the unrighteous man his thoughts;let him return to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, that he may have compassion on him,and to our God, for he will abundantly pardon.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>For my thoughts are not your thoughts,neither are your ways my ways, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18750N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18750N\"></sup>For as the heavens are higher than the earth,so are my ways higher than your waysand my thoughts than your thoughts.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18751O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18751O\"></sup>“For as the rain and the snow come down from heavenand do not return there but water the earth,making it bring forth and sprout,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18751P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18751P\"></sup>giving seed to the sower and bread to the eater,",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>so shall my word be that goes out from my mouth;it shall not return to me empty,but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18752Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18752Q\"></sup>it shall accomplish that which I purpose,and shall succeed in the thing for which I sent it.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18753R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18753R\"></sup>“For you shall go out in joyand be led forth in peace;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18753S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18753S\"></sup>the mountains and the hills before youshall break forth into singing,and all the trees of the field shall clap their hands.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18754T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18754T\"></sup>Instead of the thorn shall come up the cypress;instead of the brier shall come up the myrtle;and it shall make a name for the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,an everlasting sign that shall not be cut off.”"
		},
		"56": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">56 </span>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>:“Keep justice, and do righteousness,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18755A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18755A\"></sup>for soon my salvation will come,and my righteousness be revealed.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Blessed is the man who does this,and the son of man who holds it fast,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18756B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18756B\"></sup>who keeps the Sabbath, not profaning it,and keeps his hand from doing any evil.”",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Let not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18757C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18757C\"></sup>the foreigner who has joined himself to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> say,“The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will surely separate me from his people”;and let not the eunuch say,“Behold, I am <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18757D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18757D\"></sup>a dry tree.”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>For thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>:“To the eunuchs <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18758E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18758E\"></sup>who keep my Sabbaths,who choose the things that please meand hold fast my covenant,",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18759F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18759F\"></sup>I will give in my house and within my wallsa <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18759G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18759G\"></sup>monument and a namebetter than sons and daughters;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18759H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18759H\"></sup>I will give them an everlasting namethat shall not be cut off.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18760I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18760I\"></sup>the foreigners who join themselves to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,to minister to him, to love the name of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,and to be his servants,everyone <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18760J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18760J\"></sup>who keeps the Sabbath and does not profane it,and holds fast my covenant—",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18761K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18761K\"></sup>these I will bring to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18761L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18761L\"></sup>my holy mountain,and make them joyful in my house of prayer;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18761M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18761M\"></sup>their burnt offerings and their sacrificeswill be accepted on my altar;for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18761N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18761N\"></sup>my house shall be called a house of prayerfor all peoples.”",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>The Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18762O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18762O\"></sup>who gathers the outcasts of Israel, declares,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18762P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18762P\"></sup>“I will gather yet others to himbesides those already gathered.”",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18763Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18763Q\"></sup>All you beasts of the field, come to devour—all you beasts in the forest.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18764R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18764R\"></sup>His watchmen are blind;they are all without knowledge;they are all silent <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18764S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18764S\"></sup>dogs;they cannot bark,dreaming, lying down,loving to slumber.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18765T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18765T\"></sup>The dogs have a mighty appetite;they never have enough.But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18765U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18765U\"></sup>they are shepherds who have no understanding;they have all turned to their own way,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18765V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18765V\"></sup>each to his own gain, one and all.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18766W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18766W\"></sup>“Come,” they say, “let me get wine;let us fill ourselves with strong drink;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18766X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18766X\"></sup>and tomorrow will be like this day,great beyond measure.”"
		},
		"57": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">57 </span>The righteous man perishes,and no one lays it to heart;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18767A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18767A\"></sup>devout men are taken away,while no one understands.For the righteous man is taken away from calamity;",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><span class=\"indent-1-breaks\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18768B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18768B\"></sup>he enters into peace;they rest <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18768C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18768C\"></sup>in their bedswho walk in their uprightness.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>But you, draw near,sons of the sorceress,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18769D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18769D\"></sup>offspring of the adulterer and the loose woman.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Whom are you mocking?Against whom <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18770E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18770E\"></sup>do you open your mouth wideand stick out your tongue?Are you not children of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18770F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18770F\"></sup>transgression,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18770G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18770G\"></sup>the offspring of deceit,",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>you who burn with lust among <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18771H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18771H\"></sup>the oaks,under every green tree,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18771I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18771I\"></sup>who slaughter your children in the valleys,under the clefts of the rocks?",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Among the smooth stones of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18772J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18772J\"></sup>the valley is your portion;they, they, are your lot;to them you have poured out a drink offering,you have brought a grain offering.Shall I relent for these things?",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18773K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18773K\"></sup>On a high and lofty mountainyou have set your bed,and there you went up to offer sacrifice.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Behind the door and the doorpostyou have set up your memorial;for, deserting me, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18774L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18774L\"></sup>you have uncovered your bed,you have gone up to it,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18774M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18774M\"></sup>you have made it wide;and you have made a covenant for yourself with them,you have loved their bed,you have looked on nakedness.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>You journeyed to the king with oiland multiplied your perfumes;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18775N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18775N\"></sup>you sent your envoys far off,and sent down even to Sheol.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>You were wearied with the length of your way,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18776O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18776O\"></sup>but you did not say, “It is hopeless”;you found new life for your strength,and so you were not faint.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18777P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18777P\"></sup>Whom did you dread and fear,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18777Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18777Q\"></sup>so that you lied,and did not remember me,did not lay it to heart?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18777R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18777R\"></sup>Have I not held my peace, even for a long time,and you do not fear me?",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>I will declare your righteousness and your deeds,but they will not profit you.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18779S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18779S\"></sup>When you cry out, let your collection of idols deliver you!The wind will carry them all off,a breath will take them away.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18779T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18779T\"></sup>But he who takes refuge in me shall possess the landand shall inherit <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18779U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18779U\"></sup>my holy mountain.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>And it shall be said,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18780V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18780V\"></sup>“Build up, build up, prepare the way,remove every obstruction from my people's way.”",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>For thus says <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18781W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18781W\"></sup>the One who is high and lifted up,who inhabits eternity, whose name is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18781X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18781X\"></sup>Holy:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18781Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18781Y\"></sup>“I dwell in the high and holy place,and also <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18781Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18781Z\"></sup>with him who is of a contrite and lowly spirit,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18781AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18781AA\"></sup>to revive the spirit of the lowly,and to revive the heart of the contrite.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18782AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18782AB\"></sup>For I will not contend forever,nor will I always be angry;for the spirit would grow faint before me,and the breath of life that I made.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Because of the iniquity of his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18783AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18783AC\"></sup>unjust gain I was angry,I struck him; I hid my face and was angry,but he went on backsliding in the way of his own heart.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>I have seen his ways, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18784AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18784AD\"></sup>but I will heal him;I will lead him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18784AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18784AE\"></sup>and restore comfort to him and his mourners,",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><span class=\"indent-1-breaks\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18785AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18785AF\"></sup>creating <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18785AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18785AG\"></sup>the fruit of the lips.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18785AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18785AH\"></sup>Peace, peace, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18785AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18785AI\"></sup>to the far and to the near,” says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18785AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18785AJ\"></sup>“and I will heal him.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18786AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18786AK\"></sup>But the wicked are like the tossing sea;for it cannot be quiet,and its waters toss up mire and dirt.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18787AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18787AL\"></sup>There is no peace,” says my God, “for the wicked.”"
		},
		"58": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">58 </span>“Cry aloud; do not hold back;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18788A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18788A\"></sup>lift up your voice like a trumpet;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18788B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18788B\"></sup>declare to my people their transgression,to the house of Jacob their sins.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18789C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18789C\"></sup>Yet they seek me dailyand delight to know my ways,as if they were a nation that did righteousnessand did not forsake the judgment of their God;they ask of me righteous judgments;they delight to draw near to God.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18790D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18790D\"></sup>‘Why have we fasted, and you see it not?Why have we humbled ourselves, and you take no knowledge of it?’Behold, in the day of your fast you seek your own pleasure,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18790E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18790E\"></sup>and oppress all your workers.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Behold, you fast only to quarrel and to fightand to hit with a wicked fist.Fasting like yours this daywill not make your voice to be heard on high.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18792F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18792F\"></sup>Is such the fast that I choose,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18792G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18792G\"></sup>a day for a person to humble himself?Is it to bow down his head like a reed,and to spread sackcloth and ashes under him?Will you call this a fast,and a day acceptable to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>?",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“Is not this the fast that I choose:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18793H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18793H\"></sup>to loose the bonds of wickedness,to undo the straps <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18793I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18793I\"></sup>of the yoke,to let the oppressed go free,and to break every yoke?",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Is it not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18794J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18794J\"></sup>to share your bread with the hungryand bring the homeless poor into your house;when you see the naked, to cover him,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18794K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18794K\"></sup>and not to hide yourself from your own flesh?",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18795L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18795L\"></sup>Then shall your light break forth like the dawn,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18795M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18795M\"></sup>and your healing shall spring up speedily;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18795N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18795N\"></sup>your righteousness shall go before you;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18795O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18795O\"></sup>the glory of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> shall be your rear guard.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Then you shall call, and the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will answer;you shall cry, and he will say, ‘Here I am.’If you take away <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18796P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18796P\"></sup>the yoke from your midst,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18796Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18796Q\"></sup>the pointing of the finger, and speaking wickedness,",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18797R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18797R\"></sup>if you pour yourself out for the hungryand satisfy the desire of the afflicted,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18797S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18797S\"></sup>then shall your light rise in the darknessand your gloom be as the noonday.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>And the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will guide you continuallyand satisfy your desire in scorched placesand make your bones strong;and you shall be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18798T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18798T\"></sup>like a watered garden,like a spring of water,whose waters do not fail.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18799U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18799U\"></sup>And your ancient ruins shall be rebuilt;you shall raise up the foundations of many generations;you shall be called the repairer of the breach,the restorer of streets to dwell in.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18800V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18800V\"></sup>“If you turn back your foot from the Sabbath,from doing your pleasure on my holy day,and call the Sabbath a delightand the holy day of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> honorable;if you honor it, not going your own ways,or seeking <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18800W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18800W\"></sup>your own pleasure, or talking idly;",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>then you shall take delight in the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18801X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18801X\"></sup>and I will make you ride on the heights of the earth;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18801Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18801Y\"></sup>I will feed you with the heritage of Jacob your father,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18801Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18801Z\"></sup>for the mouth of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has spoken.”"
		},
		"59": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">59 </span>Behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18802A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18802A\"></sup>the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>'s hand is not shortened, that it cannot save,or his ear dull, that it cannot hear;",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18803B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18803B\"></sup>but your iniquities have made a separationbetween you and your God,and your sins have hidden his face from youso that he does not hear.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18804C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18804C\"></sup>For your hands are defiled with bloodand your fingers with iniquity;your lips have spoken lies;your tongue mutters wickedness.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18805D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18805D\"></sup>No one enters suit justly;no one goes to law honestly;they rely on empty pleas, they speak lies,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18805E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18805E\"></sup>they conceive mischief and give birth to iniquity.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>They hatch adders' eggs;they weave the spider's web;he who eats their eggs dies,and from one that is crushed a viper is hatched.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18807F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18807F\"></sup>Their webs will not serve as clothing;men will not cover themselves with what they make.Their works are works of iniquity,and deeds of violence are in their hands.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18808G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18808G\"></sup>Their feet run to evil,and they are swift to shed innocent blood;their thoughts are thoughts of iniquity;desolation and destruction are in their highways.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>The way of peace they do not know,and there is no justice in their paths;they have made their roads crooked;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18809H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18809H\"></sup>no one who treads on them knows peace.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Therefore justice is far from us,and righteousness does not overtake us;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18810I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18810I\"></sup>we hope for light, and behold, darkness,and for brightness, but we walk in gloom.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18811J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18811J\"></sup>We grope for the wall like the blind;we grope like those who have no eyes;we stumble at noon as in the twilight,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18811K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18811K\"></sup>among those in full vigor we are like dead men.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>We all growl like bears;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18812L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18812L\"></sup>we moan and moan like doves;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18812M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18812M\"></sup>we hope for justice, but there is none;for salvation, but it is far from us.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>For our transgressions are multiplied before you,and our sins testify against us;for our transgressions are with us,and we know our iniquities:",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>transgressing, and denying the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,and turning back from following our God,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18814N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18814N\"></sup>speaking oppression and revolt,conceiving and uttering from the heart lying words.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18815O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18815O\"></sup>Justice is turned back,and righteousness stands far away;for truth has stumbled in the public squares,and uprightness cannot enter.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Truth is lacking,and he who departs from evil makes himself a prey.The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> saw it, and it displeased himthat there was no justice.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18817P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18817P\"></sup>He saw that there was no man,and wondered that there was no one to intercede;then his own arm brought him salvation,and his righteousness upheld him.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18818Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18818Q\"></sup>He put on righteousness as a breastplate,and a helmet of salvation on his head;he put on garments of vengeance for clothing,and wrapped himself in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18818R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18818R\"></sup>zeal as a cloak.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18819S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18819S\"></sup>According to their deeds, so will he repay,wrath to his adversaries, repayment to his enemies;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18819T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18819T\"></sup>to the coastlands he will render repayment.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18820U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18820U\"></sup>So they shall fear the name of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> from the west,and his glory from the rising of the sun;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18820V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18820V\"></sup>for he will come like a rushing stream,which the wind of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> drives.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18821W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18821W\"></sup>“And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18821X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18821X\"></sup>a Redeemer will come to Zion,to those in Jacob who turn from transgression,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>“And as for me, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18822Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18822Y\"></sup>this is my covenant with them,” says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>: “My Spirit that is upon you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18822Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18822Z\"></sup>and my words that I have put in your mouth, shall not depart out of your mouth, or out of the mouth of your offspring, or out of the mouth of your children's offspring,” says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, “from this time forth and forevermore.”"
		},
		"60": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">60 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18823A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18823A\"></sup>Arise, shine, for your light has come,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18823B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18823B\"></sup>the glory of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has risen upon you.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>For behold, darkness shall cover the earth,and thick darkness the peoples;but the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will arise upon you,and his glory will be seen upon you.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18825C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18825C\"></sup>And nations shall come to your light,and kings to the brightness of your rising.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18826D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18826D\"></sup>Lift up your eyes all around, and see;they all gather together, they come to you;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18826E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18826E\"></sup>your sons shall come from afar,and your daughters shall be carried on the hip.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Then you shall see and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18827F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18827F\"></sup>be radiant;your heart shall thrill and exult,because the abundance of the sea shall be turned to you,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18827G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18827G\"></sup>the wealth of the nations shall come to you.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>A multitude of camels shall cover you,the young camels of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18828H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18828H\"></sup>Midian and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18828I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18828I\"></sup>Ephah;all those from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18828J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18828J\"></sup>Sheba shall come.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18828K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18828K\"></sup>They shall bring gold and frankincense,and shall bring good news, the praises of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>All the flocks of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18829L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18829L\"></sup>Kedar shall be gathered to you;the rams of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18829M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18829M\"></sup>Nebaioth shall minister to you;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18829N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18829N\"></sup>they shall come up with acceptance on my altar,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18829O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18829O\"></sup>and I will beautify my beautiful house.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Who are these that fly like a cloud,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18830P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18830P\"></sup>like doves to their windows?",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18831Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18831Q\"></sup>the coastlands shall hope for me,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18831R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18831R\"></sup>the ships of Tarshish first,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18831S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18831S\"></sup>to bring your children from afar,their silver and gold with them,for the name of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God,and for the Holy One of Israel,because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18831T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18831T\"></sup>he has made you beautiful.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18832U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18832U\"></sup>Foreigners shall build up your walls,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18832V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18832V\"></sup>their kings shall minister to you;for in my wrath I struck you,but in my favor I have had mercy on you.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18833W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18833W\"></sup>Your gates shall be open continually;day and night they shall not be shut,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18833X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18833X\"></sup>that people may bring to you the wealth of the nations,with their kings led in procession.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18834Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18834Y\"></sup>For the nation and kingdomthat will not serve you shall perish;those nations shall be utterly laid waste.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18835Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18835Z\"></sup>The glory of Lebanon shall come to you,the cypress, the plane, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18835AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18835AA\"></sup>the pine,to beautify the place of my sanctuary,and I will make the place of my feet glorious.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18836AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18836AB\"></sup>The sons of those who afflicted youshall come bending low to you,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18836AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18836AC\"></sup>and all who despised youshall bow down at your feet;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18836AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18836AD\"></sup>they shall call you the City of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,the Zion of the Holy One of Israel.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18837AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18837AE\"></sup>Whereas you have been forsaken and hated,with no one passing through,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18837AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18837AF\"></sup>I will make you majestic forever,a joy from age to age.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18838AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18838AG\"></sup>You shall suck the milk of nations;you shall nurse at the breast of kings;and you shall know that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18838AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18838AH\"></sup>I, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, am your Saviorand your Redeemer, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18838AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18838AI\"></sup>the Mighty One of Jacob.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Instead of bronze I will bring gold,and instead of iron I will bring silver;instead of wood, bronze,instead of stones, iron.I will make your overseers peace<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18839AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18839AJ\"></sup>and your taskmasters righteousness.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18840AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18840AK\"></sup>Violence shall no more be heard in your land,devastation or destruction within your borders;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18840AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18840AL\"></sup>you shall call your walls Salvation,and your gates Praise.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18841AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18841AM\"></sup>The sun shall be no moreyour light by day,nor for brightness shall the moongive you light;but the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will be your everlasting light,and your God will be your glory.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Your sun shall no more go down,nor your moon withdraw itself;for the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will be your everlasting light,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18842AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18842AN\"></sup>your days of mourning shall be ended.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18843AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18843AO\"></sup>Your people shall all be righteous;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18843AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18843AP\"></sup>they shall possess the land forever,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18843AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18843AQ\"></sup>the branch of my planting, the work of my hands,that I might be glorified.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18844AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18844AR\"></sup>The least one shall become a clan,and the smallest one a mighty nation;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18844AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18844AS\"></sup>I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>;in its time I will hasten it."
		},
		"61": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">61 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18845A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18845A\"></sup>The Spirit of the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span> is upon me,because the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18845B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18845B\"></sup>anointed meto bring good news to the poor;he has sent me to bind up the brokenhearted,to proclaim liberty to the captives,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18845C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18845C\"></sup>the opening of the prison to those who are bound;",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18846D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18846D\"></sup>to proclaim the year of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>'s favor,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18846E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18846E\"></sup>and the day of vengeance of our God;to comfort all who mourn;",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>to grant to those who mourn in Zion—<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18847F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18847F\"></sup>to give them a beautiful headdress instead of ashes,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18847G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18847G\"></sup>the oil of gladness instead of mourning,the garment of praise instead of a faint spirit;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18847H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18847H\"></sup>that they may be called oaks of righteousness,the planting of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18847I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18847I\"></sup>that he may be glorified.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18848J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18848J\"></sup>They shall build up the ancient ruins;they shall raise up the former devastations;they shall repair the ruined cities,the devastations of many generations.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18849K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18849K\"></sup>Strangers shall stand and tend your flocks;foreigners shall be your plowmen and vinedressers;",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18850L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18850L\"></sup>but you shall be called the priests of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>;they shall speak of you as the ministers of our God;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18850M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18850M\"></sup>you shall eat the wealth of the nations,and in their glory you shall boast.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18851N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18851N\"></sup>Instead of your shame there shall be a double portion;instead of dishonor they shall rejoice in their lot;therefore in their land they shall possess a double portion;they shall have everlasting joy.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18852O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18852O\"></sup>For I the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> love justice;I hate robbery and wrong;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18852P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18852P\"></sup>I will faithfully give them their recompense,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18852Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18852Q\"></sup>and I will make an everlasting covenant with them.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Their offspring shall be known among the nations,and their descendants in the midst of the peoples;all who see them shall acknowledge them,that they are an offspring the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has blessed.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18854R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18854R\"></sup>I will greatly rejoice in the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>;my soul shall exult in my God,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18854S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18854S\"></sup>for he has clothed me with the garments of salvation;he has covered me with the robe of righteousness,as a bridegroom decks himself <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18854T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18854T\"></sup>like a priest with a beautiful headdress,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18854U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18854U\"></sup>and as a bride adorns herself with her jewels.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>For as the earth brings forth its sprouts,and as a garden causes what is sown in it to sprout up,so the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span> will cause <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18855V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18855V\"></sup>righteousness and praiseto sprout up before all the nations."
		},
		"62": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">62 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18856A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18856A\"></sup>For Zion's sake I will not keep silent,and for Jerusalem's sake I will not be quiet,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18856B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18856B\"></sup>until her righteousness goes forth as brightness,and her salvation as a burning torch.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18857C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18857C\"></sup>The nations shall see your righteousness,and all the kings your glory,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18857D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18857D\"></sup>and you shall be called by a new namethat the mouth of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will give.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>You shall be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18858E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18858E\"></sup>a crown of beauty in the hand of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,and a royal diadem in the hand of your God.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18859F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18859F\"></sup>You shall no more be termed <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18859G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18859G\"></sup>Forsaken,and your land shall no more be termed Desolate,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18859H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18859H\"></sup>but you shall be called <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18859I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18859I\"></sup>My Delight Is in Her,and your land Married;for the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> delights in you,and your land shall be married.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>For as a young man marries a young woman,so <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18860J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18860J\"></sup>shall your sons marry you,and as the bridegroom rejoices over the bride,so <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18860K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18860K\"></sup>shall your God rejoice over you.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>On your walls, O Jerusalem,I have set <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18861L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18861L\"></sup>watchmen;all the day and all the nightthey shall never be silent.You who put the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> in remembrance,take no rest,",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>and give him no restuntil he establishes Jerusalemand makes it <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18862M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18862M\"></sup>a praise in the earth.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has sworn <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18863N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18863N\"></sup>by his right handand by his mighty arm:“I will not again give <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18863O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18863O\"></sup>your grainto be food for your enemies,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18863P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18863P\"></sup>and foreigners shall not drink your winefor which you have labored;",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18864Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18864Q\"></sup>those who garner it shall eat itand praise the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18864R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18864R\"></sup>those who gather it shall drink itin the courts of my sanctuary.”",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Go through, go through the gates;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18865S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18865S\"></sup>prepare the way for the people;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18865T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18865T\"></sup>build up, build up the highway;clear it of stones;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18865U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18865U\"></sup>lift up a signal over the peoples.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Behold, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has proclaimedto the end of the earth:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18866V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18866V\"></sup>Say to the daughter of Zion,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18866W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18866W\"></sup>“Behold, your salvation comes;behold, his reward is with him,and his recompense before him.”",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18867X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18867X\"></sup>And they shall be called The Holy People,The Redeemed of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18867Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18867Y\"></sup>and you shall be called Sought Out,A City Not Forsaken."
		},
		"63": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">63 </span>Who is this who comes from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18868A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18868A\"></sup>Edom,in crimsoned garments from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18868B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18868B\"></sup>Bozrah,he who is splendid in his apparel,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18868C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18868C\"></sup>marching in the greatness of his strength?“It is I, speaking in righteousness,mighty to save.”",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Why is your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18869D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18869D\"></sup>apparel red,and your garments like his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18869E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18869E\"></sup>who treads in the winepress?",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18870F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18870F\"></sup>“I have trodden the winepress alone,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18870G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18870G\"></sup>and from the peoples no one was with me;I trod them in my angerand trampled them in my wrath;their lifeblood spattered on my garments,and stained all my apparel.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18871H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18871H\"></sup>For the day of vengeance was in my heart,and my year of redemption had come.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>I looked, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18872I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18872I\"></sup>there was no one to help;I was appalled, but there was no one to uphold;so my own arm brought me salvation,and my wrath upheld me.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>I trampled down the peoples in my anger;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18873J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18873J\"></sup>I made them drunk in my wrath,and I poured out their lifeblood on the earth.”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>I will recount the steadfast love of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,the praises of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,according to all that the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has granted us,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18874K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18874K\"></sup>and the great goodness to the house of Israelthat he has granted them according to his compassion,according to the abundance of his steadfast love.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>For he said, “Surely they are my people,children who will not deal falsely.”And he became their Savior.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18876L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18876L\"></sup>In all their affliction he was afflicted,and the angel of his presence saved them;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18876M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18876M\"></sup>in his love and in his pity he redeemed them;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18876N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18876N\"></sup>he lifted them up and carried them all the days of old.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18877O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18877O\"></sup>But they rebelled<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18877P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18877P\"></sup>and grieved his Holy Spirit;therefore he turned to be their enemy,and himself fought against them.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Then he remembered <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18878Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18878Q\"></sup>the days of old,of Moses and his people.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18878R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18878R\"></sup>Where is he who brought them up out of the seawith the shepherds of his flock?Where is he who put in the midst of themhis Holy Spirit,",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>who caused his glorious armto go at the right hand of Moses,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18879S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18879S\"></sup>who divided the waters before them<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18879T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18879T\"></sup>to make for himself an everlasting name,",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><span class=\"indent-1-breaks\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>who led them through the depths?Like a horse in the desert,they did not stumble.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Like livestock that go down into the valley,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18881U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18881U\"></sup>the Spirit of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> gave them rest.So you led your people,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18881V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18881V\"></sup>to make for yourself a glorious name.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18882W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18882W\"></sup>Look down from heaven and see,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18882X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18882X\"></sup>from your holy and beautiful habitation.Where are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18882Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18882Y\"></sup>your zeal and your might?The stirring of your inner parts and your compassionare held back from me.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18883Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18883Z\"></sup>you are our Father,though Abraham does not know us,and Israel does not acknowledge us;you, O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, are our Father,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18883AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18883AA\"></sup>our Redeemer from of old is your name.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, why do you make us wander from your waysand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18884AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18884AB\"></sup>harden our heart, so that we fear you not?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18884AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18884AC\"></sup>Return for the sake of your servants,the tribes of your heritage.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18885AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18885AD\"></sup>Your holy people held possession for a little while;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18885AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18885AE\"></sup>our adversaries have trampled down your sanctuary.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18886AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18886AF\"></sup>We have become like those over whom you have never ruled,like those who are not called by your name."
		},
		"64": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">64 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18887A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18887A\"></sup>Oh that you would rend the heavens and come down,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18887B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18887B\"></sup>that the mountains might quake at your presence—",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup> as when fire kindles brushwoodand the fire causes water to boil—<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18888C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18888C\"></sup>to make your name known to your adversaries,and that the nations might tremble at your presence!",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18889D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18889D\"></sup>When you did awesome things that we did not look for,you came down, the mountains quaked at your presence.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18890E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18890E\"></sup>From of old no one has heardor perceived by the ear,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18890F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18890F\"></sup>no eye has seen a God besides you,who acts for those who wait for him.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>You meet him who joyfully works righteousness,those who remember you in your ways.Behold, you were angry, and we sinned;in our sins we have been a long time, and shall we be saved?",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18892G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18892G\"></sup>We have all become like one who is unclean,and all our righteous deeds are like a polluted garment.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18892H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18892H\"></sup>We all fade like a leaf,and our iniquities, like the wind, take us away.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18893I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18893I\"></sup>There is no one who calls upon your name,who rouses himself to take hold of you;for you have hidden your face from us,and have made us melt in the hand of our iniquities.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18894J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18894J\"></sup>But now, O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, you are our Father;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18894K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18894K\"></sup>we are the clay, and you are our potter;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18894L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18894L\"></sup>we are all the work of your hand.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18895M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18895M\"></sup>Be not so terribly angry, O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18895N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18895N\"></sup>and remember not iniquity forever.Behold, please look, we are all your people.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18896O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18896O\"></sup>Your holy cities have become a wilderness;Zion has become a wilderness,Jerusalem a desolation.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18897P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18897P\"></sup>Our holy and beautiful house,where our fathers praised you,has been burned by fire,and all our pleasant places have become ruins.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18898Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18898Q\"></sup>Will you restrain yourself at these things, O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>?Will you keep silent, and afflict us so terribly?"
		},
		"65": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">65 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18899A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18899A\"></sup>I was ready to be sought by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18899B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18899B\"></sup>those who did not ask for me;I was ready to be found by those who did not seek me.I said, “Here I am, here I am,”to a nation that was not called by my name.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18900C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18900C\"></sup>I spread out my hands all the dayto a rebellious people,who walk in a way that is not good,following their own devices;",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>a people who provoke meto my face continually,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18901D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18901D\"></sup>sacrificing in gardensand making offerings on bricks;",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>who sit in tombs,and spend the night in secret places;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18902E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18902E\"></sup>who eat pig's flesh,and broth of tainted meat is in their vessels;",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>who say, “Keep to yourself,do not come near me, for I am too holy for you.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18903F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18903F\"></sup>These are a smoke in my nostrils,a fire that burns all the day.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18904G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18904G\"></sup>it is written before me:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18904H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18904H\"></sup>“I will not keep silent, but I will repay;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18904I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18904I\"></sup>I will indeed repay into their lap",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><span class=\"indent-1-breaks\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>both your iniquities <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18905J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18905J\"></sup>and your fathers' iniquities together,says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18905K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18905K\"></sup>because they made offerings on the mountains<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18905L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18905L\"></sup>and insulted me on the hills,I will measure into their lappayment for their former deeds.”",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18906M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18906M\"></sup>“As the new wine is found in the cluster,and they say, ‘Do not destroy it,for there is a blessing in it,’so I will do for my servants' sake,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18906N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18906N\"></sup>and not destroy them all.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18907O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18907O\"></sup>I will bring forth offspring from Jacob,and from Judah possessors of my mountains;my chosen shall possess it,and my servants shall dwell there.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18908P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18908P\"></sup>Sharon shall become a pasture for flocks,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18908Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18908Q\"></sup>the Valley of Achor a place for herds to lie down,for my people <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18908R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18908R\"></sup>who have sought me.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18909S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18909S\"></sup>you who forsake the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,who forget <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18909T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18909T\"></sup>my holy mountain,who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18909U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18909U\"></sup>set a table for Fortuneand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18909V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18909V\"></sup>fill cups of mixed wine for Destiny,",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>I will destine you to the sword,and all of you shall bow down to the slaughter,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18910W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18910W\"></sup>because, when I called, you did not answer;when I spoke, you did not listen,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18910X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18910X\"></sup>but you did what was evil in my eyesand chose what I did not delight in.”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Therefore thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>:“Behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18911Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18911Y\"></sup>my servants shall eat,but you shall be hungry;behold, my servants shall drink,but you shall be thirsty;behold, my servants shall rejoice,but you shall be put to shame;",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18912Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18912Z\"></sup>my servants shall sing for gladness of heart,but you shall cry out for pain of heartand shall wail for breaking of spirit.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>You shall leave your name to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18913AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18913AA\"></sup>my chosen <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18913AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18913AB\"></sup>for a curse,and the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span> will put you to death,but his servants <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18913AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18913AC\"></sup>he will call by another name,",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>so that he who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18914AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18914AD\"></sup>blesses himself in the landshall bless himself by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18914AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18914AE\"></sup>the God of truth,and he who takes an oath in the landshall swear by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18914AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18914AF\"></sup>the God of truth;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18914AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18914AG\"></sup>because the former troubles are forgottenand are hidden from my eyes.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“For behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18915AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18915AH\"></sup>I create new heavensand a new earth,and the former things shall not be rememberedor come into mind.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>But be glad and rejoice foreverin that which I create;for behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18916AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18916AI\"></sup>I create Jerusalem to be a joy,and her people to be a gladness.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18917AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18917AJ\"></sup>I will rejoice in Jerusalemand be glad in my people;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18917AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18917AK\"></sup>no more shall be heard in it the sound of weepingand the cry of distress.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>No more shall there be in itan infant who lives but a few days,or an old man who does not fill out his days,for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18918AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18918AL\"></sup>the young man shall die a hundred years old,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18918AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18918AM\"></sup>the sinner a hundred years old shall be accursed.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18919AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18919AN\"></sup>They shall build houses and inhabit them;they shall plant vineyards and eat their fruit.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18920AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18920AO\"></sup>They shall not build and another inhabit;they shall not plant and another eat;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18920AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18920AP\"></sup>for like the days of a tree shall the days of my people be,and my chosen shall long enjoy the work of their hands.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18921AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18921AQ\"></sup>They shall not labor in vain<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18921AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18921AR\"></sup>or bear children for calamity,for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18921AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18921AS\"></sup>they shall be the offspring of the blessed of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,and their descendants with them.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18922AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18922AT\"></sup>Before they call I will answer;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18922AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18922AU\"></sup>while they are yet speaking I will hear.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18923AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18923AV\"></sup>The wolf and the lamb shall graze together;the lion shall eat straw like the ox,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18923AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18923AW\"></sup>dust shall be the serpent's food.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18923AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18923AX\"></sup>They shall not hurt or destroyin all my holy mountain,”says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>."
		},
		"66": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">66 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18924A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18924A\"></sup>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18924B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18924B\"></sup>“Heaven is my throne,and the earth is my footstool;what is the house that you would build for me,and what is the place of my rest?",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18925C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18925C\"></sup>All these things my hand has made,and so all these things came to be,declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18925D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18925D\"></sup>But this is the one to whom I will look:he who is humble and contrite in spiritand trembles at my word.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18926E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18926E\"></sup>“He who slaughters an ox is like one who kills a man;he who sacrifices a lamb, like one who breaks a dog's neck;he who presents a grain offering, like one who offers <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18926F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18926F\"></sup>pig's blood;he who makes a memorial offering of frankincense, like one who blesses an idol.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18926G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18926G\"></sup>These have chosen their own ways,and their soul delights in their abominations;",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18927H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18927H\"></sup>I also will choose harsh treatment for themand bring <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18927I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18927I\"></sup>their fears upon them,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18927J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18927J\"></sup>because when I called, no one answered,when I spoke, they did not listen;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18927K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18927K\"></sup>but they did what was evil in my eyesand chose that in which I did not delight.”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Hear the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,you who tremble at his word:“Your brothers who hate youand cast you out for my name's sakehave said, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18928L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18928L\"></sup>‘Let the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> be glorified,that we may see your joy’;but it is they who shall be put to shame.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“The sound of an uproar from the city!A sound from the temple!The sound of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18929M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18929M\"></sup>rendering recompense to his enemies!",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18930N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18930N\"></sup>“Before she was in laborshe gave birth;before her pain came upon hershe delivered a son.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Who has heard such a thing?Who has seen such things?Shall a land be born in one day?Shall a nation be brought forth in one moment?For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18931O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18931O\"></sup>as soon as Zion was in laborshe brought forth her children.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Shall I bring to the point of birth and not cause to bring forth?”says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>;“shall I, who cause to bring forth, shut the womb?”says your God.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18933P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18933P\"></sup>“Rejoice with Jerusalem, and be glad for her,all you who love her;rejoice with her in joy,all you who mourn over her;",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>that you may nurse and be satisfiedfrom her consoling breast;that you may drink deeply with delightfrom her glorious abundance.”",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>For thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18935Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18935Q\"></sup>“Behold, I will extend peace to her like a river,and the glory of the nations like an overflowing stream;and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18935R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18935R\"></sup>you shall nurse, you shall be carried upon her hip,and bounced upon her knees.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>As one whom his mother comforts,so <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18936S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18936S\"></sup>I will comfort you;you shall be comforted in Jerusalem.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>You shall see, and your heart shall rejoice;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18937T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18937T\"></sup>your bones shall flourish like the grass;and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18937U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18937U\"></sup>the hand of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> shall be known to his servants,and he shall show his indignation against his enemies.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“For behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18938V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18938V\"></sup>the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will come in fire,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18938W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18938W\"></sup>his chariots like the whirlwind,to render his anger in fury,and his rebuke with flames of fire.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18939X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18939X\"></sup>by fire <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18939Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18939Y\"></sup>will the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> enter into judgment,and by his sword, with all flesh;and those slain by the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> shall be many.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18940Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18940Z\"></sup>“Those who sanctify and purify themselves to go into the gardens, following one in the midst, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18940AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18940AA\"></sup>eating pig's flesh and the abomination and mice, shall come to an end together, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“For I know their works and their thoughts, and the time is coming <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18941AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18941AB\"></sup>to gather all nations and tongues. And they shall come and shall see my glory,",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>and I will set a sign among them. And from them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18942AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18942AC\"></sup>I will send survivors to the nations, to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18942AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18942AD\"></sup>Tarshish, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18942AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18942AE\"></sup>Pul, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18942AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18942AF\"></sup>Lud, who draw the bow, to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18942AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18942AG\"></sup>Tubal and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18942AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18942AH\"></sup>Javan, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18942AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18942AI\"></sup>to the coastlands far away, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18942AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18942AJ\"></sup>that have not heard my fame or seen my glory. And they shall declare my glory among the nations.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18943AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18943AK\"></sup>And they shall bring all your brothers from all the nations <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18943AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18943AL\"></sup>as an offering to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, on horses and in chariots and in litters and on mules and on dromedaries, to my holy mountain Jerusalem, says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, just as the Israelites bring their grain offering in a clean vessel to the house of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18944AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18944AM\"></sup>And some of them also I will take for priests and for Levites, says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>“For as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18945AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18945AN\"></sup>the new heavens and the new earththat I makeshall remain before me, says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,so <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18945AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18945AO\"></sup>shall your offspring and your name remain.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18946AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18946AP\"></sup>From new moon to new moon,and from Sabbath to Sabbath,all flesh shall come to worship before me,declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>“And they shall go out and look on the dead bodies of the men who have rebelled against me. For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18947AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18947AQ\"></sup>their worm shall not die, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18947AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18947AR\"></sup>their fire shall not be quenched, and they shall be an abhorrence to all flesh.”"
		}
	}
};
module.exports = book;